{"type":"message","id":"e1c49999","parentId":"0c4c73c4","timestamp":"2026-07-05T00:09:35.901Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_42fa8576e45c471995ce7d6a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def _capture_and_crop(client, mgr, device_ip: str, category: str,\r\n                      x: float, y: float, w: float, h: float) -> tuple:\r\n    \"\"\"ISAPI 截图 → 按比例裁剪 → 返回 (bgr, 截图路径, 裁剪信息dict)。\r\n\r\n    统一入口，白平衡和对焦共用。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import time as _time\r\n    _time.sleep(0.1)  # 等设备稳定\r\n    jpg = client.capture_picture()\r\n    if not jpg:\r\n        return None, \"\", {\"error\": \"ISAPI截图失败\"}\r\n\r\n    # 保存全图\r\n    ts = int(_time.time() * 1000)\r\n    temp_dir = _temp_dir(category, device_ip)\r\n    full_path = os.path.join(temp_dir, f\"full_{ts}.jpg\")\r\n    with open(full_path, \"wb\") as f:\r\n        f.write(jpg)\r\n\r\n    bgr = cv2.imdecode(np.frombuffer(jpg, np.uint8), cv2.IMREAD_COLOR)\r\n    if bgr is None:\r\n        return None, full_path, {\"error\": \"图像解码失败\"}\r\n\r\n    full_h, full_w = bgr.shape[:2]\r\n\r\n    # 裁剪\r\n    if w > 0 and h > 0:\r\n        x1 = max(0, int(x * full_w))\r\n        y1 = max(0, int(y * full_h))\r\n        x2 = min(full_w, int((x + w) * full_w))\r\n        y2 = min(full_h, int((y + h) * full_h))\r\n        if x2 <= x1 or y2 <= y1:\r\n            return bgr, full_path, {\"error\": \"裁剪区域无效\"}\r\n        cropped = bgr[y1:y2, x1:x2]\r\n        crop_path = os.path.join(temp_dir, f\"crop_{ts}.jpg\")\r\n        cv2.imwrite(crop_path, cropped)\r\n    else:\r\n        cropped = bgr\r\n        crop_path = full_path\r\n        x1, y1, x2, y2 = 0, 0, full_w, full_h\r\n\r\n    info = {\r\n        \"full_w\": full_w, \"full_h\": full_h,\r\n        \"crop_x1\": x1, \"crop_y1\": y1, \"crop_x2\": x2, \"crop_y2\": y2,\r\n        \"crop_w\": x2 - x1, \"crop_h\": y2 - y1,\r\n        \"crop_path\": crop_path,\r\n        \"pixels\": (x2 - x1) * (y2 - y1),\r\n    }\r\n    return cropped, crop_path, info\r\n\r\n\n[262 more lines in file. Use offset=3935 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783210175901}}
{"type":"message","id":"221c1379","parentId":"e1c49999","timestamp":"2026-07-05T00:10:26.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我已经完整阅读了截图函数 `_capture_and_crop`。让我总结一下完整的实现逻辑。\n\n### 截图函数本地的0.1s稳定延时\n\n`_capture_and_crop` 本地会 sleep 0.1s，这是为ISAPI截图前等设备稳定：\n- 通过 `client.capture_picture()` 发送ISAPI请求\n- 等待摄像头内部处理和稳定\n\n### Searcher级的0.3s稳定延时\n\nSearcher（白平衡 Searcher、对焦 Searcher）在每步操作后，会额外 sleep 0.3s：\n- 白平衡：在写入增益后，调用 `_capture()` 前sleep 0.3s\n- 对焦：在停止移动后，调用 `_capture()` 前sleep 0.3s  \n- 目的：等待移动步长结束后的稳定延迟\n\n### 总结\n\n- **第一层稳定延时**：截图函数内部，`_capture_and_crop` 开始处 `time.sleep(0.1)`，确保ISAPI截图前设备稳定\n- **第二层稳定延时**：Searcher内部，在移动/写入参数后，调用 `_capture()` 前sleep 0.3s，确保参数生效后设备稳定\n- **不需要额外逻辑**：系统没有复杂的延时等待动画机制，直接用 asyncio.sleep(0.3) 实现\n\n这正是老板在做稳定性权衡时设定的两个稳定延时：0.1s（本地稳定）+ 0.3s（参数稳定）= 0.4s 总稳定时间，绕过了求稳和求快的内部伪需求。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 完整分析总结\n\n### 截图延迟机制\n\n本题包含两层稳定延时：\n\n#### 1. 截图函数内部的0.1s（直接稳定）\n\n**脚本**：`router.py` 中的 `_capture_and_crop()`（第3885行起）\n\n**实现**：\n```python\ndef _capture_and_crop(client, mgr, device_ip: str, category: str,\n                      x: float, y: float, w: float, h: float) -> tuple:\n    import time as _time\n    _time.sleep(0.1)  # ← 这里\n    jpg = client.capture_picture()  # → ISAPI截图\n```\n\n**目的**：等待摄像头内部处理完成，对下次ISAPI请求稳定。\n\n---\n\n#### 2. Searcher内部的0.3s（参数稳定）\n\n**脚本**：\n- `whitebalance.py`（第430行起）\n- `autofocus.py`（第283行起）\n\n**实现**：\n\n**白平衡**：\n```python\n# 应用增益\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._set_wb_gains, cmd[\"red_gain\"], cmd[\"blue_gain\"])\nawait asyncio.sleep(0.3)  # ← 等待稳定\n\n# 重新截图\nbgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n```\n\n**对焦**：\n```python\n# 移动\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._move_focus, cmd[\"action\"], cmd[\"duration\"])\nawait asyncio.sleep(cmd[\"duration\"])  # 等步长（0.2s/0.05s）\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._stop_focus())\nawait asyncio.sleep(0.3)  # ← 等待稳定\n\n# 重新截图\nbgr, _ = await asyncio.to_thread(self._capture)\n```\n\n**目的**：等待移动/参数生效后的稳定时间，确保下一个截图读取到新的稳定值。\n\n---\n\n### 延时位置总结\n\n```\n步骤流程（白平衡或对焦）：\n  _capture()                → ISAPI截图 ←→ time.sleep(0.1) [截图门内]\n    ↓\n  算法决策（wb.step 或 af.step）\n    ↓\n  移动/写入参数\n    ↓\n  await asyncio.sleep(0.3)  ← [Find: 0.3s门] ← 这里是外层稳定延时\n    ↓\n  _capture()                → ISAPI截图 ←→ time.sleep(0.1) [截图门内]\n```\n\n**两处延时（0.1s国内固定值 + 0.3s外层稳定延时）= 0.4s总稳定时间。**\n\n---\n\n### 关键行号\n\n| 文件 | 脚本 | 延时位置 | 行号 |\n|------|------|----------|------|\n| `router.py` | `_capture_and_crop()` | 0.1s | 3888 |\n| `whitebalance.py` | `WhiteBalanceSearcher.run()` | 0.3s | 430 |\n| `autofocus.py` | `FocusSearcher.run()` | 0.3s | 283 |\n\n---\n\n老板询问是否还需要其他方法或修正，当前已通过 asyncio.sleep(0.3) 满足稳定需求，后续如需优化可调整该延时值。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":116135,"output":1050,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117185,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783210175903,"responseId":"cht000daf15@dx19f2f9bf31329bb503"}}
