{"type":"message","id":"67ed5357","parentId":"4e36e730","timestamp":"2026-07-05T00:30:27.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，从代码中找到了慢快门的配置（function.py 第118-120行）：\n```python\n\"slow_shutter\": {\n    \"label\": \"慢快门\",\n    \"endpoint\": \"/Image/channels/{ch}/Shutter\",\n    \"test_key\": \"minShutterLevelLimit\",\n```\n\n从白平衡代码看到获取到的支持快门值：\n```python\nresult[\"data\"][\"supported_levels\"] = [\n    \"1/30\", \"1/60\", \"1/125\", \"1/250\", \"1/500\",\n    \"1/1000\", \"1/2000\", \"1/4000\", \"1/8000\",\n    result[\"data\"].get(\"min\", \"1/30000\"),\n    result[\"data\"].get(\"max\", \"1/25\")\n]\n```\n\n以及获取时车读到的：\n```python\n\"min\": elem.text or \"1/30000\",\n\"max\": elem.text or \"1/25\"\n```\n\n现在需要验证\"慢快门倍率\"（慢快门*1.25~*8）是否真的是延长曝光时间（例如1/25*8=2s）。\n\n根据海康威视PTZ摄像头的标准实现，\"慢快门倍率\"的含义：\n\n1. **基本快门时间**：设备默认快门时间（如1/25s）\n2. **慢快门倍率**：快动协议支持的时间倍率（如1.25x, 2x, 8x）\n3. **实际快门时间**：1/快门值 × 倍率\n\n所以如果是1/25 × 8 = 2s，这是对的。慢快门倍率通过minShutterLevelLimit和maxShutterLevelLimit反映。具体实现逻辑是定义1/25慢快门模式，快动协议再旋转到1.25~8倍率。接下来搜索慢快门倍率的min和max约束，得到精确范围。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好，从代码中找到了慢快门配置（function.py 第118-120行）。\n\n现在让我查找海康威视ISAPI关于慢快门的详细文档。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":126729,"output":494,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127223,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783211366142,"responseId":"cht000d64af@dx19f2fae542329bb503"}}
