{"type":"message","id":"9060ae89","parentId":"8ed5a218","timestamp":"2026-07-05T00:44:22.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到5处硬编码延时。现在我需要在 region_base.py 中创建统一的延时函数。\n\n根据老板的要求：\n- 延时 = 曝光时间*2 + 基础延迟\n- 基础延迟 = 0.5s（替代原来的0.3s）\n- 截图函数中的 0.1s 也要统一\n\n需要读取曝光时间的功能。让我先搜索现有的曝光时间读取逻辑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d50f0ab57d2346f09a658e09","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"exposure_time|曝光时间|ExposureTime|exposure_ms|get_exposure\" -Context 0,3 | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object -First 40","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":131906,"output":189,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132095,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783212246146,"responseId":"cht000d576f@dx19f2fbba9ca2871503"}}
