{"type":"message","id":"d67e3037","parentId":"60e8f167","timestamp":"2026-07-05T07:51:44.085Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about ISAPI endpoints for slow shutter functionality. They want me to check if the ISAPI has endpoints for reading/writing slow shutter settings.\n\nFrom what I can see:\n1. The code uses `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` endpoint for slow shutter\n2. The slow shutter control uses `minShutterLevelLimit` XML field\n3. The current implementation reads from this endpoint to get slow shutter status\n\nLet me check the actual ISAPI documentation or test if the endpoint exists. I should look at what fields are available in the Shutter endpoint response.\n\nThe slow shutter implementation seems to:\n- GET `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` - reads current shutter settings including minShutterLevelLimit and maxShutterLevelLimit\n- PUT `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` - writes minShutterLevelLimit to control slow shutter ratio\n\nI should verify what ISAPI endpoint is actually used and what fields are available.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板在问ISAPI端点是否存在。让我读取router.py中慢快门相关的完整实现，检查ISAPI端点。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_46d1126c95644248b048d5eb","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":3667,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4439,"output":304,"cacheRead":163102,"cacheWrite":3254,"totalTokens":171099,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783237886171,"responseId":"msg_77088dc1-c901-4b97-b051-b273171db440"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a61a0d14","parentId":"d67e3037","timestamp":"2026-07-05T07:51:44.109Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_46d1126c95644248b048d5eb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# === 慢快门 (v8.44) ===\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"获取慢快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_slow_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取慢快门状态和倍率。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取慢快门失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        shutter_level = None\r\n        min_limit = None\r\n        max_limit = None\r\n\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag in (\"ShutterLevel\", \"shutterLevel\"):\r\n                shutter_level = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n            elif tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                min_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                max_limit = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n\r\n        supported = bool(min_limit and max_limit and min_limit != max_limit)\r\n\r\n        ratio = 1.0\r\n        if supported and shutter_level and min_limit:\r\n            from src.controlpanel.region_base import _parse_shutter_level\r\n            base_time = _parse_shutter_level(shutter_level)\r\n            min_time = _parse_shutter_level(min_limit)\r\n            if base_time > 0 and min_time > 0:\r\n                ratio = round(base_time / min_time, 2)\r\n\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"data\": {\r\n                \"supported\": supported,\r\n                \"enabled\": ratio > 1.0,\r\n                \"ratio\": ratio,\r\n                \"shutter_level\": shutter_level,\r\n                \"min_limit\": min_limit,\r\n                \"max_limit\": max_limit\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取慢快门异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"设置慢快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_slow_shutter(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置慢快门倍率。\r\n\r\n    请求体:\r\n        {\"ratio\": 0}  → 关闭\r\n        {\"ratio\": 1.25} → 1.25倍率\r\n        {\"ratio\": 2} → 2倍率\r\n        {\"ratio\": 4} → 4倍率\r\n        {\"ratio\": 8} → 8倍率\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import re\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n\n[603 more lines in file. Use offset=3747 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783237904109}}
{"type":"message","id":"73645ff5","parentId":"a61a0d14","timestamp":"2026-07-05T07:52:44.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是ISAPI端点是否存在。我已经看到了代码中使用的ISAPI端点是 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter`。\n\n但是用户问的是\"读取\"慢快门。让我思考一下这个问题：\n\n1. 当前的实现是读取 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` 端点\n2. 从这个端点获取 `minShutterLevelLimit` 和 `maxShutterLevelLimit` 字段\n3. 如果 `min_limit != max_limit`，说明慢快门功能被支持\n\n但是，这里有个问题：`minShutterLevelLimit` 字段是否真的存在？我需要检查：\n- 这个字段是否是ISAPI标准的一部分\n- 设备是否真的返回这个字段\n- 如果设备不支持慢快门，这个字段是否存在\n\n我应该检查：\n1. 现有的代码中，是否有读取这个字段的逻辑\n2. 这个字段的来源是什么\n3. 是否需要实际测试设备来验证\n\n让我看看现有的代码中，是否有其他地方读取这个字段。\n从代码中看，ISAPI端点是 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter`，读取 `minShutterLevelLimit` 和 `maxShutterLevelLimit` 字段。\n\n但是这里有个潜在问题：\n- `minShutterLevelLimit` 这个字段是否真的存在？\n- 如果设备不支持慢快门，这个字段可能不存在\n\n让我检查现有的代码中，是否有其他读取这个字段的逻辑，或者这个字段是否真的存在。\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_68165ae7e9244c379577eca9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"minShutterLevelLimit|MaxShutterLevelLimit|MinShutterLevelLimit\" -Context 2,2 | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":5016,"output":424,"cacheRead":166356,"cacheWrite":582,"totalTokens":172378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783237904112,"responseId":"msg_8114ec4e-15e6-4b43-b467-ba3a6d237bd3"}}
