{"type":"message","id":"ff71d0b2","parentId":"bb79f250","timestamp":"2026-07-05T08:06:51.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to search for Hikvision ISAPI documentation for slow shutter (低照度电子慢快门). The previous attempts to fetch documentation failed. Let me think about what I know about Hikvision ISAPI and slow shutter:\n\nFrom my knowledge:\n1. Slow shutter in Hikvision ISAPI is typically controlled via `/Image/channels/{channel}/SlowShutter` endpoint\n2. It's different from the mechanical shutter `/Image/channels/{channel}/Shutter`\n3. The slow shutter has modes like: off, auto, manual\n4. It has a multiplier setting (1x, 2x, 4x, 8x, etc.)\n\nBut I need to be careful - I don't have direct access to the official documentation since all web fetch attempts failed. I should tell the user that I cannot access the official documentation due to network issues, and suggest alternative approaches:\n\n1. Test the endpoint directly on the device\n2. Use the Hikvision SDK documentation\n3. Check if there's any local documentation\n\nLet me be honest with the user that the network searches are failing and I cannot access the official ISAPI documentation.\n\nActually, looking at the code, I see that the current implementation uses `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` with `minShutterLevelLimit` and `maxShutterLevelLimit`. But the user is asking about \"低照度电子慢快门\" which is a different feature from the mechanical shutter.\n\nIn Hikvision ISAPI, the slow shutter (低照度电子慢快门) is typically:\n- Endpoint: `/Image/channels/{channel}/SlowShutter` or `/Image/channels/{channel}/slowShutter`\n- Fields: SlowShutterMode, SlowShutterMultiplier or similar\n\nBut I need to verify this. Since the network searches are failing, I should:\n1. Acknowledge that network searches are failing\n2. Suggest testing the endpoint directly on the device\n3. Provide what I know from general Hikvision ISAPI knowledge\n\nLet me be honest and direct with the user.\n老板，网络搜索全部失败，无法访问海康ISAPI官方文档。\n\n**现状：**\n当前代码使用的是 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` 端点，通过 `minShutterLevelLimit` 控制慢快门。但您说的是\"低照度电子慢快门\"，这可能是不同的功能。\n\n**可能的端点：**\n根据一般海康ISAPI知识，慢快门可能在：\n- `/Image/channels/{channel}/SlowShutter`\n- `/Image/channels/{channel}/slowShutter`\n\n**建议：**\n直接在设备上测试端点是否存在：\n```\nGET http://{设备IP}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/SlowShutter\nGET http://{设备IP}/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/slowShutter\n```\n\n需要我现在测试设备吗？老板，网络搜索全部失败，无法访问海康ISAPI官方文档。\n\n**当前实现问题：**\n代码使用 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` + `minShutterLevelLimit`，但这可能是机械快门的限制，不是低照度电子慢快门。\n\n**低照度电子慢快门可能的端点：**\n- `/Image/channels/{channel}/SlowShutter`\n- `/Image/channels/{channel}/slowShutter`\n\n**建议：**\n直接在设备上测试端点是否存在，确认正确的ISAPI端点。需要我测试吗？","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The user is asking about Hikvision ISAPI endpoint for \"low illumination slow shutter\" (低照度电子慢快门). Network searches are failing. Let me check the existing codebase for any references to slow shutter or low illumination endpoints.\n\nThe user specifically said:\n- \"低照度电子慢快门\" (low illumination slow shutter)\n- NOT mechanical shutter\n- They want the ISAPI endpoint\n\nFrom my previous analysis, I saw references to `minShutterLevelLimit` in the code. But the user is asking about a different feature - \"low illumination slow shutter\" which is typically a digital/electronic shutter extension feature.\n\nIn Hikvision ISAPI, the slow shutter / low illumination feature is typically controlled via:\n- `/ISAPI/Image/channels/{channel}/exposure` - exposure settings\n- Or `/ISAPI/ContentMgmt/Streaming/channels/{channel}/slowShutter` \n\nLet me search the codebase for any slow shutter related code.\n老板在找海康ISAPI中\"低照度电子慢快门\"的端点。网络搜索失败，让我在代码中找线索。\n...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_952d69f9098e4d95b1ce7e77","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"astrohub\\src\" -Recurse -Filter \"*.py\" | Select-String -Pattern \"slow|Slow|low|Low\" | Select-Object Path, LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object 