{"type":"message","id":"554b577a","parentId":"b87cdbc4","timestamp":"2026-07-05T08:32:02.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to find the Hikvision ISAPI endpoint for slow shutter (低照度电子慢快门). I've been searching online but all attempts have failed. Now I have device information - there's a device at 192.168.5.72 with credentials.\n\nI should:\n1. Try to access the device directly and probe for slow shutter endpoints\n2. Check what endpoints exist on the device\n3. Look for the correct ISAPI endpoint for slow shutter functionality\n\nLet me try to access the device and probe different endpoints to find the slow shutter functionality.\n...\n有设备信息，让我直接测试ISAPI端点。\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5104abfeca4a41f8b6d09ccb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n\n# Device credentials\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nport = 80\nusername = 'admin'\npassword = 'Nftw1357'\n\n# Possible slow shutter endpoints\nendpoints = [\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/SlowShutter',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/slowShutter',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/SlowShutterMode',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/exposure',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/Exposure'\n]\n\nsession = requests.Session()\nsession.auth = HTTPDigestAuth(username, password)\nsession.headers.update({'Content-Type': 'application/xml; charset=UTF-8'})\n\nfor endpoint in endpoints:\n    url = f'http://{ip}:{port}{endpoint}'\n    try:\n        resp = session.get(url, timeout=5)\n        print(f'{endpoint}: {resp.status_code}')\n        if resp.status_code == 200 and 'slow' in resp.text.lower():\n            print(f'  Found slow shutter related content!')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{endpoint}: Error - {e}')\n\"\n","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe user wants me to check