{"type":"message","id":"dec800fb","parentId":"db3a8e32","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:17:57.631Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nThe user wants me to search the official Hikvision ISAPI documentation PDF for the slow shutter endpoint. The PDF has 1268 pages. I need to search for keywords like \"慢快门\" (slow shutter) or \"低照度\" (low illumination) in the PDF.\n\nLet me search the PDF for slow shutter related content.\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_44d202f93da44e67aa6b8dd6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport os, fitz\n\npdf_dir = r'astrohub\\documents\\ISAPI_SDK'\npdf_files = [f for f in os.listdir(pdf_dir) if f.endswith('.pdf')]\npdf_path = os.path.join(pdf_dir, pdf_files[0])\n\ndoc = fitz.open(pdf_path)\n# Search for slow shutter / 慢快门 / 低照度\nkeywords = ['慢快门', '低照度', 'slow', 'SlowShutter', 'shutter']\n\nfor i, page in enumerate(doc):\n    text = page.get_text()\n    for kw in keywords:\n        if kw.lower() in text.lower():\n            # Find context around the keyword\n            lines = text.split('\\n')\n            for j, line in enumerate(lines):\n                if kw.lower() in line.lower():\n                    start = max(0, j-2)\n                    end = min(len(lines), j+3)\n                    print(f'=== Page {i+1} (keyword: {kw}) ===')\n                    print('\\n'.join(lines[start:end]))\n                    print()\ndoc.close()\n\" 2>&1 | Select-Object -First 80\n","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nPDF打开成功，1268页。现在搜索慢快门相关内容。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3a7e4069b899458196d3194e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport os, fitz\npdf_dir = r'astrohub\\documents\\ISAPI_SDK'\npdf_files = [f for f in os.listdir(pdf_dir) if f.endswith('.pdf')]\npdf_path = os.path.join(pdf_dir, pdf_files[0])\ndoc = fitz.open(pdf_path)\nfound = []\nfor i, page in enumerate(doc):\n    text = page.get_text()\n    if '慢快门' in text or 'SlowShutter' in text or 'slow shutter' in text.lower():\n        found.append(i+1)\nprint(f'Found on pages: {found[:20]}')\nif found:\n    for p in found[:3]:\n        page = doc[p-1]\n        text = page.get_text()\n        # Find context around the keyword\n        for kw in ['慢快门', 'SlowShutter', 'slow shutter']:\n            idx = text.lower().find(kw.lower())\n            if idx >= 0:\n                start = max(0, idx-100)\n                end = min(len(text), idx+200)\n                print(f'\\n--- Page {p} (around {kw}) ---')\n                print(text[start:end])\ndoc.close()\n\"\n","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":3143,"output":727,"cacheRead":197857,"cacheWrite":1590,"totalTokens":203317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783243037880,"responseId":"msg_34b03d7b-43c8-449d-bb5b-1d5491588626"}}
