{"type":"message","id":"e10b4f0c","parentId":"586b4a31","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:22:33.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板指出我陷入了循环。我需要重新总结已找到的信息并继续任务。\n\n从PDF中我找到了：\n- DSS (Dynamic Slow Shutter) 是海康的慢快门功能\n- 包含 enabled 和 DSSLevel 字段\n- DSSLevel 有 *1.25, *1.5, *2, *3, *4, *5, *6, *8 等值\n\n我需要找到DSS的端点路径。从PDF内容看，DSS嵌套在图像设置XML中，和NoiseReduce、WhiteBalance在同一层级。这应该是 `/Image/channels/{channel}/DSS` 端点。\n\n让我直接确认这个端点并更新代码。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。**DSS (Dynamic Slow Shutter)** 是海康的慢快门功能。\n\n**PDF内容（第405页）：**\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>\n    <!--opt, enum, 低照度等级, subType:string, \n    [*1.25, *1.5, *2, *3, *4, *5, *6, *8, *12, *16, *24, *32, *48, *64, *96, *128, *256, *512, auto]-->\n    *1.25\n  </DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\nDSS和NoiseReduce、WhiteBalance在同一层级，端点应该是 `/Image/channels/{channel}/DSS`。\n\n让我直接测试这个端点：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9bef2f1985354291a2f8b2f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nsession = requests.Session()\nsession.auth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nsession.headers.update({'Content-Type': 'application/xml; charset=UTF-8'})\n\nendpoints = [\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/dss',\n]\n\nfor ep in endpoints:\n    url = f'http://{ip}:80{ep}'\n    try:\n        resp = session.get(url, timeout=5)\n        print(f'{ep}: {resp.status_code}')\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            print(resp.text[:500])\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{ep}: Error - {e}')\n\" 2>&1 | Select-String -Pattern \"Error|Warning\" -NotMatch","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":9402,"output":626,"cacheRead":161329,"cacheWrite":883,"totalTokens":172240,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783243295867,"responseId":"msg_4af69cd9-2470-45fd-8d18-f7346279ea89"}}
{"type":"message","id":"57f2cc7a","parentId":"e10b4f0c","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:22:34.815Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_9bef2f1985354291a2f8b2f4","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS: 200\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n\r\n<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n\r\n<enabled>true</enabled>\r\n\r\n<DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\r\n\r\n</DSS>\r\n\r\n\r\n/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/dss: 200\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n\r\n<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n\r\n<enabled>true</enabled>\r\n\r\n<DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\r\n\r\n</DSS>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1471,"aggregated":"/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS: 200\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n\r\n<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n\r\n<enabled>true</enabled>\r\n\r\n<DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\r\n\r\n</DSS>\r\n\r\n\r\n/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/dss: 200\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n\r\n<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n\r\n<enabled>true</enabled>\r\n\r\n<DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\r\n\r\n</DSS>","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783243354815}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ae0e5b0","parentId":"57f2cc7a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:23:12.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The correct ISAPI endpoint for slow shutter is:\n\n**`/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS`**\n\n- GET returns current state: enabled=true, DSSLevel=*8\n- DSSLevel values: *1.25, *1.5, *2, *3, *4, *5, *6, *8, *12, *16, *24, *32, *48, *64, *96, *128, *256, *512, auto\n\nThe current implementation uses `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` with `minShutterLevelLimit` - this is WRONG. The correct approach is to use the DSS endpoint.\n\nNow I need to update the slow shutter implementation in router.py to use the correct endpoint.\n\nLet me report this to the boss first, then fix the code.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！正确的ISAPI端点：\n\n**`/ISAPI/Image/channels/{channel}/DSS`** (Dynamic Slow Shutter)\n\n```xml\nGET /ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS → 200\n\n<DSS version=\"2.0\">\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n**支持的倍率值**（来自官方SDK文档）：\n`*1.25, *1.5, *2, *3, *4, *5, *6, *8, *12, *16, *24, *32, *48, *64, *96, *128, *256, *512, auto`\n\n---\n\n**问题确认：**\n当前代码使用 `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` + `minShutterLevelLimit` 控制慢快门 → **这是错误的**。\n\n**正确方案：**\n- 端点：`/ISAPI/Image/channels/{channel}/DSS`\n- `<enabled>true/false</enabled>` → 开关\n- `<DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>` → 倍率\n\n**下拉菜单选项应对应：**\n关闭(enabled=false) → *1.25 → *1.5 → *2 → *3 → *4 → *5 → *6 → *8\n\n老板，确认是否按此方案更新代码？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":9692,"output":520,"cacheRead":200704,"cacheWrite":980,"totalTokens":211896,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783243354819,"responseId":"msg_f4f404bc-5241-4095-a633-f191a1ca1b8c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6d0ddd0","parentId":"7ae0e5b0","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:41:51.363Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"46276\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-07-05 17:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n有什么方法，从设备获取慢快门是否支持，以及支持多少倍"}],"timestamp":1783244511348}}
{"type":"message","id":"be20bbeb","parentId":"a6d0ddd0","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:42:17.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to determine from the device whether slow shutter (DSS) is supported and what multiplier values it supports. I should check the ISAPI capabilities endpoint for DSS.\n\nFrom the SDK documentation pattern, I should check:\n1. `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/capabilities` - this might list supported features\n2. Or `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS/capabilities` - specific capabilities for DSS\n\nLet me test this on the device.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f21d22a5a5c04cd0a1495662","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport requests\nfrom requests.auth import HTTPDigestAuth\n\nip = '192.168.5.72'\nsession = requests.Session()\nsession.auth = HTTPDigestAuth('admin', 'Nftw1357')\nsession.headers.update({'Content-Type': 'application/xml; charset=UTF-8'})\n\n# 测试capabilities端点\nendpoints = [\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/capabilities',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS/capabilities',\n    '/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS?format=json',\n]\n\nfor ep in endpoints:\n    url = f'http://{ip}:80{ep}'\n    try:\n        resp = session.get(url, timeout=5)\n        print(f'{ep}: {resp.status_code}')\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\n            print(resp.text[:800])\n        print()\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{ep}: Error - {e}')\n        print()\n\" 2>&1 | Select-String -Pattern \"Warning\" -NotMatch","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":9948,"output":407,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":163194,"totalTokens":173549,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783244511378,"responseId":"msg_2dedcbab-8e0b-4965-9127-0c8151e4ab96"}}
