{"type":"message","id":"ad76a3ac","parentId":"49c85d96","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:43:17.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! Now I have the full capabilities response. I can see the DSS section:\n\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled opt=\"true,false\">true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel opt=\"*1.25,*1.5,*2,*3,*4,*6,*8\">*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\nSo the device supports DSS with these multiplier values: *1.25, *1.5, *2, *3, *4, *6, *8\n\nThe current value is *8 and enabled is true.\n\nNow I need to update the code to use the correct DSS endpoint and get the supported values from capabilities.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"完美！从 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/capabilities` 可以直接获取：\n\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled opt=\"true,false\">true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel opt=\"*1.25,*1.5,*2,*3,*4,*6,*8\">*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n**结论：**\n\n| 信息 | 获取方式 |\n|------|----------|\n| 是否支持DSS | capabilities中有 `<DSS>` 节点 = 支持 |\n| 支持的倍率 | `<DSSLevel opt=\"*1.25,*1.5,*2,*3,*4,*6,*8\">` |\n| 当前状态 | GET `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/DSS` |\n| 当前倍率 | `*8` |\n\n**设备实际支持：关闭、*1.25、*1.5、*2、*3、*4、*6、*8**（不是之前设想的*5）\n\n现在按此方案更新代码？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":11503,"output":393,"cacheRead":163575,"cacheWrite":778,"totalTokens":176249,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783244559473,"responseId":"msg_875ae51a-4d5c-435c-b578-b7b45b150489"}}
