{"type":"message","id":"3650be87","parentId":"bfe61340","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:48:59.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\nOK, now I have a good understanding. Let me read the current loadSlowShutter function to understand how it's currently implemented.\n\nThe user wants me to:\n1. Add full /Image/channels/1/capabilities test to function.py\n2. Write full info to function.json\n3. Update slow shutter dropdown to read from function.json (not hardcoded)\n4. Review all other dropdowns that need device capability detection\n\nI need to:\n1. First give the boss a report (as requested)\n2. Wait for review before executing\n\nLet me read the current loadSlowShutter function to understand the current implementation.\n...\n...\nLet me read the current loadSlowShutter function and understand the current implementation.\n...\n...\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5113a7dd4a7043cba558dc2c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1549,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_51348e54c1124c9aa43e2951","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\data\\devices\\240f9b764193\\function.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":9182,"output":313,"cacheRead":211204,"cacheWrite":691,"totalTokens":221390,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783244914907,"responseId":"msg_6a15165b-9de1-4e38-acc3-376830e536c2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7079d3a","parentId":"3650be87","timestamp":"2026-07-05T09:48:59.268Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_5113a7dd4a7043cba558dc2c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/slow-shutter').then(function(r) {\r\n        var sel = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\r\n        if (!sel) return;\r\n        if (!r || !r.success || !r.data) { sel.disabled = true; return; }\r\n        var d = r.data;\r\n        if (!d.supported) { sel.disabled = true; return; }\r\n        sel.disabled = false;\r\n        var ratios = [0, 1.25, 2, 4, 8];\r\n        sel.innerHTML = '';\r\n        ratios.forEach(function(ratio) {\r\n            var opt = document.createElement('option');\r\n            opt.value = ratio;\r\n            opt.textContent = ratio === 0 ? '关闭' : ratio + 'x';\r\n            if (Math.abs((d.ratio || 1) - ratio) < 0.01) opt.selected = true;\r\n            sel.appendChild(opt);\r\n        });\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    var ratio = parseFloat(val);\r\n    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/slow-shutter', { ratio: ratio }).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            showToast('success', r.message);\r\n            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\n[422 more lines in file. Use offset=1579 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783244939268}}
