{"type":"message","id":"f4a6c4a1","parentId":"d53a20bb","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:09:19.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nNow I need to verify the router.py changes were applied correctly. Let me check the slow-shutter endpoints in the modified router.py.\n验证router.py修改：\n...\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a8073cf8dd554280b1891350","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":3667,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\n...\n用户要求继续执行修复任务。我已经：\n1. ✅ 修改了function.py中的P4.6定义（改为DSS端点）\n2. ✅ 修改了router.py中的慢快门API（使用DSS端点）\n\n现在需要：\n3. 修改console.html中的loadSlowShutter函数，从function.json读取opt_values而不是API实时获取\n4. 执行功能测试脚本更新function.json\n5. 重启服务验证\n\n让我继续修改console.html。\n现在修改console.html中的loadSlowShutter函数，从function.json读取opt_values：router.py已更新。继续修改console.html中的loadSlowShutter，从function.json读取opt_values：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_8b1757ffd00f40509e5ae3f2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\npath = r'astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html'\nwith open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\nold = '''function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/slow-shutter').then(function(r) {\n        var sel = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n        if (!sel) return;\n        if (!r || !r.success || !r.data) { sel.disabled = true; return; }\n        var d = r.data;\n        if (!d.supported) { sel.disabled = true; return; }\n        sel.disabled = false;\n        var ratios = [0, 1.25, 2, 4, 8];\n        sel.innerHTML = '';\n        ratios.forEach(function(ratio) {\n            var opt = document.createElement('option');\n            opt.value = ratio;\n            opt.textContent = ratio === 0 ? '关闭' : ratio + 'x';\n            if (Math.abs((d.ratio || 1) - ratio) < 0.01) opt.selected = true;\n            sel.appendChild(opt);\n        });\n    });\n}\n\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    var ratio = parseFloat(val);\n    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/slow-shutter', { ratio: ratio }).then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            showToast('success', r.message);\n            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\n        }\n    });\n}'''\n\nnew = '''function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {\n    var sel = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n    if (!sel) return;\n    \n    // 从function.json读取DSS支持倍率\n    if (!deviceFunctionData || !deviceFunctionData.functions || !deviceFunctionData.functions.slow_shutter) {\n        sel.disabled = true;\n        sel.innerHTML = '<option value=\\\"\\\">设备不支持</option>';\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    var dss = deviceFunctionData.functions.slow_shutter;\n    if (!dss.supported) {\n        sel.disabled = true;\n        sel.innerHTML = '<option value=\\\"\\\">设备不支持</option>';\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    sel.disabled = false;\n    sel.innerHTML = '';\n    \n    // 添加\\\"关闭\\\"选项\n    var offOpt = document.createElement('option');\n    offOpt.value = 'off';\n    offOpt.textContent = '关闭';\n    sel.appendChild(offOpt);\n    \n    // 从opt_values添加倍率选项\n    if (dss.opt_values && Array.isArray(dss.opt_values)) {\n        dss.opt_values.forEach(function(level) {\n            var opt = document.createElement('option');\n            opt.value = level;\n            opt.textContent = level;\n            sel.appendChild(opt);\n        });\n    }\n    \n    // 获取当前DSS状态并设置选中项\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/slow-shutter').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            if (r.data.enabled && r.data.dss_level) {\n                sel.value = r.data.dss_level;\n            } else {\n                sel.value = 'off';\n            }\n        }\n    });\n}\n\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/slow-shutter', { dss_level: val }).then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            showToast('success', r.message);\n            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\n        }\n    });\n}'''\n\nif old in content:\n    content = content.replace(old, new)\n    with open(path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(content)\n    print('console.html loadSlowShutter replaced')\nelse:\n    print('Pattern not found')\n    # Try to find the function\n    idx = content.find('function loadSlowShutter')\n    if idx >= 0:\n        print('Found at', idx)\n        print('Content:', repr(content[idx:idx+200]))\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":7044,"output":1356,"cacheRead":231312,"cacheWrite":143,"totalTokens":239855,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246119799,"responseId":"msg_c5825fee-03d7-4d0e-a28e-6a6b337469a6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac010420","parentId":"f4a6c4a1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:09:19.997Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_a8073cf8dd554280b1891350","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# === 慢快门 DSS (v8.45) ===\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"获取慢快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_slow_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    mgr = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取DSS失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        enabled = False\r\n        dss_level = \"\"\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"enabled\":\r\n                enabled = (elem.text or \"\").strip().lower() == \"true\"\r\n            elif tag == \"DSSLevel\":\r\n                dss_level = (elem.text or \"\").strip()\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"data\": {\"supported\": True, \"enabled\": enabled, \"dss_level\": dss_level}}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取DSS异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter\", summary=\"设置慢快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_slow_shutter(device_id: str, body: dict) -> dict:\r\n    mgr = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    dss_level = body.get(\"dss_level\", \"\")\r\n    try:\r\n        if dss_level == \"off\":\r\n            enabled = \"false\"\r\n            level_str = \"*1\"\r\n        else:\r\n            enabled = \"true\"\r\n            level_str = dss_level\r\n        xml_str = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>' + chr(10) + '<DSS version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">' + chr(10) + '  <enabled>' + enabled + '</enabled>' + chr(10) + '  <DSSLevel>' + level_str + '</DSSLevel>' + chr(10) + '</DSS>'\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"dss\", {\"device\": device_id, \"level\": dss_level})\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"慢快门: \" + (\"关闭\" if dss_level == \"off\" else dss_level)}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置DSS异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/osd/ptz\", summary=\"获取PTZ OSD状态\", tags=[\"OSD\"])\r\nasync def get_osd_ptz(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取PTZ OSD显示状态。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        ch = getattr(client, 'channel', 1)\r\n\n[513 more lines in file. Use offset=3747 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783246159997}}
{"type":"message","id":"0108b782","parentId":"ac010420","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:09:19.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_8b1757ffd00f40509e5ae3f2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"File \"<string>\", line 38\r\n    new = '''function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {\r\n          ^\r\nSyntaxError: unterminated triple-quoted string literal (detected at line 45)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":395,"aggregated":"File \"<string>\", line 38\r\n    new = '''function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {\r\n          ^\r\nSyntaxError: unterminated triple-quoted string literal (detected at line 45)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783246159997}}
{"type":"message","id":"6236d490","parentId":"0108b782","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:09:51.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Python inline script has issues with the triple quotes and escaping. I need to use a Python script file instead. Let me write a Python script to modify the console.html file.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"需要用脚本文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_afb167d2d89a45a298310296","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Replace loadSlowShutter in console.html to read from function.json\"\"\"\npath = r'astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html'\nwith open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Find the loadSlowShutter function\nstart_marker = 'function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {'\nend_marker = '}'  # Will find the matching closing brace\n\nstart_idx = content.find(start_marker)\nif start_idx < 0:\n    print('loadSlowShutter not found')\n    exit(1)\n\n# Find the setSlowShutter function end\nset_start = content.find('function setSlowShutter(val) {', start_idx)\nif set_start < 0:\n    print('setSlowShutter not found')\n    exit(1)\n\n# Find the end of setSlowShutter\nbrace_count = 0\nend_idx = set_start\nfor i in range(set_start, len(content)):\n    if content[i] == '{':\n        brace_count += 1\n    elif content[i] == '}':\n        brace_count -= 1\n        if brace_count == 0:\n            end_idx = i + 1\n            break\n\n# Also remove the newline after\nwhile end_idx < len(content) and content[end_idx] in '\\r\\n':\n    end_idx += 1\n\nold_section = content[start_idx:end_idx]\nprint(f'Found old section: {len(old_section)} chars')\n\nnew_section = '''function loadSlowShutter(deviceIp) {\n    var sel = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n    if (!sel) return;\n    \n    // v8.45: 从function.json读取DSS支持倍率\n    if (!deviceFunctionData || !deviceFunctionData.functions || !deviceFunctionData.functions.slow_shutter) {\n        sel.disabled = true;\n        sel.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">设备不支持</option>';\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    var dss = deviceFunctionData.functions.slow_shutter;\n    if (!dss.supported) {\n        sel.disabled = true;\n        sel.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">设备不支持</option>';\n        return;\n    }\n    \n    sel.disabled = false;\n    sel.innerHTML = '';\n    \n    // 添加\"关闭\"选项\n    var offOpt = document.createElement('option');\n    offOpt.value = 'off';\n    offOpt.textContent = '关闭';\n    sel.appendChild(offOpt);\n    \n    // 从opt_values添加倍率选项\n    if (dss.opt_values && Array.isArray(dss.opt_values)) {\n        dss.opt_values.forEach(function(level) {\n            var opt = document.createElement('option');\n            opt.value = level;\n            opt.textContent = level;\n            sel.appendChild(opt);\n        });\n    }\n    \n    // 获取当前DSS状态并设置选中项\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/slow-shutter').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            if (r.data.enabled && r.data.dss_level) {\n                sel.value = r.data.dss_level;\n            } else {\n                sel.value = 'off';\n            }\n        }\n    });\n}\n\nfunction setSlowShutter(val) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/slow-shutter', { dss_level: val }).then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            showToast('success', r.message);\n            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('慢快门: ' + r.message, 'success');\n        }\n    });\n}\n'''\n\ncontent = content[:start_idx] + new_section + content[end_idx:]\nwith open(path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint('console.html loadSlowShutter/setSlowShutter replaced')\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\fix_console.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":9203,"output":999,"cacheRead":231455,"cacheWrite":384,"totalTokens":242041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246160005,"responseId":"msg_5d533356-91f9-466f-8303-d2aa87961710"}}
