{"type":"message","id":"1c307a5f","parentId":"6e342c4d","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:12:59.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue. Let me check what modes are currently handled in the function.py detection logic. I see that there are modes like \"numeric\", \"toggle\", \"action_switch\", \"shutter\", \"iris\", etc. But I don't see an \"enum\" mode handler.\n\nThe P4.6 slow_shutter was changed to \"mode\": \"enum\", but the detection logic doesn't have an enum handler. I need to add one.\n\nBut wait, let me re-read the requirements:\n1. Add full /Image/channels/1/capabilities test to function.py\n2. Write full capabilities info to function.json\n3. Console slow shutter reads from function.json\n4. Check what other controls need capability-based detection\n\nLet me check what's already there and what needs to be done. Let me look at the current state of things more carefully.\n\nActually, let me re-read the user's original request:\n- Task 1: Add full /Image/channels/1/capabilities test\n- Task 2: Write full info to function.json\n- Task 3: Console slow shutter reads from function.json\n- Task 4: Check what other controls need capability-based detection\n\nAnd the boss said:\n- Keep white balance as is\n- Fix the rest according to plan\n- Don't over-develop\n- Backup and iterate\n\nSo the key thing is: the capabilities endpoint returns opt values for each field. The current function.py already has some capability reading (like shutter, iris), but we need to make sure the slow_shutter (DSS) detection works properly.\n\nLet me look at how the detection currently works for P4.6. The P4.6 was \"read_only\" mode, now it should be \"enum\" mode. But I need to check if the detection code handles this.\n\nActually, looking at the code more carefully, I see that the detection code already has logic for different modes. The \"enum\" mode I defined doesn't exist yet. I need to either:\n1. Add an \"enum\" mode handler\n2. Or reuse an existing mode\n\nSince the DSS endpoint has two fields (enabled and DSSLevel), it's actually more complex than a simple enum. Let me think about this differently.\n\nThe DSS XML structure is:\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\nAnd the capabilities endpoint returns:\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled opt=\"true,false\">true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel opt=\"*1.25,*1.5,*2,*3,*4,*6,*8\">*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Parse the DSS capabilities to get the opt values for DSSLevel\n2. Store this in function.json\n3. The frontend reads from function.json\n\nBut actually, looking at the current detection logic, it seems like the code already handles parsing opt values from capabilities. Let me check how it does this for other endpoints.\n\nActually, I think the simplest approach is to:\n1. Keep P4.6 as a simple read endpoint that just reads the current DSS state and supported levels\n2. The frontend reads from function.json\n\nBut the current P4.6 definition uses \"mode\": \"enum\" which doesn't have a handler. Let me check what happens when a mode doesn't have a handler.\n\nActually, let me just run the function detection and see what happens. If it fails, I'll add the handler.\n\nBut wait, I should be more careful. Let me check the full detection flow first.\n\nActually, let me just focus on what the user wants:\n1. The slow_shutter in function.json should have the correct opt_values from capabilities\n2. The frontend reads these opt_values\n\nLet me check if the current detection code can handle this. Let me look at how opt_values are populated.\n\nLooking at the code, I see that `_fetch_capabilities_opt_values` is called to get opt values. But it's called per-key. For DSS, we need to get the opt values for DSSLevel.\n\nLet me check the current state of the detection code and see if it handles the DSS endpoint properly.\n\nActually, I think the issue is that the P4.6 definition uses \"mode\": \"enum\" but there's no handler for \"enum\" mode. Let me add one.\n\nLet me read the full detection code to understand the flow better.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我先读取完整的function.py探测逻辑，了解当前的实现：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9239ea5a0d8d4bc191a8f275","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":650,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":5863,"output":1061,"cacheRead":236812,"cacheWrite":1490,"totalTokens":245226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246335319,"responseId":"msg_93758151-76d6-4277-8875-0471102264b2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c847747","parentId":"1c307a5f","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:12:59.709Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_9239ea5a0d8d4bc191a8f275","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            self._results[item_key] = result\r\n            self._write_config(result)\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        # ---- Step 1: GET 端点检查是否存在 ----\r\n        response = self._probe_endpoint(endpoint)\r\n        if response.status_code != 200:\r\n            result.supported = False\r\n            result.error = f\"HTTP {response.status_code}\"\r\n            self._results[item_key] = result\r\n            self._write_config(result)\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        # ---- Step 2: 读取当前值,保存原始 XML ----\r\n        try:\r\n            root = ET.fromstring(response.xml)\r\n            self._original_xml[item_key] = response.xml  # 保存原始 XML\r\n\r\n            # 解析当前值\r\n            if mode == \"multi_field\":\r\n                result.current_values = self._parse_all_values(\r\n                    root, cap_def[\"test_keys\"]\r\n                )\r\n            else:\r\n                val = self._parse_xml_value(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\r\n                result.current_values = {cap_def[\"test_key\"]: val}\r\n\r\n            # 解析取值范围 (如果不是 read_only 模式)\r\n            if mode != \"read_only\":\r\n                # v7.08: 对于 shutter/iris 模式，尝试从 capabilities 获取 opt 值\r\n                # v7.52: exposure_mode 分离处理，直接使用 test_values\r\n                if mode in (\"shutter\", \"iris\"):\r\n                    opt_values = self._fetch_capabilities_opt_values(endpoint, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\r\n                    if opt_values:\r\n                        result.opt_values = opt_values\r\n                        result.min_val = opt_values[0] if opt_values else cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n                        result.max_val = opt_values[-1] if opt_values else cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 100)\r\n                    else:\r\n                        min_range, max_range = self._parse_range(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\r\n                        if min_range == 0 and max_range == 100:\r\n                            min_range = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n                            max_range = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 100)\r\n                        result.min_val = min_range\r\n                        result.max_val = max_range\r\n                elif mode == \"exposure_mode\":\r\n                    # 字符串选项型：直接使用 test_values（ISAPI 定义的 ExposureType 可选值）\r\n                    result.opt_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [])\r\n                else:\r\n                    min_range, max_range = self._parse_range(root, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\r\n                    # XML 中没有找到范围则用 CSV 定义的\r\n                    if min_range == 0 and max_range == 100:\r\n                        min_range = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n                        max_range = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 100)\r\n                    result.min_val = min_range\r\n                    result.max_val = max_range\r\n            else:\r\n                result.min_val = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n                result.max_val = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 0)\r\n\r\n        except ET.ParseError:\r\n            result.supported = False\r\n            result.error = \"XML 解析失败\"\r\n            self._original_xml[item_key] = response.xml\r\n            result.min_val = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n            result.max_val = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 100)\r\n            self._results[item_key] = result\r\n            self._write_config(result)\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        # ---- Step 3 & 4: 执行修改测试 ----\r\n        if mode == \"read_only\":\r\n            # P4.6 慢快门: 仅读取,不PUT\r\n            result.test_results.append({\"action\": \"read_only\", \"success\": True})\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"numeric\":\r\n            # 数值型: PUT 测试值\r\n            test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", 50)\r\n            success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)\r\n            result.test_results.append({\r\n                \"value\": test_val,\r\n                \"success\": success,\r\n                \"range\": f\"{result.min_val}~{result.max_val}\",\r\n            })\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"multi_field\":\r\n            # 多字段型 (whiteBalance: Red=200 + Blue=200)\r\n            test_keys = cap_def[\"test_keys\"]\r\n            test_desc = \", \".join(f\"{k}={v}\" for k, v in test_keys.items())\r\n            success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, None, item_key)\r\n            result.test_results.append({\r\n                \"values\": test_desc,\r\n                \"success\": success,\r\n                \"range\": f\"{result.min_val}~{result.max_val}\",\r\n            })\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"style_switch\":\r\n            # 风格切换型 (Focus/噪声/镜像): PUT 各个模式值\r\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [])\r\n            for val in test_values:\r\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\r\n\n[486 more lines in file. Use offset=750 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783246379709}}
{"type":"message","id":"0814feed","parentId":"1c847747","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:13:58.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求继续。我已经完成了以下修改：\n\n1. ✅ function.py - P4.6改为DSS端点（endpoint: /Image/channels/{ch}/DSS, mode: \"enum\"）\n2. ✅ router.py - 慢快门API改为DSS端点\n3. ✅ console.html - loadSlowShutter改为从function.json读取\n\n现在的问题是：P4.6的mode被我改成了\"enum\"，但function.py中没有\"enum\" mode的handler。当前只有以下modes有handler：\n- read_only\n- numeric\n- multi_field\n- style_switch\n- toggle\n- action_switch\n- focus_continuous\n- shutter\n- iris\n- exposure_mode\n\n我需要添加\"enum\" mode的handler。但实际上，DSS慢快门的功能逻辑和shutter/iris类似——它需要：\n1. 从capabilities读取opt值\n2. PUT测试值\n\n最简单的方法是复用shutter的逻辑，或者添加一个enum handler。\n\n考虑到用户要求\"禁止过度开发\"和\"禁止新增脚本\"，我应该最小化修改。\n\n实际上，最好的方式是：把P4.6的mode改为\"enum\"（或类似），并在探测逻辑中添加对enum的处理。但更简单的方式是：直接复用shutter的逻辑。\n\n不过shutter的逻辑有一个问题：它通过_capabilities端点获取opt值，而DSS也应该这样。\n\n让我看看shutter是怎么获取opt值的...\n\n从代码看：\n```python\nif mode in (\"shutter\", \"iris\"):\n    opt_values = self._fetch_capabilities_opt_values(endpoint, cap_def[\"test_key\"])\n    if opt_values:\n        result.opt_values = opt_values\n        ...\n```\n\n但_fetch_capabilities_opt_values方法构造的cap_endpoint是：\n```python\nif \"/Image/channels/\" in endpoint_base:\n    cap_endpoint = \"/Image/channels/\" + str(self.channel) + \"/capabilities\"\n```\n\n所以它会调用 `/Image/channels/1/capabilities`，并从中解析出指定key的opt值。\n\n对于DSS，key是\"DSSLevel\"。cap_endpoint是 `/Image/channels/1/capabilities`。\n这个方法会遍历capabilities XML，找到所有匹配key的元素的opt属性。\n\n问题是：cap XML返回的是整个ImageChannel的capabilities，包括DSS节点。`_parse_opt_values`方法会遍历所有元素，找到匹配的key。\n\n所以实际上，如果mode是\"shutter\"或\"iris\"，`_fetch_capabilities_opt_values`会从capabilities XML中解析opt值。\n\n那我可以把P4.6的mode改为\"shutter\"（复用shutter的逻辑），或者把\"enum\"添加到shutter/iris的if条件中。\n\n但实际上DSS和shutter不同：shutter的test_value是字符串（如\"1/100\"），而DSS的test_value也是字符串（如\"*8\"）。所以它们可以共用shutter的PUT测试逻辑。\n\n但是有个问题：shutter模式的PUT逻辑是什么？让我看看 `_test_value` 方法。\n\n实际上，shutter的PUT逻辑是：发送包含ShutterLevel的XML。但DSS的XML格式是：\n```xml\n<DSS version=\"2.0\" ...>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n所以直接复用shutter的 `_test_value` 可能不行，因为test_value是\"*8\"，而endpoint是\"/Image/channels/1/DSS\"，需要发送包含enabled和DSSLevel的完整XML。\n\n但等等，shutter模式的test_value只是一个值，`_test_value`可能会构建一个简单的XML：\n```xml\n<Shutter>\n  <ShutterLevel>1/100</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>\n```\n\n但DSS需要的是：\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n所以直接复用可能不行。我需要么：\n1. 添加一个enum mode handler，构建完整的DSS XML\n2. 或者修改_test_value方法来支持DSS格式\n\n最简单的方法是：把P4.6的mode改回\"read_only\"，然后在capabilities探测完成后，额外读取DSS的capabilities来填充opt_values。\n\n或者更简单的：由于我现在的function.py中P4.6的mode已经是\"enum\"了，我需要在探测逻辑中添加enum handler。\n\n让我写一个最小化的enum handler：\n1. GET endpoint获取当前值\n2. GET capabilities获取opt_values\n3. PUT test_value测试\n4. 恢复原始值\n\n让我检查_test_value方法的实现...\n\n实际上，让我直接看看_test_value方法怎么写的，然后决定如何最小化修改。\n\n等等，我应该先完成用户要求的核心任务。让我重新理解一下：\n\n用户要求：\n1. ✅ function.py中加入完整的capabilities测试\n2. ✅ 全量信息写入function.json\n3. 主控台慢快门从本地文件读取（已完成console.html修改）\n4. 全面复查其他控件\n\n当前阻塞点是：P4.6的mode是\"enum\"，但function.py中没有enum handler。\n\n最简单的修复：把P4.6的mode改为\"shutter\"（因为DSS和shutter都是类似的PUT单个值到endpoint），或者添加一个小的enum handler。\n\n我选择：添加enum handler，因为它只修改function.py，且改动很小。但如果太复杂，就改为\"shutter\" mode并修改_test_value来支持。\n\n让我先看_test_value的实现...\n\n实际上，让我直接运行一下看看会发生什么。如果报\"Unknown mode: enum\"错误，我就添加handler。\n\n或者我可以直接添加一个最小化的enum handler。\n\n考虑到用户说\"禁止过度开发\"，我应该最小化修改。让我看看shutter的逻辑是否可以直接复用。\n\nshutter的PUT逻辑：`_test_value` 方法发送包含test_key的XML到endpoint。\n\n对于DSS：\n- endpoint: /Image/channels/1/DSS\n- test_key: DSSLevel\n- test_value: \"*8\"\n\n`_test_value` 构建的XML可能是：\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n但这样缺少了enabled字段！DSS的PUT需要同时设置enabled和DSSLevel。\n\n所以shutter的逻辑不能直接复用。我需要么：\n1. 修改_test_value来支持同时设置多个字段\n2. 或者为DSS添加特殊的PUT逻辑\n\n最简单的方法：在enum handler中，手动构建包含enabled和DSSLevel的XML。\n\n让我看一下`_test_value`方法的实现...\n\n实际上，让我先读取完整的_test_value方法。\n\n不，我应该直接添加一个enum handler，并在其中手动处理DSS的特殊情况。\n\nOK，让我直接修改function.py，添加enum mode handler。\n\nenum handler的逻辑：\n1. 从test_values获取所有值（如 [\"*1.25\", \"*1.5\", \"*2\", ...]）\n2. 对每个值，PUT完整的DSS XML\n3. 记录测试结果\n\n但问题是：PUT时，enabled应该设为true（因为我们要开启慢快门），然后DSSLevel设为对应的倍率。\n\n所以完整的PUT XML应该是：\n```xml\n<DSS version=\"2.0\" ...>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n让我添加一个enum handler。\n\n实际上，为了最小化修改，我可以把P4.6的mode改为类似\"shutter\"的方式，但自定义PUT逻辑。\n\n或者更简单：直接在function.py中添加enum handler，并让它调用`_test_value`。如果`_test_value`不工作，我再手动构建XML。\n\n让我先看看`_test_value`的实现。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我需要添加enum mode的handler，因为DSS需要特殊的PUT逻辑。让我先看看`_test_value`方法的实现：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:250","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py\" -Pattern \"def _test_value\" -Context 0,20 | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":225999,"output":1681,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":227680,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246379714,"responseId":"cht000de9e0@dx19f31c48c702871503"}}
