{"type":"message","id":"7f88d349","parentId":"c28c7b8d","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:14:49.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\n我需要查看 `_test_value` 方法的实现，了解它如何测试值。然后我需要：\n\n1. 为 P4.6 DSS 慢快门添加测试逻辑\n2. 确保它能从 capabilities 端点获取 opt_values\n3. 确保测试能正确写入 function.json\n\n让我先看看 _test_value 方法的实现。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_53e2d8c20a7840808b3ad682","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":536,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":212091,"output":152,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":212243,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246439039,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4a3b2b38-e768-9d31-9b29-872c7991c956"}}
{"type":"message","id":"46e96633","parentId":"7f88d349","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:14:49.394Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_53e2d8c20a7840808b3ad682","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def _test_value(self, cap_def: dict, endpoint: str, value: Any, item_key: str = \"\") -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"测试单个值是否可设置 (PUT + 范围验证)。\"\"\"\r\n        original = self._original_xml.get(item_key, \"\")\r\n        if not original:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n        xml_body = self._build_xml_from_template(original, cap_def, value)\r\n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml_body)\r\n        if result.status_code != 200:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n        # Verification step: GET endpoint again and verify value matches\r\n        verify_response = self.client.get(endpoint)\r\n        if verify_response.status_code != 200:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n        try:\r\n            verify_root = ET.fromstring(verify_response.xml)\r\n            key = cap_def.get(\"test_key\", \"\")\r\n            if not key:\r\n                return True  # multi_field mode, skip single value check\r\n\r\n            actual_value = self._parse_xml_value(verify_root, key)\r\n\r\n            # Check range correctness\r\n            # For iris mode: use cap_def range_min/range_max (discrete values)\r\n            min_range = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n            max_range = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 100)\r\n            \r\n            if isinstance(actual_value, (int, float)) and isinstance(min_range, int) and isinstance(max_range, int):\r\n                if min_range <= actual_value <= max_range:\r\n                    # Step 5b: Restore original value\r\n                    if original:\r\n                        restore_result = self.client.put(endpoint, original)\r\n                        if restore_result.status_code != 200:\r\n                            return False\r\n                        # Verify restore\r\n                        verify_restore = self.client.get(endpoint)\r\n                        if verify_restore.status_code != 200:\r\n                            return False\r\n                        try:\r\n                            restore_root = ET.fromstring(verify_restore.xml)\r\n                            restored_key_val = self._parse_xml_value(restore_root, key)\r\n                            original_key_val = self._parse_xml_value(ET.fromstring(original), key)\r\n                            if restored_key_val != original_key_val:\r\n                                # For string/toggle values, accept restored to original\r\n                                pass  # Accept if GET returns 200 after restore\r\n                        except ET.ParseError:\r\n                            pass  # Accept restore if GET succeeds\r\n                    return True\r\n                # Value outside parsed range = failure\r\n                return False\r\n\r\n            return True  # String/toggle values pass on successful PUT\r\n        except ET.ParseError:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n    def _test_values(self, cap_def: dict, endpoint: str, test_values: list, item_key: str = \"\") -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"测试多个值(用于 style_switch / toggle / action_switch 模式)。\"\"\"\r\n        results = []\r\n\n[640 more lines in file. Use offset=596 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783246489394}}
{"type":"message","id":"be2f5b17","parentId":"46e96633","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:15:10.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n好的，我理解了。`_test_value` 方法的工作流程是：\n1. 获取原始 XML\n2. 构建新的 XML（使用 `_build_xml_from_template`）\n3. PUT 到 endpoint\n4. 验证 GET 返回的值\n5. 恢复原始值\n\n对于 DSS 模式，我需要：\n1. 添加 enum 模式的处理逻辑\n2. 在探测阶段从 capabilities 获取 opt_values\n3. 在测试阶段，对每个测试值调用 `_test_value`\n\n但是 `_test_value` 使用的 `_build_xml_from_template` 方法需要支持 DSS 的特殊结构（enabled + DSSLevel）。\n\n让我看看 `_build_xml_from_template` 方法...","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n让我看看 `_build_xml_from_template` 方法，了解它如何构建 XML：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a8865c7b2e364bb3a221a297","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":490,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":7066,"output":253,"cacheRead":238302,"cacheWrite":3733,"totalTokens":249354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246489399,"responseId":"msg_ef6648ea-c80e-4fb9-b497-7e1642c33a0f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ac2f4d0","parentId":"be2f5b17","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:15:10.166Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_a8865c7b2e364bb3a221a297","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        重要:海康设备不接受带命名空间前缀的XML(如 ns0:),\r\n        所以必须使用正则替换而非 ET.tostring()。\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        import re\r\n\r\n        key = cap_def.get(\"test_key\", \"\")\r\n\r\n        # 单字段模式:用正则替换值\r\n        if \"test_keys\" not in cap_def:\r\n            # 匹配 <key>原值</key>\r\n            pattern = rf\"(<{key}>)[^<]*(</{key}>)\"\r\n            if re.search(pattern, original_xml, re.IGNORECASE):\r\n                new_xml = re.sub(pattern, rf\"\\g<1>{value}\\g<2>\", original_xml, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\r\n                return new_xml\r\n            # 尝试带命名空间的匹配:<ns:key>原值</ns:key>\r\n            pattern_ns = rf\"(<[\\w]+:{key}>)[^<]*(</[\\w]+:{key}>)\"\r\n            if re.search(pattern_ns, original_xml, re.IGNORECASE):\r\n                new_xml = re.sub(pattern_ns, rf\"\\g<1>{value}\\g<2>\", original_xml, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\r\n                return new_xml\r\n        else:\r\n            # 多字段模式\r\n            new_xml = original_xml\r\n            for k, v in cap_def[\"test_keys\"].items():\r\n                pattern = rf\"(<{k}>)[^<]*(</{k}>)\"\r\n                if re.search(pattern, new_xml, re.IGNORECASE):\r\n                    new_xml = re.sub(pattern, rf\"\\g<1>{v}\\g<2>\", new_xml, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\r\n            return new_xml\r\n\r\n        # 备用方案:直接返回原始XML\r\n        return original_xml\r\n\r\n    def _restore_single(self, item_key: str) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"恢复单个端点的原始 XML 值。\"\"\"\r\n        original = self._original_xml.get(item_key, \"\")\r\n        if not original:\r\n            return True  # 未修改过\r\n\r\n        cap_def = FUNCTION_ENDPOINTS.get(item_key)\r\n        if not cap_def:\r\n            return True\r\n\r\n        endpoint = self._endpoint(cap_def)\r\n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, original)\r\n        return result.status_code == 200\r\n\r\n    def _test_value(self, cap_def: dict, endpoint: str, value: Any, item_key: str = \"\") -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"测试单个值是否可设置 (PUT + 范围验证)。\"\"\"\r\n        original = self._original_xml.get(item_key, \"\")\r\n        if not original:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n        xml_body = self._build_xml_from_template(original, cap_def, value)\r\n        result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml_body)\r\n        if result.status_code != 200:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n        # Verification step: GET endpoint again and verify value matches\r\n        verify_response = self.client.get(endpoint)\r\n        if verify_response.status_code != 200:\r\n            return False\r\n\r\n        try:\r\n            verify_root = ET.fromstring(verify_response.xml)\r\n            key = cap_def.get(\"test_key\", \"\")\r\n            if not key:\r\n                return True  # multi_field mode, skip single value check\r\n\r\n            actual_value = self._parse_xml_value(verify_root, key)\r\n\r\n            # Check range correctness\r\n            # For iris mode: use cap_def range_min/range_max (discrete values)\r\n            min_range = cap_def.get(\"range_min\", 0)\r\n            max_range = cap_def.get(\"range_max\", 100)\r\n            \r\n            if isinstance(actual_value, (int, float)) and isinstance(min_range, int) and isinstance(max_range, int):\r\n                if min_range <= actual_value <= max_range:\r\n                    # Step 5b: Restore original value\r\n                    if original:\r\n                        restore_result = self.client.put(endpoint, original)\r\n\n[666 more lines in file. Use offset=570 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783246510166}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d06db47","parentId":"6ac2f4d0","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:16:22.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在理解了整个流程：\n\n1. `_build_xml_from_template` 使用原始XML，然后通过正则替换key的值\n2. 对于DSS，原始XML是：\n```xml\n<DSS>\n  <enabled>true</enabled>\n  <DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>\n</DSS>\n```\n\n3. 如果要测试DSSLevel=\"*4\"，它会替换 `<DSSLevel>*8</DSSLevel>` 为 `<DSSLevel>*4</DSSLevel>`\n\n4. 问题：DSS需要enabled=true才能生效。如果当前enabled=false，测试会失败。\n\n5. 解决方案：在enum模式的测试逻辑中，需要先设置enabled=true，然后再测试DSSLevel。\n\n但是，`_build_xml_from_template` 只替换test_key的值，不会修改enabled字段。\n\n我需要为enum模式添加特殊的处理逻辑：\n- 测试前：确保enabled=true\n- 测试DSSLevel\n- 恢复：恢复原始XML\n\n让我看看当前的探测流程（Step 3 & 4）中enum模式应该如何处理。\n\n实际上，我看到当前代码中还没有enum模式的处理逻辑。我需要添加它。\n\n让我添加enum模式的处理：\n\n```python\nelif mode == \"enum\":\n    # 枚举型 (DSS: 慢快门倍率)\n    test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [])\n    for val in test_values:\n        success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\n        result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})\n```\n\n但是有个问题：如果当前enabled=false，测试DSSLevel会失败。\n\n\n我可以在测试前设置enabled=true。最简单的方法是修改测试流程，在enum模式测试前确保enabled为true。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n好的，我理解了。`_build_xml_from_template` 使用正则替换原始XML中key的值。对于DSS，它只会替换 `<DSSLevel>` 的值，但不会修改 `<enabled>` 字段。\n\n问题是：如果当前enabled=false，测试DSSLevel会失败。\n\n我需要为enum模式添加特殊的处理逻辑。让我先看看当前的探测流程中是否有处理这种情况的代码：\n...\n\n...\n好的，我理解了。现在我需要为enum模式添加探测逻辑。DSS的问题是：\n1. 如果当前enabled=false，测试DSSLevel会失败\n2. 需要在测试前设置enabled=true\n\n让我修改function.py，添加enum模式的处理逻辑：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ee1915eb7019498aa922d990","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":750,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":7959,"output":609,"cacheRead":242035,"cacheWrite":220,"totalTokens":250823,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246510172,"responseId":"msg_6ca6de73-08f6-4e47-ba1e-0055e5cca904"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3100e822","parentId":"2d06db47","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:16:22.990Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ee1915eb7019498aa922d990","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"toggle\":\r\n            # 布尔切换型 (BLC: true/false)\r\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [\"true\", \"false\"])\r\n            for val in test_values:\r\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\r\n                result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"action_switch\":\r\n            # 动作切换型 (IRCUT: day/night)\r\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [\"night\", \"day\"])\r\n            for val in test_values:\r\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\r\n                result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"focus_continuous\":\r\n            # Focus+/- 控制: 通过 PTZ continuous 端点\r\n            # XML格式: <PTZData><pan>0</pan><tilt>0</tilt><zoom>0</zoom><focus>5</focus></PTZData>\r\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [\"5\", \"-5\", \"0\"])\r\n            for val in test_values:\r\n                # 构建 PTZ XML\r\n                xml_body = f\"<PTZData><pan>0</pan><tilt>0</tilt><zoom>0</zoom><focus>{val}</focus></PTZData>\"\r\n                put_result = self.client.put(endpoint, xml_body)\r\n                success = put_result.status_code == 200\r\n                result.test_results.append({\"value\": f\"focus={val}\", \"success\": success})\r\n                # focus=0 停止后继续\r\n                if val == \"0\":\r\n                    break\r\n\r\n        elif mode == \"shutter\":\r\n            # 快门型: PUT shutter string value\r\n            test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", \"1/100\")\r\n            success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)\r\n            result.test_results.append({\r\n                \"value\": test_val,\r\n                \"success\": success,\r\n                \"range\": f\"{result.min_val}~{result.max_val}\",\r\n            })\r\n        \r\n        elif mode == \"iris\":\r\n            # 光圈型: 使用PUT绝对值设置IrisLevel\r\n            # 光圈值是离散值: [160, 200, 240, 280, 340, 400, 480, 560, 680, 960, 1100, 1400, 1600, 1900, 2200]\r\n            # 数值越大光圈越小: 160=F1.6(最大光圈), 2200=F22(最小光圈)\r\n            # 公式: F数值 = IrisLevel / 100\r\n            \r\n            # 1. 测试切换到test_value\r\n            test_val = cap_def.get(\"test_value\", 160)\r\n            success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, test_val, item_key)\r\n            result.test_results.append({\r\n\n[436 more lines in file. Use offset=800 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783246582990}}
{"type":"message","id":"47183c84","parentId":"3100e822","timestamp":"2026-07-05T10:17:05.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\n好的，我看到了现有的测试逻辑。现在我需要：\n\n1. 为enum模式添加测试逻辑（在toggle和action_switch之间或之后）\n2. 特殊处理DSS：如果当前enabled=false，需要先设置为true，然后测试DSSLevel\n3. 在测试完成后恢复原始状态\n\n让我为enum模式添加特殊的处理逻辑：\n\n```python\nelif mode == \"enum\":\n    # 枚举型 (DSS: 慢快门倍率)\n    # DSS需要先确保enabled=true\n    test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [])\n    \n    # 1. 获取当前XML\n    original = self._original_xml.get(item_key, \"\")\n    \n    # 2. 如果enabled=false，先设置为true\n    import re\n    if '<enabled>false</enabled>' in original.lower():\n        enable_xml = re.sub(\n            r'(<enabled>)[^<]*(</enabled>)',\n            r'\\g<1>true\\g<2>',\n            original,\n            flags=re.IGNORECASE\n        )\n        self.client.put(endpoint, enable_xml)\n    \n    # 3. 测试每个DSSLevel值\n    for val in test_values:\n        success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\n        result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})\n    \n    # 4. 恢复原始状态（_test_value会自动恢复）\n```\n\n但是有个问题：`_test_value` 会使用原始XML来恢复，所以如果原始enabled=false，它会在每个测试后恢复为false。\n我需要确保：\n1. 测试前：设置enabled=true\n2. 测试后：恢复原始状态（包括enabled状态）\n\n\n我需要在测试前启用DSS，然后测试每个倍率值。由于`_test_value`会自动恢复原始状态，我只需要确保测试前设置enabled=true即可。\n好的，我需要添加enum模式的测试逻辑。关键问题是：\n1. DSS需要先设置enabled=true才能测试DSSLevel\n2. 需要在测试后恢复原始状态\n\n让我添加enum模式的处理：\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_21ef81e698f342acb41f10dc","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        elif mode == \"toggle\":\n            # 布尔切换型 (BLC: true/false)\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [\"true\", \"false\"])\n            for val in test_values:\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\n                result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})\n\n        elif mode == \"enum\":\n            # 枚举型 (DSS: 慢快门倍率) - 需要先启用再测试\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [])\n            original = self._original_xml.get(item_key, \"\")\n            \n            # DSS特殊处理：如果enabled=false，先设置为true\n            import re\n            if '<enabled>false</enabled>' in original.lower():\n                enable_xml = re.sub(\n                    r'(<enabled>)[^<]*(</enabled>)',\n                    r'\\g<1>true\\g<2>',\n                    original,\n                    flags=re.IGNORECASE\n                )\n                self.client.put(endpoint, enable_xml)\n            \n            # 测试每个DSSLevel值\n            for val in test_values:\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\n                result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})","oldText":"        elif mode == \"toggle\":\n            # 布尔切换型 (BLC: true/false)\n            test_values = cap_def.get(\"test_values\", [\"true\", \"false\"])\n            for val in test_values:\n                success = self._test_value(cap_def, endpoint, val, item_key)\n                result.test_results.append({\"value\": val, \"success\": success})"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":9158,"output":921,"cacheRead":242255,"cacheWrite":151,"totalTokens":252485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783246582995,"responseId":"msg_66430993-1818-4b6a-ad61-6b066085e046"}}
