{"type":"message","id":"fd177585","parentId":"1533f21a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T11:40:56.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题清楚了。`run_all` 方法在第925行，缩进4个空格，但它在 `cancel_active_function` 函数之后（第917行开始），所以它实际上是 `cancel_active_function` 函数的嵌套函数，而不是 `FunctionDetector` 类的方法。\n\n类在第910行 `cancel` 方法结束后就关闭了（第913行开始是模块级代码）。\n\n我需要：\n1. 将 `run_all` 方法移回类内部（在 `cancel` 方法之后，第911行之前）\n2. 保持4个空格的缩进\n\n让我先读取 `run_all` 方法的完整内容，然后修复它。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了！`run_all` 方法（第925行）被错误地放在了 `cancel_active_function` 函数之后，导致它成为嵌套函数而不是类方法。\n\n类在第910行结束。我需要将 `run_all` 移回类内部。先读取完整内容：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_fbe09045ef8c48edacd23fb9","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":925,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\function.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":684,"output":295,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":48413,"totalTokens":49392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783251644085,"responseId":"msg_2cedb665-babf-4dec-8c68-835dbfe9c9cd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"72621003","parentId":"fd177585","timestamp":"2026-07-05T11:40:56.229Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_fbe09045ef8c48edacd23fb9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def run_all(self) -> dict[str, Any]:\r\n        \"\"\"运行全部功能探测 (P4.1-P4.21)。\r\n\r\n        Bug #2 修复: 在功能探测开始之前,第一步执行预置点10设置。\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        import time\r\n        import json\r\n        from pathlib import Path\r\n\r\n        # 步骤1: 设置预置点10为HOME (1800,450,10)\r\n        ptz = PTZController(self.client)\r\n        ptz.setup_home_preset()\r\n        print('Function起点: HOME preset 10 set')\r\n\r\n        # 步骤2: 遍历所有功能端点\r\n        result = {}\r\n        for item_key in FUNCTION_ENDPOINTS:\r\n            if self._cancelled:\r\n                return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"用户取消\"}\r\n            result[item_key] = self.detect_single(item_key)\r\n\r\n        # 步骤3: 恢复所有原始值\r\n        self.restore_all()\r\n\r\n        # 步骤4: 构建完整输出\r\n        output = {\r\n            \"_format\": \"AstroHub Function Detection v1.0 - 读取格式: output.functions[item_key].opt_values\",\r\n            \"_path\": \"data/devices/{mac}/function.json\",\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"total_functions\": len(FUNCTION_ENDPOINTS),\r\n            \"supported_count\": sum(1 for r in result.values() if r.get(\"supported\", False)),\r\n            \"device_info\": {\r\n                \"ip\": self.client.ip,\r\n                \"mac\": self._mac_clean or \"\",\r\n                \"model\": self._model_short or \"\",\r\n            },\r\n            \"detected_at\": datetime.now(timezone.utc).replace(tzinfo=None).isoformat(),\r\n            \"functions\": {}\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        for item_key, data in result.items():\r\n            output[\"functions\"][item_key] = {\r\n                \"p_id\": data.get(\"p_id\", \"\"),\r\n                \"item\": data.get(\"item\", item_key),\r\n                \"label\": data.get(\"label\", item_key),\r\n                \"supported\": data.get(\"supported\", False),\r\n                \"min\": data.get(\"min_val\"),\r\n                \"max\": data.get(\"max_val\"),\r\n                \"endpoint\": data.get(\"endpoint\", \"\"),\r\n                \"opt_values\": data.get(\"opt_values\", []),\r\n                \"current_values\": data.get(\"current_values\", {}),\r\n                \"test_results\": data.get(\"test_results\", []),\r\n                \"restored\": data.get(\"restored\", False),\r\n                \"error\": data.get(\"error\")\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        # 步骤5: 保存到function.json\r\n        try:\r\n            self._init_device_info()\r\n            output_file = get_data_path_write(self._model_short, self._mac_clean, 'function')\r\n            with open(output_file, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\r\n                json.dump(output, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\r\n        except Exception:\r\n            pass\r\n\r\n        return output\r\n\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n#  P5.1 Continuous Move 和 P5.2 Absolute Move 测试\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\r\ndef test_continuous_move(client: ISAPIClient) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"P5.1: 测试持续运动能力。\r\n\r\n    方法:\r\n    - pan/tilt 50持续2秒,0.1s采样一次\r\n    - 移动后回到HOME位\r\n    - 记录坐标变化\r\n\r\n    预期: 设备支持Continuous Move并能正确执行,返回HOME成功\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import time\r\n    from src.ptz.constants import HOME_COORDS\r\n\r\n    ptz = PTZController(client)\r\n    results = {\"pan\": {}, \"tilt\": {}}\r\n\r\n    # 从HOME开始\r\n    ptz.goto_preset(10)\r\n    time.sleep(3)\r\n    start_pos = ptz.get_position()\r\n\r\n    # Pan持续运动测试\r\n    ptz.continuous_move(pan=50, tilt=0)\r\n    pan_samples = []\r\n    for _ in range(20):  # 2秒,0.1s采样\r\n        pos = ptz.get_position()\r\n        if pos:\r\n            pan_samples.append(pos.get(\"pan\", 0))\r\n\n[232 more lines in file. Use offset=1025 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783251656229}}
