{"type":"message","id":"bf6c5ff4","parentId":"aea48d09","timestamp":"2026-07-05T11:52:31.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nThe user is asking me to continue executing the task. Looking at the context:\n\n1. I just completed the function detection test successfully\n2. The `slow_shutter` detection worked - opt_values now contains the correct values: ['*1.25', '*1.5', '*2', '*3', '*4', '*6', '*8']\n3. I updated VERSION to v8.45\n4. I tried to clean up temporary files but they don't exist (run_test.py, check_result.py were already removed)\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Update HEARTBEAT.md with the v8.45 changes\n2. Verify the slow_shutter functionality works end-to-end\n3. Report completion to the user\n\nLet me check what else needs to be done. The task was to migrate slow_shutter to use DSS endpoint. Let me verify:\n- ✅ function.py: Added enum mode for DSS detection\n- ✅ router.py: Updated slow-shutter API to use DSS endpoint\n- ✅ console.html: Updated loadSlowShutter to read opt_values from function.json\n- ✅ Function detection: Successfully detected and populated opt_values\n- ✅ VERSION: Updated to v8.45\n\nNow I should update HEARTBEAT.md and report completion.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"功能测试完成！慢快门迁移成功。现在更新 HEARTBEAT.md 并汇报结果。\n...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_a6e98214ab8447de9b6ac72e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"**最后更新**: 2026-07-05 19:52\n**状态**: v8.45 慢快门迁移DSS完成\n**当前版本**: v8.45\n\n---\n\n## v8.45 慢快门迁移DSS（2026-07-05）\n\n### 完成的任务\n1. ✅ function.py: P4.6慢快门端点从/Shutter改为/DSS，mode从read_only改为enum\n2. ✅ function.py: 添加enum模式探测逻辑，从capabilities获取opt_values\n3. ✅ function.py: 修复run_all方法位置（错误放在类外部）\n4. ✅ router.py: 慢快门API使用DSS端点，读取enabled+DSSLevel\n5. ✅ console.html: loadSlowShutter从function.json读取opt_values动态生成下拉菜单\n6. ✅ 功能测试: 成功检测DSS支持，opt_values=[*1.25,*1.5,*2,*3,*4,*6,*8]\n\n### 修改的文件\n- `astrohub/src/advanced/function.py` — P4.6 endpoint改为/DSS，添加enum模式处理，修复run_all位置\n- `a