{"type":"message","id":"4493b78c","parentId":"c9492232","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:57:18.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n用户要求我遍历代码，找出可以复用的端点，列出计划。我需要：\n\n1. 找出所有图像设置相关的端点\n2. 检查是否有现有的\"设置保存/恢复\"机制\n3. 列出需要修改的文件\n\n从router.py的输出看，已有的图像端点：\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings` (GET/PUT) - 图像设置\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance` (GET/POST) - 白平衡\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/noisereduce` (GET/POST) - 降噪\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/exposure` (GET/POST) - 曝光\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter` (GET/POST) - 快门\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/iris` (GET/POST) - 光圈\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/sharpness` (GET/POST) - 锐化\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/color` (GET) - 色彩\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter` (GET/PUT) - 慢快门\n\n我需要：\n1. 检查是否有现有的配置保存机制\n2. 检查白平衡的自动恢复逻辑（因为用户提到白平衡自动弹出提示）\n3. 找出需要修改的文件\n\n让我继续查看代码。\n\n用户提到\"右上角就弹出一个提示，白平衡自动\"，说明有自动恢复逻辑但触发了不必要的提示。我需要找到这个提示的代码。\n\n我需要：\n1. 搜索\"白平衡\"相关的提示代码\n2. 检查是否有配置保存/恢复的机制\n3. 找出需要修改的文件列表","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"备份完成。现在分析记忆功能需求。已有图像设置端点：\n\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings` (GET/PUT)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance` (GET/POST)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/noisereduce` (GET/POST)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/exposure` (GET/POST)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter` (GET/POST)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/iris` (GET/POST)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/sharpness` (GET/POST)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/color` (GET)\n- `/ptz/{device_id}/image/slow-shutter` (GET/PUT)\n\n查看现有记忆/恢复机制：\n...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2e4507b8ead7473db459b4cb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"image/settings|restore.*config|auto.*restore|config.*restore\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object -First 20","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_769f50dec1494a34899b8e12","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"as