{"type":"message","id":"79d7bee6","parentId":"22812ce2","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:57:37.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\n用户要求我遍历代码，找出可以复用的端点，列出计划。我需要分析：\n\n1. 现有的配置保存/恢复机制\n2. 哪些参数需要记忆（白平衡、慢快门、降噪、亮度、快门、光圈等）\n3. 现有的端点结构\n4. 如何根据MAC作为唯一标识保存配置\n\n从输出看：\n- router.py有 `image/settings` 端点（GET/PUT）\n- console.html有白平衡相关的showToast\n- 有 `_isInitializingImageParams` 标志（可能是初始化时防止重复提示）\n\n让我查看现有的配置保存逻辑和图像参数初始化逻辑。\n\n用户提到\"重启astrohub连接设备后弹出白平衡自动提示\"，说明有自动恢复逻辑，但可能每次都重复提示。需要找到这个逻辑。\n\n我需要：\n1. 查看 `/image/settings` 端点的实现\n2. 查看前端图像参数加载逻辑\n3. 查看是否有配置文件保存机制\n4. 列出需要修改的文件\n\n让我继续搜索相关代码。\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cf6506300f914aed8486c50a","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":1337,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0af7c77cf2fc4dbd998ac969","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"_isInitializingImageParams|loadImageParams|initImageParams\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object -First 30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_3777e1c213d441b7bb3a06a6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html\" -Pattern \"_isInitializingImageParams|loadImageParams|initImageParams\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object -First 30","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7627a07c9ad945418e7eeca4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"function.*whiteBalance|function.*loadWhiteBalance|function.*setWhiteBalance\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object -First 20","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4447,"output":627,"cacheRead":76501,"cacheWrite":1294,"totalTokens":82869,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256239100,"responseId":"msg_65cfd7e3-2f87-4deb-bf46-4a13c9e47ac5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f513944f","parentId":"79d7bee6","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:57:38.136Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_cf6506300f914aed8486c50a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings\", summary=\"获取画面设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_image_settings(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取当前画面参数(亮度/对比度/饱和度)。\"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    client = mgr._clients.get(target_ip)\r\n    if not client:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"ISAPI client not found for {target_ip}\"}\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取画面设置失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n\r\n        # 查找 Color 节点\r\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"Color\":\r\n                for child in elem:\r\n                    ctag = child.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in child.tag else child.tag\r\n                    if ctag == \"brightnessLevel\":\r\n                        result[\"data\"][\"brightness\"] = int((child.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n                    elif ctag == \"contrastLevel\":\r\n                        result[\"data\"][\"contrast\"] = int((child.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n                    elif ctag == \"saturationLevel\":\r\n                        result[\"data\"][\"saturation\"] = int((child.text or \"50\").strip())\r\n                break\r\n\r\n        return result\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取画面设置异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.put(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings\", summary=\"更新画面设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def update_image_settings(device_id: str, req: ImageAdjustRequest) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"更新画面参数。\"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    client = mgr._clients.get(target_ip)\r\n    if not client:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"ISAPI client not found for {target_ip}\"}\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        # 先获取当前设置\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取画面设置失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        xml_str = resp.xml\r\n        import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(xml_str)\r\n\r\n        # 修改 Color 节点\r\n        updated = {}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag == \"Color\":\r\n                for child in elem:\r\n                    ctag = child.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in child.tag else child.tag\r\n                    if ctag == \"brightnessLevel\" and req.brightness is not None:\r\n                        child.text = str(req.brightness)\r\n                        updated[\"brightness\"] = req.brightness\r\n                    elif ctag == \"contrastLevel\" and req.contrast is not None:\r\n                        child.text = str(req.contrast)\r\n\n[2843 more lines in file. Use offset=1417 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256258136}}
