{"type":"message","id":"cb03cbe1","parentId":"01050b88","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:58:35.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nNow I need to understand the full picture. Let me analyze what I've found:\n\n**Current image params loading flow** (console.html lines 857-870):\n- `_isInitializingImageParams = true` (flag to prevent operationLog during init)\n- Line 860: `loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp)` - reads from device\n- Line 861: `loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp)` - reads from device\n- Line 863: `loadSlowShutter(deviceIp)` - reads from device\n- Line 866: `loadSharpness(deviceIp)` - reads from device\n- Line 867: `loadColorParams(deviceIp)` - reads from device\n- After 3 seconds: `_isInitializingImageParams = false`\n\n**Current state**: All these `load*` functions read from the device directly, not from any saved config. So when AstroHub restarts and reconnects, it reads whatever the device currently has, NOT what the user previously set.\n\n**The user's problem**:\n1. No parameter memory - when AstroHub restarts, it doesn't remember previous settings\n2. On reconnect, it shows \"白平衡自动\" toast even though user didn't set it - this is because the device returns its default/previous state, and the load function shows a toast\n\n**What needs to happen**:\n1. Every time a user changes a parameter (white balance, noise reduce, slow shutter, sharpness, color, exposure, shutter, iris), save it to a local config file keyed by device MAC\n2. When connecting to a device, first restore saved settings, then don't show the \"auto\" toast during init\n\n**Existing infrastructure**:\n- `data/devices/{mac}/` directory already exists per device\n- `function.json` - device capabilities\n- `info.json` - device info\n- `speed.json/csv` - speed data\n- `limit.json/csv` - limit data\n\n**Plan**:\n1. Create a new file: `data/devices/{mac}/settings.json` to store user's last settings\n2. Create backend endpoints:\n   - `GET /api/v1/devices/{device_id}/settings` - read saved settings\n   - `PUT /api/v1/devices/{device_id}/settings` - save settings\n3. Modify each `set_*` endpoint to auto-save to settings.json after successful PUT\n4. Modify frontend `loadImageParams` flow:\n   - On connect, load from settings.json first\n   - Apply saved settings to device (restore)\n   - Suppress toasts during init (already done with `_isInitializingImageParams`)\n\nWait, actually let me re-think. The user said:\n- \"右上角就弹出一个提示，白平衡自动\" - this is the toast from loadWhiteBalance showing the current device state\n- \"实际上我没有做任何设置\" - user didn't set it, so it shouldn't show a toast\n- \"之前的设置没有记忆功能\" - no memory of previous settings\n\nSo the fix has two parts:\n1. **Suppress toasts during init** - the `_isInitializingImageParams` flag exists but maybe `showToast` is not respecting it\n2. **Add parameter memory** - save and restore settings\n\nLet me check the `loadWhiteBalance` function to see if it's showing toasts during init.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n- `_isInitializingImageParams` is used to prevent `operationLog` entries during init\n- But `showToast` might still fire during init\n\nLet me look at the loadWhiteBalance function to understand the toast issue.\n\nActually, the user's request is clear:\n1. Add parameter memory (save/restore per device MAC)\n2. Fix the init toast issue (don't show toast on reconnect)\n3. List the plan concisely\n\nLet me provide the plan now. I have enough info to give a clear answer.\n\n**Files to modify**:\n\n1. **`src/api/router.py`** - Add settings save/load endpoints, modify set_* endpoints to auto-save\n2. **`src/web/includes/console.html`** - Modify load flow to restore from saved settings, suppress toasts during init\n3. **New file: `src/advanced/device_settings.py`** (or add to existing module) - Settings read/write logic\n4. **`data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`** - New config file per device\n\nLet me formulate the plan concisely.\n\nActually wait, I should also check if the `showToast` is called from `loadWhiteBalance` and if it respects the init flag. Let me check that quickly.\n\nAlso, I need to check what the `loadImageParams` function does - specifically lines 857-870 of console.html.\n...\n\nLet me look at the init flow and the loadWhiteBalance function to understand the toast issue:\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_da26472e3691449eb12254e3","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":855,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f70f814f93b446ce8f7f17a3","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":988,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2793,"output":1193,"cacheRead":81728,"cacheWrite":1135,"totalTokens":86849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256275994,"responseId":"msg_508d4abe-f46f-48e0-84fc-706d0bd9786f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfdf961a","parentId":"cb03cbe1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:58:35.719Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_da26472e3691449eb12254e3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\r\nfunction loadAllImageParams(deviceIp) {\r\n    _isInitializingImageParams = true;  // v7.59: 开始初始化,禁止记录日志\r\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\r\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\r\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\r\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\r\n    loadFilterStatus(deviceIp);\r\n    loadSlowShutter(deviceIp);\r\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\r\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\r\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\r\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\r\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\r\n    // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\r\n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 显示功能检测覆盖层\r\nfunction showFunctionOverlay() {\r\n\n[1153 more lines in file. Use offset=875 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256315719}}
{"type":"message","id":"47549426","parentId":"dfdf961a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:58:35.719Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_f70f814f93b446ce8f7f17a3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/whitebalance').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n            var wb = r.data;\r\n            deviceImageParams.whiteBalance = wb;\r\n\r\n            var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbModeSelect) {\r\n                // 根据设备返回的模式设置下拉菜单\r\n                if (wb.mode === 'manual') {\r\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'auto';\r\n                }\r\n                // 触发显示/隐藏逻辑\r\n                onWbModeChange(wbModeSelect.value);\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            // 更新 R/B 滑动条\r\n            var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n            var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n            var wbRedVal = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n            var wbBlueVal = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n\r\n            if (wbRed && wb.red_gain !== undefined) {\r\n                wbRed.value = wb.red_gain;\r\n                if (wbRedVal) wbRedVal.textContent = wb.red_gain;\r\n            }\r\n            if (wbBlue && wb.blue_gain !== undefined) {\r\n                wbBlue.value = wb.blue_gain;\r\n                if (wbBlueVal) wbBlueVal.textContent = wb.blue_gain;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            // 设置范围\r\n            if (wb.min !== undefined && wb.max !== undefined) {\r\n                if (wbRed) { wbRed.min = wb.min; wbRed.max = wb.max; }\r\n                if (wbBlue) { wbBlue.min = wb.min; wbBlue.max = wb.max; }\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            // 只有手动模式时 R/B 滑动条才可用\r\n            var isManual = wb.mode === 'manual';\r\n            if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = !isManual;\r\n            if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = !isManual;\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        console.warn('[WB] Load failed:', e);\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 加载降噪\r\nfunction loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/noisereduce').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n            var nr = r.data;\r\n            deviceImageParams.noiseReduce = nr;\r\n\r\n            var dnrSpatial = document.getElementById('dnrSpatial');\r\n            var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');\r\n            var dnrSpatialVal = document.getElementById('dnrSpatialVal');\r\n            var dnrTemporalVal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporalVal');\r\n\n[980 more lines in file. Use offset=1048 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256315719}}
{"type":"message","id":"003fb8e0","parentId":"47549426","timestamp":"2026-07-05T12:59:10.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了\"...\"，这是继续信号。我需要分析代码并给出计划。\n\n从刚才读取的代码来看：\n\n1. `loadAllImageParams` 函数（第855行）：\n   - 设置 `_isInitializingImageParams = true`\n   - 调用各个 load 函数\n   - 3秒后设置 `_isInitializingImageParams = false`\n\n2. `loadWhiteBalance` 函数（第988行）：\n   - 从设备读取白平衡设置\n   - 更新 UI 元素\n   - 没有看到 showToast 调用\n\n问题是：重启 AstroHub 后连接设备，会弹出\"白平衡自动\"提示。这个提示应该来自 `onWbModeChange` 函数。\n\n我需要：\n1. 找到 `onWbModeChange` 函数，看看是否有 showToast\n2. 理解当前的初始化流程\n3. 设计参数记忆方案\n\n参数记忆方案思路：\n- 存储位置：`data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n- 存储内容：白平衡模式、R/B增益、降噪、慢快门、快门、光圈等所有图像参数\n- 保存时机：每次参数修改成功后\n- 恢复时机：设备连接后加载参数时，优先使用保存的配置\n\n需要修改的文件：\n1. `src/api/router.py` - 添加保存/读取设置的端点\n2. `src/web/includes/console.html` - 修改 loadAllImageParams 和各个设置函数，添加保存逻辑\n3. 可能需要新建一个 settings 管理模块\n\n让我先找到 showToast 的调用位置，然后给出完整计划。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c04d129097214a12b144d1aa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"onWbModeChange|showToast.*白平衡\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_441c4db33fd847d88739d507","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1488,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2676,"output":523,"cacheRead":82863,"cacheWrite":2166,"totalTokens":88228,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256315721,"responseId":"msg_5d993c51-14e2-472d-a3b8-7bd180be788c"}}
