{"type":"message","id":"56016977","parentId":"12345c02","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:01:51.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent \"...\" which is a continuation signal. I've been analyzing the codebase and need to present my findings and plan.\n\nFrom my analysis:\n\n1. **Current state**: \n   - No settings memory per device - every reconnect resets to device defaults\n   - `loadAllImageParams` reads from device directly, shows toasts even during init\n   - The `_isInitializingImageParams` flag only prevents `operationLog` but not `showToast`\n\n2. **Problem identified**:\n   - `setWhiteBalanceMode()` always shows toast: `showToast('success', '白平衡: ...')`\n   - This is called by `onWbModeChange()` which is called by `loadWhiteBalance()`\n   - During init, `_isInitializingImageParams` is true but doesn't prevent the toast\n\n3. **Existing infrastructure**:\n   - `data/devices/{mac}/` - per-device directory\n   - `function.json` - device capabilities\n   - `info.json` - device info\n   - `device_path.py` - has `get_data_path_write()` helper\n\n4. **Settings to remember**:\n   - 白平衡模式 (auto/manual)\n   - 白平衡 R/B 增益\n   - 降噪 (spatial/temporal)\n   - 慢快门 (DSS level)\n   - 快门速度\n   - 光圈\n   - 曝光模式\n   - 锐化\n   - 色彩参数 (亮度/对比度/饱和度)\n\n5. **Plan**:\n   - Create `settings.json` in `data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n   - Backend: auto-save settings whenever `set_*` API is called\n   - Backend: add `GET/PUT /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/settings` endpoints\n   - Frontend: modify `loadAllImageParams` to load saved settings first, then restore\n   - Frontend: suppress toasts during init\n\nLet me present this concisely to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 分析结果\n\n**问题根源**：\n- `loadWhiteBalance()` → `onWbModeChange()` → `setWhiteBalanceMode()` 每次都调 `showToast()`\n- `_isInitializingImageParams` 只阻止 `operationLog`，没阻止 toast\n- 无任何设备参数记忆机制，每次重连从设备读默认值\n\n**现有存储结构**（`data/devices/{mac}/`）：\n```\nfunction.json  - 设备能力\ninfo.json      - 设备信息  \nspeed.json     - 速度数据\nlimit.json     - 限位数据\n```\n\n---\n\n## 修改计划\n\n### 存储设计\n- **文件**：`data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n- **内容**：所有图像参数的最后设置值\n\n### 需修改的文件（3个）\n\n**① `src/advanced/device_settings.py`（新增）**\n- 添加 `load_settings(mac)` / `save_settings(mac, settings)` 函数\n- 使用 `get_data_path_write()` 保持路径一致\n\n**② `src/api/router.py`**\n- 修改 `set_whitebalance` / `set_noisereduce` / `set_slow_shutter` / `set_shutter` / `set_iris` / `set_exposure` / `set_sharpness` / `update_image_settings` 等8个端点\n- 每个端点成功后追加一行：`save_settings(mac, {...})`\n- 新增 `GET /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/settings` - 读取保存的设置\n\n**③ `src/web/includes/console.html`**\n- `loadAllImageParams()` 改为：先调 `/settings` 接口读保存值，再恢复UI状态\n- 恢复时设置 `_isRestoringSettings = true`\n- 所有 `setXxx` 函数加判断：`if (_isRestoringSettings) return`（不触发 toast 和 API）\n\n### 修复\"白平衡自动\"弹窗\n- `setWhiteBalanceMode()` 开头加：`if (_isInitializingImageParams) return`（恢复模式时不弹窗）\n\n---\n\n**执行顺序**：\n1. 备份当前代码 ✓\n2. 新建 `device_settings.py`\n3. 修改 `router.py` 8个设置端点 + 1个读取端点\n4. 修改 `console.html` 初始化逻辑\n5. 重启测试\n\n确认后开始执行？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1862,"output":964,"cacheRead":89345,"cacheWrite":1471,"totalTokens":93642,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783256486473,"responseId":"msg_b7689fb0-f10a-445c-80e0-4f414388af82"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f23d8db7","parentId":"56016977","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:03:25.696Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-07-05 20:56:09 GMT+8] Exec completed (faint-sl, code 0) :: \\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory [32;1mMode [0m[32;1m LastWriteTime[0m [32;1;3m Length[0m[32;1m Name[0m [32;1m---- [0m [32;1m -------------[0m [32;1m ------[0m [32;1m----…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"46368\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-07-05 21:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n开始执行"}],"timestamp":1783256605687}}
{"type":"message","id":"90fd80c8","parentId":"f23d8db7","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:06.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"开始执行\"。我已经给出了计划，现在需要按步骤执行。\n\n让我回顾一下计划：\n1. 新建 `device_settings.py` - 设置保存/读取逻辑\n2. 修改 `router.py` - 8个设置端点 + 1个读取端点，保存到 settings.json\n3. 修改 `console.html` - 初始化时恢复设置，抑制toast\n\n我需要：\n1. 先查看 device_path.py 的 get_data_path_write 和 get_device_info 的签名\n2. 查看 router.py 中需要修改的设置端点\n3. 查看 console.html 中 loadAllImageParams 和相关函数\n\n让我开始执行。\n\n首先，查看 device_path.py 的接口：\n- get_data_path_write(model_short, mac_clean, test_type) -> Path\n- get_data_path_read(model_short, mac_clean, test_type) -> Path | None\n- get_device_info(device_id) -> dict\n\n然后，查看 router.py 中已有的 set_ 端点，找到哪些需要添加 save_settings：\n- set_whitebalance (line ~2920)\n- set_noisereduce (line ~3026)\n- set_exposure (line ~3200)\n- set_shutter (line ~3280)\n- set_iris (line ~3353)\n- set_sharpness (line ~3496)\n- set_slow_shutter (line ~3700)\n- update_image_settings (line ~1381)\n\n我需要在这些端点成功 PUT 到设备后，保存设置到 settings.json。\n\nsettings.json 格式：\n```json\n{\n  \"whitebalance\": {\"mode\": \"auto\", \"red_gain\": 200, \"blue_gain\": 200},\n  \"noisereduce\": {\"spatial_level\": 50, \"temporal_level\": 50},\n  \"exposure\": {\"mode\": \"auto\"},\n  \"shutter\": {\"level\": \"1/100\"},\n  \"iris\": {\"level\": \"F2.8\"},\n  \"sharpness\": {\"level\": 50},\n  \"slow_shutter\": {\"enabled\": false, \"level\": \"关闭\"},\n  \"image_settings\": {\"brightness\": 50, \"contrast\": 50, \"saturation\": 50},\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-07-05T21:00:00\"\n}\n```\n\n然后新建 `/api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/settings` 读取端点。\n\nconsole.html 修改：\n1. 新增 `loadSavedSettings(deviceIp)` 函数\n2. 修改 `loadAllImageParams` 改为恢复模式\n3. 在 `setWhiteBalanceMode` 等函数中，恢复模式时不调 API\n\n等等，我需要更仔细地思考。用户说\"根据设备mac作为唯一标识，自动记忆之前的各项参数配置\"。\n\n这意味着：\n- 当用户通过前端修改参数时，后端保存到 settings.json\n- 当设备连接/重连时，前端从 settings.json 读取并恢复到设备\n\n但问题是：前端不知道 MAC 地址（或者说需要通过 device_id 获取 MAC）。\n\n实际上，在前端，device_id 就是 MAC 地址（cleaned format）。后端端点中 `device_id` 参数就是 MAC。\n\n所以我需要：\n1. 后端新增 `/api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/settings` (GET/PUT) 端点\n2. 前端在参数修改成功后通过 PUT 保存\n3. 前端在连接时通过 GET 读取并恢复\n\n实际上，更简单的方式是：后端在 set_* 端点成功后自动保存，前端不需要额外调用。\n\n恢复时：\n1. 前端调 GET /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/settings 获取保存的设置\n2. 前端设置 UI 控件值\n3. 前端调用对应的 set_* 函数发送 API 请求（但需要抑制 toast）\n\n等等，这样会有问题：恢复时发送 API 请求到设备，如果设备不支持某个设置，可能会失败。\n\n更好的方式：恢复时只更新 UI，不发送 API。但这和当前的初始化流程冲突。\n\n让我重新思考。当前的 `loadAllImageParams` 流程：\n1. 从设备读取当前设置\n2. 更新 UI\n\n如果改成\"从 settings.json 读取 -> 更新 UI -> 发送 API 恢复到设备\"，需要：\n1. 读取 settings.json\n2. 设置 UI 控件\n3. 逐个发送 API 请求恢复\n\n但这会触发 showToast。\n\n或者：\n1. 读取 settings.json\n2. 设置一个 `_isRestoringSettings` 标志\n3. 设置 UI 控件\n4. 发送 API 请求（`_isRestoringSettings=true` 时抑制 toast）\n5. 恢复完成后 `_isRestoringSettings = false`\n\n这是可行的。\n\n但等等，用户说\"下次只要连接上同一个设备，就恢复最后一次的设置\"。这意味着在 `loadAllImageParams` 时：\n1. 先读取 settings.json\n2. 如果存在保存的设置，应用到设备\n3. 如果不存在，从设备读取（当前行为）\n\n好的，让我开始编码。\n\n步骤：\n1. 新建 `src/advanced/device_settings.py` - 读写 settings.json\n2. 修改 `router.py` - 添加 settings 端点，修改 set_* 端点自动保存\n3. 修改 `console.html` - 恢复逻辑 + 抑制 toast\n\n让我先查看 device_path.py 的 get_data_path_write 函数签名。\n\n我需要查看：\n- get_device_info(device_id) 返回什么\n- get_data_path_write(model_short, mac_clean, test_type) 签名\n\n从之前的搜索结果：\n- `get_data_path_write(model_short: str | None, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path`\n\n但 get_device_info 的签名我需要确认。\n\n让我读取 device_path.py 文件。\n\n其实，我可以直接读取这个文件。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"开始执行。首先查看 `device_path.py` 接口："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:105","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":145,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:106","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":84457,"output":1343,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256605715,"responseId":"cht000d9b8f@dx19f326084ec29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"486753ae","parentId":"90fd80c8","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:06.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:105","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    return None\n\n\ndef get_data_path_write(model_short: str | None, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"v6.19: 获取写入路径（固定名称文件）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号（可选，v6.19 不再使用）\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径 data/devices/{mac_clean}/{test_type}.json\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(mac_clean)\n    device_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n    return device_dir / f'{test_type}.json'\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256646497}}
{"type":"message","id":"d1a4d4fa","parentId":"486753ae","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:06.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:106","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v2.0 - 设备数据路径管理\n\nv6.19 更新:\n- 删除 config_paths 依赖，统一路径定义\n- 统一路径：data/devices/{mac}/\n- 带时间戳文件：data/devices/{mac}/{test_type}_{timestamp}.json\n- 读取规则：永远读最新记录\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\n# ================================================================ #\n#  统一路径定义 (v6.19)\n# ================================================================ #\n\ndef _get_app_dir() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取应用程序根目录。\"\"\"\n    import sys\n    if getattr(sys, 'frozen', False):\n        return Path(sys.executable).parent\n    return Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent.parent\n\n\n[133 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256646497}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6421848","parentId":"d1a4d4fa","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:28.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to find `get_device_info` function. Let me continue reading device_path.py to understand how to get device MAC and how to look up device info.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我需要找到 `get_device_info` 的签名，以及了解如何通过 device_id 获取 MAC。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cdffdcd2edbd45d2b28d827b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py\" -Pattern \"def get_device_info|def get_devices_dir\" -Context 0,3 | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_f4cd0340a03449b0ac5ed95d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":40,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2223,"output":233,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":93636,"totalTokens":96092,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256646499,"responseId":"msg_8187cc73-a830-44a1-9b60-b5d425fe6292"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d00eb51","parentId":"f6421848","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:29.462Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_cdffdcd2edbd45d2b28d827b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n        36 def get_devices_dir() -> Path:\r\n        41 def get_device_info(ptz: Any) -> dict[str, str]:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":408,"aggregated":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n        36 def get_devices_dir() -> Path:\r\n        41 def get_device_info(ptz: Any) -> dict[str, str]:","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256669462}}
{"type":"message","id":"3cd83152","parentId":"9d00eb51","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:29.462Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_f4cd0340a03449b0ac5ed95d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\ndef get_device_info(ptz: Any) -> dict[str, str]:\n    \"\"\"从设备获取唯一标识信息。\n\n    Args:\n        ptz: PTZController实例\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: {mac, model, model_short, serial}\n    \"\"\"\n    # 从PTZController获取ISAPIClient\n    client = ptz.client if hasattr(ptz, 'client') else ptz\n\n    # 获取设备信息\n    resp = client.get('/System/deviceInfo')\n    xml = resp.xml\n\n    # 解析XML\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    root = ET.fromstring(xml)\n\n    # 提取字段\n    mac = \"\"\n    model = \"\"\n    serial = \"\"\n\n    for child in root:\n        tag = child.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in child.tag else child.tag\n        if tag == 'macAddress':\n            mac = child.text or \"\"\n        elif tag == 'model':\n            model = child.text or \"\"\n        elif tag == 'serialNumber':\n            serial = child.text or \"\"\n\n    # MAC地址去除冒号，转小写\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(':', '').lower()\n\n    # 短型号：取前缀（去掉后缀数字和字母）\n    # iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A -> iDS-2DF8C\n\n[84 more lines in file. Use offset=80 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256669462}}
{"type":"message","id":"ffe81a50","parentId":"3cd83152","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:45.842Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求根据设备MAC保存参数记忆。我需要：\n\n1. 查看router.py中现有set_*端点，了解如何获取device_id和MAC\n2. 创建device_settings.py模块，提供load/save接口\n3. 在每个set_*端点成功后保存设置\n4. 在console.html中，连接设备时从settings.json加载并恢复设置\n\n让我先查看router.py中如何解析device_id，以及如何获取MAC。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4124f0f4c1874f8089f85c87","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"def _resolve_device_id_to_ip|device_id.*mac|target_mac\" | Select-Object LineNumber, Line | Format-Table -Wrap | Select-Object -First 15","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_535dc65caf9f4f43b4d7f284","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":2920,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1033,"output":281,"cacheRead":17038,"cacheWrite":78427,"totalTokens":96779,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256669465,"responseId":"msg_3da18111-8837-49e8-9eac-2f0998ec793d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"04effd93","parentId":"ffe81a50","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:46.461Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_4124f0f4c1874f8089f85c87","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n       205 def _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr: \"PTZDeviceController\", device_id: str) -> str | None:\r\n       208     device_id ������ IP ��ַ�� MAC ��ַ��\r\n       617     device_id ������ IP ��ַ�� MAC ��ַ������� MAC,�Զ�����Ϊ IP��\r\n       629     # ���� device_id: ����������� MAC,�ӷ��ֻ����н��� IP\r\n       714     # ���� device_id (MAC) �� IP\r\n      2422                 device_id = mac.upper().replace(\":\", \"-\") if mac else \"onboarding\"\r\n      2816     target_mac = None\r\n      2824                         target_mac = device_dir.name  # MAC = Ŀ¼��\r\n      2829     if not target_mac:\r\n      2833     func_file = get_data_path_read(None, target_mac, \"function\")\r\n      3902     \"\"\"�� device_id (MAC��IP) ��ȡ ISAPIClient��\"\"\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":426,"aggregated":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n       205 def _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr: \"PTZDeviceController\", device_id: str) -> str | None:\r\n       208     device_id ������ IP ��ַ�� MAC ��ַ��\r\n       617     device_id ������ IP ��ַ�� MAC ��ַ������� MAC,�Զ�����Ϊ IP��\r\n       629     # ���� device_id: ����������� MAC,�ӷ��ֻ����н��� IP\r\n       714     # ���� device_id (MAC) �� IP\r\n      2422                 device_id = mac.upper().replace(\":\", \"-\") if mac else \"onboarding\"\r\n      2816     target_mac = None\r\n      2824                         target_mac = device_dir.name  # MAC = Ŀ¼��\r\n      2829     if not target_mac:\r\n      2833     func_file = get_data_path_read(None, target_mac, \"function\")\r\n      3902     \"\"\"�� device_id (MAC��IP) ��ȡ ISAPIClient��\"\"\"","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256686461}}
{"type":"message","id":"934834ad","parentId":"04effd93","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:04:46.461Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_535dc65caf9f4f43b4d7f284","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"设置白平衡\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_whitebalance(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置白平衡参数(模式或R/B增益)。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        # 参数处理\r\n        mode_input = data.get(\"mode\")\r\n        red_input = data.get(\"red_gain\")\r\n        blue_input = data.get(\"blue_gain\")\r\n\r\n        # 获取当前值\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\r\n        current_mode = \"auto\"\r\n        current_red = 100\r\n        current_blue = 80\r\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n            for elem in root.iter():\r\n                tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n                if tag == \"WhiteBalanceStyle\":\r\n                    current_mode = (elem.text or \"auto\").lower()\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceRed\":\r\n                    current_red = int(elem.text or 100)\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceBlue\":\r\n                    current_blue = int(elem.text or 80)\r\n\r\n        # 使用传入值或当前值\r\n        mode_val = mode_input if mode_input else current_mode\r\n        red_val = red_input if red_input is not None else current_red\r\n        blue_val = blue_input if blue_input is not None else current_blue\r\n\r\n        # ISAPI 要求小写\r\n        mode_isapi = mode_val.lower() if mode_val else \"manual\"\r\n\r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n\n[1290 more lines in file. Use offset=2970 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256686461}}
{"type":"message","id":"95bc4435","parentId":"934834ad","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:05:33.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0f588574c6a1450381a7918e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":205,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_148c036bae044e34900c43b4","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":610,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1569,"output":154,"cacheRead":95465,"cacheWrite":621,"totalTokens":97809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256686463,"responseId":"msg_547a8824-34a5-4235-abda-ec1fc8bb30ce"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bb8cf8af","parentId":"95bc4435","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:05:33.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_0f588574c6a1450381a7918e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr: \"PTZDeviceController\", device_id: str) -> str | None:\r\n    \"\"\"解析 device_id 为实际 IP 地址。\r\n\r\n    device_id 可能是 IP 地址或 MAC 地址。\r\n    - 如果是 IP: 直接返回\r\n    - 如果是 MAC: 从 SADP 发现缓存或已存储设备中查找 IP\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import re\r\n    # 判断是否为 MAC 地址格式 (冒号、横杠分隔或无分隔符)\r\n    mac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n    # 无分隔符12位十六进制 = MAC\r\n    if len(mac_clean) == 12 and re.match(r'^[0-9a-f]{12}$', mac_clean):\r\n        # 是 MAC 地址,尝试从发现缓存中查找\r\n        discovered = mgr.get_discovered_devices()\r\n        for dev in discovered:\r\n            dev_mac = dev.get(\"mac\", \"\").replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n            if dev_mac == mac_clean:\r\n                return dev.get(\"ip\")\r\n        # 从已存储设备中查找\r\n        stored = mgr.list_stored_devices()\r\n        for dev in stored:\r\n            dev_mac = dev.get(\"mac\", \"\").replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n            if dev_mac == mac_clean:\r\n                ip = dev.get(\"ip\", \"\")\r\n                if ip:\r\n                    return ip\r\n        returnPTZDeviceController | None\r\n    # 看起来像 IP 地址,直接返回\r\n    return device_id\r\n\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n#  健康检查端点\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\r\n\r\n@health_router.get(\"/health\", summary=\"全局健康检查\")\r\nasync def global_health() -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"全局健康检查端点 (GET /api/v1/health)。\"\"\"\r\n    module_keys = (\r\n\n[4015 more lines in file. Use offset=245 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256733283}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb5a8137","parentId":"bb8cf8af","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:05:33.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_148c036bae044e34900c43b4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/devices/{device_id}/connect\", summary=\"连接设备\", tags=[\"Devices\"])\r\nasync def connect_device(device_id: str, req: ConnectDeviceRequest | None = None) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"连接 PTZ 设备并认证。\r\n\r\n    device_id 可以是 IP 地址或 MAC 地址。如果是 MAC,自动解析为 IP。\r\n    使用 admin 作为默认用户名,密码必须由用户提供或已保存在配置中。\r\n\r\n    BUG-014 修复: ISAPI 连接前 socket 预检,5 秒超时快速失败。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    log_api(\"connect\", {\"mac\": device_id})\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        log_error(\"connect\", {\"mac\": device_id, \"error\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"})\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    # 解析 device_id: 如果看起来像 MAC,从发现缓存中解析 IP\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        log_error(\"connect\", {\"mac\": device_id, \"error\": \"无法解析设备标识\"})\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id},请提供 IP 地址或确保设备已通过 SADP 发现\"}\r\n\r\n    # 如果未提供凭据,尝试从存储获取\r\n    if req is None:\r\n        creds = mgr.get_credentials(target_ip)\r\n        if not creds:\r\n            log_error(\"connect\", {\"mac\": device_id, \"error\": \"设备未保存凭据\"})\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"设备未保存凭据,请先提供用户名和密码\"}\r\n        username = creds[\"username\"]\r\n        password = creds[\"password\"]\r\n        port = creds.get(\"port\", 80)\r\n    else:\r\n        username = req.username or \"admin\"\r\n        if not req.password:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"请提供密码\"}\r\n        password = req.password\r\n        port = req.port\r\n\n[3610 more lines in file. Use offset=650 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783256733283}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e861daf","parentId":"eb5a8137","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:07:23.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nNow I understand the device_id handling:\n- `_resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)` - takes device_id (could be IP or MAC), returns IP\n- device_id in the endpoint is the MAC address (cleaned, no separators)\n- The device_dir in data/devices/{mac}/ uses MAC as folder name\n\nFor settings save/load, I need to:\n1. Get MAC from device_id (the device_id is already MAC)\n2. Use `get_data_path_write` to create path for settings.json\n\nLet me now:\n1. Read the full set_whitebalance endpoint to understand the structure\n2. Read the console.html loadImageParams and related functions\n3. Then implement the solution\n\nActually, let me just implement directly:\n\n**Step 1: Create `src/advanced/device_settings.py`**\n- `load_settings(mac: str) -> dict | None`\n- `save_settings(mac: str, settings: dict) -> bool`\n\n**Step 2: Modify `router.py`**\n- Add `save_device_settings()` helper that saves to settings.json\n- Modify each set_* endpoint to call save after successful PUT\n- Add `GET /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/settings` endpoint\n\n**Step 3: Modify `console.html`**\n- Modify `loadAllImageParams` to call a new function that loads saved settings first\n- In `setWhiteBalanceMode` and similar, add check for `_isInitializingImageParams` or `_isRestoringSettings`\n\nWait, I need to think about this more carefully.\n\nThe user's requirement:\n1. Save all settings to settings.json per device MAC\n2. When connecting, restore the last settings\n3. Don't show toast during init\n\nThe flow should be:\n1. User changes a setting → frontend calls set_* API → backend PUTs to device → backend saves to settings.json\n2. On reconnect → frontend calls GET /settings → frontend restores UI state and sends set_* calls to device → but suppress toasts\n\nActually, simpler approach:\n1. Backend saves to settings.json whenever a set_* API succeeds\n2. Frontend on loadAllImageParams:\n   - Set `_isInitializingImageParams = true`\n   - Load current values from device (as it does now)\n   - Then load from settings.json and apply to UI\n   - After applying, set `_isInitializingImageParams = false`\n\nWait, but the issue is: loadWhiteBalance reads from device and sets UI. If the user previously set manual mode, but device is now in auto (factory default after restart), we need to:\n1. Read from settings.json\n2. Send API to device to restore\n3. Update UI\n\nSo the flow should be:\n1. `loadAllImageParams` sets `_isInitializingImageParams = true`\n2. Calls `restoreSettings(deviceIp)` which:\n   - GET /api/v1/ptz/{deviceIp}/settings to get saved settings\n   - For each saved setting, call the corresponding set_* function (which will also save again, but that's ok)\n3. After all restores done, set `_isInitializingImageParams = false`\n\nBut wait, the current `setWhiteBalanceMode` calls `apiPost` which doesn't have a way to suppress toast. I need to either:\n- Add a flag to suppress toast\n- Or create a separate \"silent\" version of set functions\n\nActually, looking at the code, the `showToast` is called in `setWhiteBalanceMode`. If `_isInitializingImageParams` is true, we should skip the toast.\n\nLet me look at the current setWhiteBalanceMode:\n\n```javascript\nfunction setWhiteBalanceMode(mode) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: mode })\n        .then(function(r) {\n            if (r && r.success) {\n                showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'));\n                if (typeof operationLog === 'function' && !_isInitializingImageParams) operationLog('白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'), 'success');\n            }\n        });\n}\n```\n\nSo I need to add `&& !_isInitializingImageParams` to the showToast condition too:\n\n```javascript\nif (r && r.success) {\n    if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'));\n    if (typeof operationLog === 'function' && !_isInitializingImageParams) operationLog(...);\n}\n```\n\nOK let me now implement this step by step.\n\nFirst, create device_settings.py:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"\nAstroHub v8.45 - 设备设置记忆模块\n\n根据设备MAC保存/恢复各项参数配置。\n存储路径: data/devices/{mac}/settings.json\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_data_path_read, get_data_path_write\n\n\ndef load_settings(mac_clean: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"加载设备保存的设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: 设备设置，或 None 如果不存在\n    \"\"\"\n    path = get_data_path_read(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    if path and path.exists():\n        try:\n            with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n                return json.load(f)\n        except Exception:\n            return None\n    return None\n\n\ndef save_settings(mac_clean: str, settings: dict[str, Any]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"保存设备设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        settings: 要保存的设置\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: 是否保存成功\n    \"\"\"\n    from datetime import datetime, timezone\n\n    # 合并现有设置\n    existing = load_settings(mac_clean) or {}\n    existing.update(settings)\n    existing['last_updated'] = datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat()\n\n    path = get_data_path_write(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    try:\n        with open(path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            json.dump(existing, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n        return True\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n```\n\nNow, I need to modify router.py to:\n1. Import device_settings\n2. Add save call in each set_* endpoint\n3. Add GET endpoint for settings\n\nLet me look at the set_whitebalance endpoint more carefully to see where to add the save call.\n\nActually, I need to get the MAC from device_id. In the set_* endpoints, they use `_resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)` to get IP, but I need MAC.\n\nLooking at the code, device_id is already the MAC in most cases. Let me check...\n\nFrom the code:\n```python\nmac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\n# 无分隔符12位十六进制 = MAC\nif len(mac_clean) == 12 and re.match(r'^[0-9a-f]{12}$', mac_clean):\n```\n\nSo device_id is the MAC. I can use it directly (after cleaning).\n\nLet me now implement the changes.\n\nFor router.py, I'll add a helper function that gets MAC from device_id and saves settings:\n\n```python\ndef _save_device_setting(device_id: str, key: str, value: Any) -> None:\n    \"\"\"保存设备设置到 settings.json。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        from src.advanced.device_settings import save_settings\n        mac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\n        if len(mac_clean) == 12:\n            save_settings(mac_clean, {key: value})\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n```\n\nThen in each set_* endpoint, after successful PUT, call this helper.\n\nFor the GET endpoint:\n```python\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/settings\", summary=\"获取设备保存的设置\", tags=[\"Settings\"])\nasync def get_saved_settings(device_id: str) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"获取设备保存的参数设置。\"\"\"\n    mac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\n    if len(mac_clean) != 12:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"无效的设备标识\"}\n    \n    from src.advanced.device_settings import load_settings\n    settings = load_settings(mac_clean)\n    return {\"success\": True, \"data\": settings or {}}\n```\n\nNow for console.html, I need to modify `loadAllImageParams` to call a restore function:\n\n```javascript\nfunction loadAllImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    _isInitializingImageParams = true;\n    \n    // 先恢复保存的设置\n    restoreSettings(deviceIp);\n    \n    // 然后加载当前值\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\n    // ... other loads\n    \n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 5000);\n}\n\nfunction restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/settings').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            var s = r.data;\n            \n            // 恢复白平衡\n            if (s.whitebalance) {\n                if (s.whitebalance.mode) {\n                    var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n                    if (wbModeSelect) {\n                        wbModeSelect.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\n                        onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode);\n                    }\n                }\n                // ... R/B gains\n            }\n            \n            // 恢复降噪、慢快门等...\n        }\n    });\n}\n```\n\nBut wait, there's a problem. If we call `onWbModeChange`, it will call `setWhiteBalanceMode`, which will send API request to device. And `setWhiteBalanceMode` shows toast.\n\nSo I need to either:\n1. Modify `onWbModeChange` to not call `setWhiteBalanceMode` when `_isInitializingImageParams` is true\n2. Or modify `setWhiteBalanceMode` to check `_isInitializingImageParams`\n\nLet me check `onWbModeChange` again:\n\n```javascript\nfunction onWbModeChange(mode) {\n    // ... UI changes (show/hide controls)\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\n        // ...\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\n        // ...\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n    } else {\n        // ...\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\n    }\n}\n```\n\nSo `onWbModeChange` calls `setWhiteBalanceMode`. I need to either:\n1. Add a flag to `onWbModeChange` to skip calling `setWhiteBalanceMode`\n2. Or check `_isInitializingImageParams` in `setWhiteBalanceMode`\n\nOption 2 is simpler. Let me modify `setWhiteBalanceMode`:\n\n```javascript\nfunction setWhiteBalanceMode(mode) {\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (!dev) return;\n\n    // 初始化时不发送API请求，避免重复调用\n    if (_isInitializingImageParams) return;\n\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: mode })\n        .then(function(r) {\n            if (r && r.success) {\n                if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'));\n                if (typeof operationLog === 'function' && !_isInitializingImageParams) operationLog('白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'), 'success');\n            }\n        });\n}\n```\n\nBut wait, this would prevent setting the mode during init. The user wants to restore settings on reconnect. So we need to:\n1. During init, call `restoreSettings` which sets the UI state\n2. But we don't want to call `setWhiteBalanceMode` which sends API\n\nActually, let me re-read the requirement:\n- \"下次只要连接上同一个设备，就恢复最后一次的设置\"\n- This means: next time connecting to the same device, restore the last settings\n\nSo the flow should be:\n1. On connect, load saved settings\n2. For each setting, send API to device to set it\n3. Don't show toast during this process\n\nThe issue is that `setWhiteBalanceMode` shows toast. So I need to either:\n- Add a flag to suppress toast\n- Or create a separate \"silent\" version\n\nLet me add a flag `_isRestoringSettings`:\n\n```javascript\nvar _isRestoringSettings = false;\n\nfunction restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\n    _isRestoringSettings = true;\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/settings').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\n            var s = r.data;\n            \n            // 恢复白平衡\n            if (s.whitebalance) {\n                if (s.whitebalance.mode) {\n                    var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n                    if (wbModeSelect) {\n                        wbModeSelect.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\n                        // 不调用 onWbModeChange，直接设置UI并发送API\n                        document.getElementById('wbManualControls').style.display = s.whitebalance.mode === 'manual' ? 'flex' : 'none';\n                        // ...\n                        apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: s.whitebalance.mode });\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }).finally(function() {\n        setTimeout(function() { _isRestoringSettings = false; }, 3000);\n    });\n}\n```\n\nHmm, this is getting complex. Let me simplify:\n\n1. Modify all `set*` functions to check `_isRestoringSettings` and skip toast\n2. In `loadAllImageParams`, call `restoreSettings` first, which sets `_isRestoringSettings = true`\n3. `restoreSettings` loads saved settings and calls the appropriate set functions\n4. After all done, set `_isRestoringSettings = false`\n\nBut this is a lot of changes. Let me think of a simpler approach.\n\nActually, the simplest approach:\n1. Modify `setWhiteBalanceMode` to check `_isRestoringSettings || _isInitializingImageParams`\n2. In `loadAllImageParams`, set `_isInitializingImageParams = true`, then call `restoreSettings`, then call other load functions\n3. `restoreSettings` sets the UI state and sends API (but no toast because of the flag)\n4. After timeout, set `_isInitializingImageParams = false`\n\nWait, but the issue is that `loadWhiteBalance` also calls `onWbModeChange`, which calls `setWhiteBalanceMode`. So even without `restoreSettings`, the load function would try to set the mode.\n\nLet me re-think this.\n\nCurrent flow:\n1. `loadAllImageParams` sets `_isInitializingImageParams = true`\n2. Calls `loadWhiteBalance` which reads from device and sets UI\n3. `loadWhiteBalance` calls `onWbModeChange` which calls `setWhiteBalanceMode`\n4. `setWhiteBalanceMode` sends API to device\n5. After API success, shows toast\n\nThe problem is step 5: toast is shown during init.\n\nSolution:\n1. Modify `setWhiteBalanceMode` to not show toast when `_isInitializingImageParams` is true\n2. Add `restoreSettings` to load saved settings and apply them\n\nFor `restoreSettings`:\n1. GET /settings to get saved settings\n2. For each setting, call the appropriate set function (which will send API to device)\n3. The set function should check `_isInitializingImageParams` to suppress toast\n\nSo I need to modify:\n- `setWhiteBalanceMode` - check `_isInitializingImageParams` for toast\n- `setWhiteBalanceGain` - check `_isInitializingImageParams` for toast\n- `setNoiseReduce` - check `_isInitializingImageParams` for toast\n- etc.\n\nAnd add:\n- `restoreSettings` function\n- Call `restoreSettings` in `loadAllImageParams`\n\nLet me also check: does the current `loadWhiteBalance` read from device or from settings.json? It reads from device. So if device is in auto mode (factory default), it will set UI to auto. Then `restoreSettings` will override it with the saved mode.\n\nActually, I think the order should be:\n1. `loadAllImageParams` sets `_isInitializingImageParams = true`\n2. Calls `restoreSettings` first (to set saved mode)\n3. Then calls other load functions (which read from device and update UI)\n\nBut wait, if `restoreSettings` sets the mode, and then `loadWhiteBalance` reads from device, it might override the restored setting.\n\nActually, the flow should be:\n1. Load current values from device (as it does now)\n2. Then apply saved settings on top\n\nSo:\n1. `loadAllImageParams` sets `_isInitializingImageParams = true`\n2. Calls load functions (read from device, set UI)\n3. After a short delay, call `restoreSettings` (apply saved settings)\n4. After timeout, set `_isInitializingImageParams = false`\n\nLet me implement this.\n\nActually, let me just implement the core parts:\n\n1. Create `device_settings.py` - load/save functions\n2. Modify `router.py` - add GET /settings endpoint, add save call in set_* endpoints\n3. Modify `console.html` - add `restoreSettings`, modify set* functions to suppress toast\n\nLet me start coding.\n\nFor device_settings.py:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"\nAstroHub v8.45 - 设备设置记忆模块\n\n根据设备MAC保存/恢复各项参数配置。\n存储路径: data/devices/{mac}/settings.json\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_data_path_read, get_data_path_write\n\n\ndef load_settings(mac_clean: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"加载设备保存的设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: 设备设置，或 None 如果不存在\n    \"\"\"\n    path = get_data_path_read(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    if path and path.exists():\n        try:\n            with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n                return json.load(f)\n        except Exception:\n            return None\n    return None\n\n\ndef save_settings(mac_clean: str, settings: dict[str, Any]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"保存设备设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        settings: 要保存的设置\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: 是否保存成功\n    \"\"\"\n    from datetime import datetime, timezone\n\n    # 合并现有设置\n    existing = load_settings(mac_clean) or {}\n    existing.update(settings)\n    existing['last_updated'] = datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat()\n\n    path = get_data_path_write(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    try:\n        with open(path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            json.dump(existing, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n        return True\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n```\n\nFor router.py, I need to:\n1. Add import at the top\n2. Add GET endpoint\n3. Add save call in set_* endpoints\n\nFor console.html, I need to:\n1. Add `restoreSettings` function\n2. Modify `loadAllImageParams` to call it\n3. Modify set* functions to check `_isInitializingImageParams` for toast\n\nLet me now implement this.\n\nFirst, let me read the full set_whitebalance endpoint to see where to add the save call.\n\nActually, let me just do it step by step:\n\n1. Create device_settings.py\n2. Add import and GET endpoint in router.py\n3. Add save call in set_whitebalance\n4. Modify console.html\n\nLet me start.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"用户要求开始执行任务。我需要：\n1. 创建设置保存模块 `device_settings.py`\n2. 修改 `router.py` 添加保存逻辑和读取接口\n3. 修改 `console.html` 实现自动恢复和抑制弹窗\n\n让我先分析现有代码结构，然后逐步实现。\n\n**步骤 1: 创建设置保存模块**备份已完成，现在开始实现。分三步：\n\n1. 新建 `device_settings.py`\n2. 修改 `router.py`\n3. 修改 `console.html`\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_38a837f239ac40679d7789bb","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v8.45 - 设备设置记忆模块\n\n根据设备MAC保存/恢复各项参数配置。\n存储路径: data/devices/{mac}/settings.json\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_data_path_read, get_data_path_write\n\n\ndef load_settings(mac_clean: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"加载设备保存的设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: 设备设置，或 None 如果不存在\n    \"\"\"\n    path = get_data_path_read(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    if path and path.exists():\n        try:\n            with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n                return json.load(f)\n        except Exception:\n            return None\n    return None\n\n\ndef save_settings(mac_clean: str, settings: dict[str, Any]) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"保存设备设置。\n\n    Args:\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无分隔符，小写）\n        settings: 要保存的设置\n\n    Returns:\n        bool: 是否保存成功\n    \"\"\"\n    from datetime import datetime, timezone\n\n    # 合并现有设置\n    existing = load_settings(mac_clean) or {}\n    existing.update(settings)\n    existing['last_updated'] = datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat()\n\n    path = get_data_path_write(None, mac_clean, 'settings')\n    try:\n        with open(path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            json.dump(existing, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n        return True\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_settings.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1977,"output":5185,"cacheRead":96086,"cacheWrite":688,"totalTokens":103936,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783256733287,"responseId":"msg_fc342539-266d-4c8f-ac9f-7ab3d19334de"}}
