odify console.html for restore logic\n4. Update VERSION and HEARTBEAT.md\n\nThe previous exec command had a syntax error. Let me fix it and continue.\n\nActually, looking at the user's request, they want me to:\n1. Add save_settings to all set_* endpoints in router.py\n2. Add GET /settings endpoint for restoring settings\n3. Modify console.html to restore settings on connect and suppress toast\n\nLet me check which endpoints still need modification and continue."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:158","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":15,"offset":3390,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user sent \"...\" which is a continuation signal. I've been working on modifying router.py to add save_settings to each endpoint. I've completed:\n- set_whitebalance ✅\n- set_noisereduce ✅\n- update_image_settings (color) ✅\n- set_exposure ✅\n- set_shutter ✅\n\nStill need:\n- set_iris ❌\n- set_sharpness ❌\n- set_slow_shutter ❌\n- set_filter_settings (not sure if needed)\n\nAlso need:\n- GET /settings endpoint\n- Modify console.html\n\nLet me continue by reading and modifying the remaining endpoints. I'll read the iris endpoint first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:159","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Iris\", xml_str)\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\n            log_info(\"image\", \"iris\", {\"device\": device_id, \"level\": level})\n            try:\n                mac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\n                if len(mac_clean) == 12:\n                    save_settings(mac_clean, {\"iris\": {\"level\": level}})\n            except Exception:\n                pass\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"光圈已设置\"}","oldText":"        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Iris\", xml_str)\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\n            log_info(\