nding \"...\" repeatedly, which is a continuation signal. I've been working on modifying console.html to add restore logic and suppress toast during init.\n\nSo far in console.html:\n1. ✅ Modified setWhiteBalanceMode to suppress toast during init\n2. ✅ Modified setWhiteBalanceGain to suppress toast during init\n3. ✅ Modified setNoiseReduce to suppress toast during init\n\nNow I need to:\n4. Fix other set functions (setShutterSpeed, setIrisLevel, setExposureMode, setSharpness, setSlowShutter) to suppress toast during init\n5. Add restoreSettings function\n6. Call restoreSettings in loadAllImageParams\n\nLet me continue reading and modifying the console.html file. I need to find all the set functions that call showToast.\n\nActually, let me take a more efficient approach. Instead of reading and editing one by one, let me just write a Python script that modifies the console.html file to add _isInitializingImageParams checks to all showToast calls in set functions.\n\nBut the edit tool only supports exact text replacement. Let me just continue with manual editing.\n\nLet me read the remaining parts of the file to find the set functions.\n\nActually, I realize I've been spending too much time on this. Let me take a more efficient approach:\n\n1. First, read all showToast calls in the file\n2. Identify which ones are in set functions\n3. Modify them all at once\n\nLet me use a Python script to find and modify all showToast calls in set functions.</think>用户一直在催促，我需要加快速度。让我写一个Python脚本一次性修改所有需要的地方：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:198","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import re\n\nwith open('astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 1. 在setWhiteBalanceMode中抑制toast（已完成，跳过）\n# 2. 在setWhiteBalanceGain中抑制toast（已完成，跳过）\n# 3. 在setNoiseReduce中抑制toast（已完成，跳过）\n\n# 4. 修改setShutterSpeed中的showToast\ncontent = content.replace(\n    \"                showToast('success', '快门: ' + shutterLevel);\",\n    \"                if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '快门: ' + shutterLevel);\"\n)\n\n# 5. 修改setIrisLevel中的showToast\ncontent = content.replace(\n    \"                showToast('success', '光圈: ' + label);\",\n    \"                if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '光圈: ' + label);\"\n)\n\n# 6. 修改setExposureMode中的showToast\ncontent = content.replace(\n    \"                showToast('success', '曝光: ' + label);\",\n    \"                if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '曝光: ' + label);\"\n)\n\n# 7. 修改setSharpness中的showToast\ncontent = content.replace(\n    \"                showToast('success', '锐度: ' + sharpnessLevel);\",\n    \"                if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '锐度: ' + sharpnessLevel);\"\n)\n\n# 8. 修改setSlowShutter中的showToast\ncontent = content.replace(\n    \"                showToast('success', '慢快门: ' + (dssLevel === 'off' ? '关闭' : dssLevel));\",\n    \"                if (!_isInitializingImageParams) showToast('success', '慢快门: ' + (dssLevel === 'off' ? '关闭' : dssLevel));\"\n)\n\nwith open('astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint('console.html 修改完成')\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\fix_console.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user is sending \"...\" repeatedly, which is a continuation signal. I've been working on modifying console.html to add restore logic and suppress toast during init.\n\nSo far in console.html:\n1. ✅ Modified setWhiteBalanceMode to suppress toast during init\n2. ✅ Modified setWhiteBalanceGain to suppress toast during init\n3. ✅ Modified setNoiseReduce to suppress toast during init\n\nNow I need to:\n4. Fix other set functions (setShutterSpeed, setIrisLevel, setExposureMode, setSharpness, setSlowShutter) to suppress toast during init\n5. Add restoreSettings function\n6. Call restoreSettings in loadAllImageParams\n\nLet me execute the Python script I just wrote to modify all the showToast calls at once."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:199","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory && python fix_console.py","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user is sending \"...\" repeatedly, which is a continuation signal. I've been working on modifying console.html to add restore logic and suppress toast during init.\n\nSo far in console.html:\n1. ✅ Modified setWhiteBalanceMode to suppress toast during init\n2. ✅ Modified setWhiteBalanceGain to suppress toast during init\n3. ✅ Modified setNoiseReduce to suppress toast during init\n4. ✅ Modified other set functions (via Python script)\n\nNow I need to:\n5. Add restoreSettings function\n6. Call restoreSettings in loadAllImageParams\n7. Update VERSION and HEARTBEAT.md\n8. Restart and test\n\nLet me continue by adding the restoreSettings function and modifying loadAllImageParams.</think>完成！现在添加restoreSettings函数并修改loadAllImageParams：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:200","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":855,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user is sending \"...\" repeatedly, which is a continuation signal. I've been working on modifying console.html to add restore logic and suppress toast during init. I've already:\n\n1. Modified setWhiteBalanceMode to suppress toast ✅\n2. Modified setWhiteBalanceGain to suppress toast ✅\n3. Modified setNoiseReduce to suppress toast ✅\n4. Modified other set functions via Python script ✅\n\nNow I need to:\n5. Add restoreSettings function\n6. Call restoreSettings in loadAllImageParams\n7. Update VERSION and HEARTBEAT.md\n8. Restart and test\n\nLet me continue by adding the restoreSettings function. I need to read the loadAllImageParams function and modify it."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:201","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"// v8.45: 恢复保存的设置\nfunction restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings-saved').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data && Object.keys(r.data).length > 0) {\n            var s = r.data;\n            // 恢复白平衡\n            if (s.whitebalance && s.whitebalance.mode) {\n                var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n                if (wbMode) {\n                    wbMode.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\n                    onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复降噪\n            if (s.noisereduce) {\n                var dnrSpatial = document.getElementById('dnrSpatial');\n                var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');n                if (dnrSpatial && s.noisereduce.spatial_level !== undefined) dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level;\n                if (dnrTemporal && s.noisereduce.temporal_level !== undefined) dnrTemporal.value = s.noisereduce.temporal_level;\n            }\n            // 恢复慢快门\n            if (s.slow_shutter && s.slow_shutter.dss_level) {\n                var ssSelect = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n                if (ssSelect) {\n                    ssSelect.value = s.slow_shutter.dss_level;\n                    onSlowShutterChange(s.slow_shutter.dss_level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复快门\n            if (s.shutter && s.shutter.level) {\n                var shutterSelect = document.getElementById('shutterSpeed');\n                if (shutterSelect) shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;\n            }\n            // 恢复光圈\n            if (s.iris && s.iris.level) {\n                var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n                if (irisSelect) irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;\n            }\n            // 恢复曝光模式\n            if (s.exposure && s.exposure.mode) {\n                var exposureSelect = document.getElementById('exposureMode');\n                if (exposureSelect) exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;\n            }\n            // 恢复锐度\n            if (s.sharpness && s.sharpness.level !== undefined) {\n                var sharpnessInput = document.getElementById('sharpness');\n                if (sharpnessInput) sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level;\n            }\n            // 恢复画面设置\n            if (s.image_settings) {\n                var brightness = document.getElementById('brightness');\n                var contrast = document.getElementById('contrast');\n                var saturation = document.getElementById('saturation');\n                if (brightness && s.image_settings.brightness !== undefined) brightness.value = s.image_settings.brightness;\n                if (contrast && s.image_settings.contrast !== undefined) contrast.value = s.image_settings.contrast;\n                if (saturation && s.image_settings.saturation !== undefined) saturation.value = s.image_settings.saturation;\n            }\n        }\n    });\n}\n\n// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\nfunction loadAllImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    _isInitializingImageParams = true;\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n    loadFilterStatus(deviceIp);\n    loadSlowShutter(deviceIp);\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\n    // v8.45: 恢复保存的设置\n    setTimeout(function() { restoreSettings(deviceIp); }, 500);\n    // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\n}","oldText":"// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\nfunction loadAllImageParams(deviceIp) {\n    _isInitializingImageParams = true;  // v7.59: 开始初始化,禁止记录日志\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\n    loadFilterStatus(deviceIp);\n    loadSlowShutter(deviceIp);\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\n    // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\n}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user sent \"...\" again. I need to continue working on the task. I've been modifying console.html to add restore logic and suppress toast during init. I've already:\n\n1. Modified setWhiteBalanceMode to suppress toast during init ✅\n2. Modified setWhiteBalanceGain to suppress toast during init ✅\n3. Modified setNoiseReduce to suppress toast during init ✅\n4. Modified other set functions via Python script ✅\n5. Added restoreSettings function ✅ (just added)\n6. Modified loadAllImageParams to call restoreSettings ✅ (just added)\n\nNow I need to:\n7. Update VERSION and HEARTBEAT.md\n8. Restart and test\n9. Clean up temporary files\n\nLet me continue by updating VERSION and HEARTBEAT.md, then restarting the service.\n\nBut wait, the edit for loadAllImageParams may have failed because the oldText didn't match exactly. Let me check.\n\nActually, looking at the edit result, it says \"Successfully replaced 1 block(s)\". So the edit succeeded!\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Update VERSION to v8.46\n2. Update HEARTBEAT.md\n3. Clean up temporary files\n4. Restart service\n5. Test\n\nLet me continue."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:202","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":5,"offset":13,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\main\\constants.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user is sending \"...\" repeatedly, which is a continuation signal. I've been working on the device settings memory feature. Let me review what I've done and what remains:\n\nDone:\n1. ✅ Created `src/advanced/device_settings.py`\n2. ✅ Modified `router.py`:\n   - Added import for device_settings\n   - Modified all set_* endpoints to save settings\n   - Added GET /settings-saved endpoint\n3. ✅ Modified `console.html`:\n   - Suppressed toast in set functions during init\n   - Added restoreSettings function\n   - Modified loadAllImageParams to call restoreSettings\n\nRemaining:\n1. Update VERSION (currently v8.45, need to update to v8.46)\n2. Update HEARTBEAT.md\n3. Clean up temporary files\n4. Restart service\n5. Test\n\nLet me continue by updating VERSION and HEARTBEAT.md.</think>用户继续发送\"...\"，我需要继续完成任务。我已经完成了大部分工作，现在需要更新版本号、清理临时文件并重启服务。继续执行：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:203","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"VERSION = \"v8.46\"","oldText":"VERSION = \"v8.45\""}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\main\\constants.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:204","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## v8.46 设备参数记忆（2026-07-05）\n\n### 完成的任务\n1. ✅ 新建 device_settings.py - 按MAC保存/恢复设备参数\n2. ✅ router.py: 修改8个set_*端点，成功PUT后自动保存到settings.json\n3. ✅ router.py: 新增GET /settings-saved端点，读取保存的参数\n4. ✅ console.html: 所有set函数在初始化时抑制toast\n5. ✅ console.html: 添加restoreSettings函数，连接设备时自动恢复参数\n\n### 修改的文件\n- `astrohub/src/advanced/device_settings.py` — 新增，设备设置读写\n- `astrohub/src/api/router.py` — 8个端点添加save_settings，新增GET端点\n- `astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html` — 抑制toast，恢复设置\n- `astrohub/src/main/constants.py` — VERSION v8.45→v8.46\n\n### 技术细节\n- **存储路径**: `data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n- **保存时机**: 每个set_*端点成功PUT后自动保存\n- **恢复时机**: `loadAllImageParams` 完成设备读取后，500ms延迟恢复\n- **抑制toast**: `_isInitializingImageParams` 标志控制\n\n---","oldText":"---"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user sent \"...\" again. I need to continue working on the task. I've been working on the device settings memory feature. I've already:\n\n1. Created `src/advanced/device_settings.py` ✅\n2. Modified `router.py` to save settings in all set_* endpoints ✅\n3. Added GET /settings-saved endpoint ✅\n4. Modified `console.html` to suppress toast during init ✅\n5. Added `restoreSettings` function ✅\n6. Modified `loadAllImageParams` to call `restoreSettings` ✅\n7. Updated VERSION to v8.46 ✅\n8. Updated HEARTBEAT.md ✅\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Clean up temporary files\n2. Restart the service\n3. Test the functionality\n\nLet me continue by cleaning up temporary files and restarting the service.</think>用户继续发送\"...\"，催促我完成任务。我需要清理临时文件并重启服务。\n\n已完成工作：\n1. ✅ 新建 device_settings.py\n2. ✅ 修改 router.py 8个端点 + GET端点\n3. ✅ 修改 console.html 抑制toast + 恢复设置\n4. ✅ 更新 VERSION 到 v8.46\n5. ✅ 更新 HEARTBEAT.md\n\n现在需要：\n- 清理临时文件\n- 重启服务\n- 测试\n\n让我继续执行。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:205","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Remove-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\fix_console.py\", \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\find_returns.py\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; Write-Host \"Cleaned up temp files\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"The user is sending \"...\" repeatedly, which is a continuation signal. I've been working on the device settings memory feature. I've completed all the code changes and need to:\n\n1. ✅ Created `src/advanced/device_settings.py`\n2. ✅ Modified `router.py` to save settings in all set_* endpoints\n3. ✅ Added GET /settings-saved endpoint\n4. ✅ Modified `console.html` to suppress toast during init\n5. ✅ Added `restoreSettings` function\n6. ✅ Modified `loadAllImageParams` to call `restoreSettings`\n7. ✅ Updated VERSION to v8.46\n8. ✅ Updated HEARTBEAT.md\n\nNow I need to:\n9. Clean up temporary files ✅ (just done)\n10. Restart the service\n11. Test the functionality\n\nLet me restart the service and test.</think>用户继续催促。我已经完成了所有代码修改，现在需要重启服务并测试。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:206","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub 