-saved` 端点\n\n**③ 修改 `src/web/includes/console.html`**\n- 所有 set 函数在 `_isInitializingImageParams=true` 时抑制 toast\n- 新增 `restoreSettings(deviceIp)` 函数，从 settings.json 恢复参数\n- `loadAllImageParams()` 完成设备读取后 500ms 调用恢复\n\n**④ VERSION**: v8.45 → v8.46\n\n### 验证\n- ✅ 模块导入测试通过（Router import OK）\n- ✅ 代码无语法错误\n\n### 重启服务后测试\n1. 修改任意参数（白平衡、快门等）\n2. 断开设备\n3. 重新连接同一设备\n4. 验证参数是否自动恢复"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":117889,"output":25875,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783257759271,"responseId":"cht000d28af@dx19f32720eb82871503"}}
