{"type":"message","id":"ad74cbad","parentId":"3a99a988","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:42:13.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我继续执行任务。我需要：\n1. 更新HEARTBEAT.md，反映当前版本v8.46和状态\n2. 重启服务使新代码生效\n3. 测试设备参数记忆功能\n\n首先更新HEARTBEAT.md，然后重启服务。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4bae401a5b3b448caac490aa","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"**最后更新**: 2026-07-05 20:15\n**状态**: v8.46 设备参数记忆功能完成\n**当前版本**: v8.46\n\n---\n\n## v8.46 设备参数记忆（2026-07-05）\n\n### 完成的功能\n1. ✅ 设备参数自动保存到 `data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n2. ✅ 连接设备时自动恢复上次保存的参数\n3. ✅ 初始化期间抑制toast弹窗，避免误报\n\n### 支持的参数记忆\n- 白平衡（模式 + R/B增益）\n- 降噪（空域/时域等级）\n- 曝光模式\n- 快门速度\n- 光圈等级\n- 锐化等级\n- 慢快门（DSS倍率）\n- 画面设置（亮度/对比度/饱和度）\n\n### 技术实现\n- `device_settings.py`: save_device_settings() / load_device_settings()\n- `router.py`: 8个设置端点成功PUT后自动保存\n- `router.py`: GET `/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings-saved` 读取保存的参数\n- `console.html`: loadAllImageParams() 完成后500ms调用restoreSettings()\n- `console.html`: 所有set函数在 _isInitializingImageParams=true 时抑制toast\n\n### 测试方法\n1. 修改任意图像参数（如白平衡模式、慢快门倍率）\n2. 断开设备连接\n3. 重新连接设备\n4. 观察参数是否自动恢复，且无弹窗提示\n\n---\n\n## v8.45 慢快门迁移DSS（2026-07-05）","oldText":"**最后更新**: 2026-07-05 19:52\n**状态**: v8.45 慢快门迁移DSS完成\n**当前版本**: v8.45\n\n---\n\n## v8.45 慢快门迁移DSS（2026-07-05）"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":792,"output":606,"cacheRead":188858,"cacheWrite":284,"totalTokens":190540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783258903274,"responseId":"msg_506725dd-7e23-4157-91a5-effcf1fb92a6"}}
