{"type":"message","id":"70ce094d","parentId":"08d5101d","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:45:05.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"服务正常运行。settings-saved端点返回空数据（因为还没有保存过设置）。\n\n## ✅ v8.46 设备参数记忆功能完成\n\n### 已完成的修改\n\n| 文件 | 修改内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| `src/advanced/device_settings.py` | 新增：`save_device_settings()` / `load_device_settings()` |\n| `src/api/router.py` | 8个端点添加自动保存：whitebalance, noisereduce, exposure, shutter, iris, sharpness, slow_shutter, image_settings |\n| `src/api/router.py` | 新增GET `/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings-saved` 端点 |\n| `src/web/includes/console.html` | 所有set函数在 `_isInitializingImageParams=true` 时抑制toast |\n| `src/web/includes/console.html` | 新增 `restoreSettings()` 函数，设备重连时自动恢复参数 |\n| `src/main/constants.py` | VERSION v8.45→v8.46 |\n\n### 支持的参数\n白平衡模式 + R/B增益、降噪（空域/时域）、曝光模式、快门、光圈、锐度、慢快门（DSS）、亮度/对比度/饱和度\n\n### 工作机制\n```\n设置参数 → PUT API → 设备接受 → 自动保存到 settings.json\n连接设备 → loadAllImageParams() → 500ms后 restoreSettings() → 恢复参数（无弹窗）\n```\n\n### 测试方法\n1. 修改任意参数（如白平衡为手动、慢快门*4）\n2. 断开设备\n3. 重新连接\n4. 验证参数已恢复，无\"白平衡自动\"弹窗"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":468,"output":375,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":171091,"totalTokens":171934,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783259080943,"responseId":"msg_879b9190-9ba2-4801-a97a-f8775028dc85"}}
