{"type":"message","id":"0fb20ac9","parentId":"c633ca89","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:48:58.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我继续。从之前的上下文来看，我们正在测试设备参数记忆功能（v8.46）。\n\n让我分析当前状态：\n\n1. settings.json 文件已存在，包含白平衡、降噪、慢快门的设置\n2. 之前测试了设置白平衡和降噪，它们被成功保存\n3. 现在我需要继续测试其他参数：曝光模式、快门、光圈、锐度、画面设置等\n\n从代码分析来看，router.py 中有8个端点添加了保存逻辑：\n- image_settings (1439行) - 画面设置（亮度/对比度/饱和度）\n- whitebalance (2989行) - 白平衡\n- noisereduce (3092行) - 降噪\n- exposure (3250行) - 曝光模式\n- shutter (3337行) - 快门\n- iris (3416行) - 光圈\n- sharpness (3564行) - 锐度\n- slow_shutter (3770行) - 慢快门\n\n当前 settings.json 已经包含：\n- whitebalance: mode=manual, red_gain=200, blue_gain=51\n- noisereduce: spatial_level=75, temporal_level=6\n- slow_shutter: dss_level=*4, enabled=true\n\n我需要继续测试剩余的参数，确保它们都能正确保存。我应该：\n1. 测试设置曝光模式\n2. 测试设置快门速度\n3. 测试设置光圈\n4. 测试设置锐度\n5. 测试设置画面参数（亮度/对比度/饱和度）\n6. 最后验证 settings.json 包含所有设置\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"settings.json 正常保存了白平衡、降噪和慢快门。继续测试其他参数：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cd04087c09804d2db78a99fe","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"\nimport requests\n\nbase = 'http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/240f9b764193'\n\n# 测试曝光模式\nr = requests.post(f'{base}/image/exposure', json={'mode': 'manual'})\nprint('曝光模式:', r.json())\n\n# 测试快门速度\nr = requests.post(f'{base}/image/shutter', json={'level': '1/500'})\nprint('快门:', r.json())\n\n# 测试光圈\nr = requests.post(f'{base}/image/iris', json={'level': 160})\nprint('光圈:', r.json())\n\n# 测试锐度\nr = requests.post(f'{base}/image/sharpness', json={'level': 60})\nprint('锐度:', r.json())\n\n# 测试画面设置（亮度/对比度/饱和度）\nr = requests.put(f'{base}/image/settings', json={'brightness': 55, 'contrast': 52, 'saturation': 58})\nprint('画面设置:', r.json())\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2135,"output":706,"cacheRead":1957