{"type":"message","id":"e13d12e5","parentId":"81a3cad6","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:55:21.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the file, I can see there's a restoreSettings function. Let me check if it's being called properly when devices connect.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02cfcda6359d4d9497f2ac63","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":855,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":21182,"output":76,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21258,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783259699369,"responseId":"cht000d2cec@dx19f328fd3632872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"db3fc9cc","parentId":"e13d12e5","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:55:21.197Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_02cfcda6359d4d9497f2ac63","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// v8.45: 恢复保存的设置\r\nfunction restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings-saved').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data && Object.keys(r.data).length > 0) {\r\n            var s = r.data;\r\n            // 恢复白平衡\r\n            if (s.whitebalance && s.whitebalance.mode) {\r\n                var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n                if (wbMode) {\r\n                    wbMode.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\r\n                    onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复降噪\r\n            if (s.noisereduce) {\r\n                var dnrSpatial = document.getElementById('dnrSpatial');\r\n                var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');n                if (dnrSpatial && s.noisereduce.spatial_level !== undefined) dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level;\r\n                if (dnrTemporal && s.noisereduce.temporal_level !== undefined) dnrTemporal.value = s.noisereduce.temporal_level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复慢快门\r\n            if (s.slow_shutter && s.slow_shutter.dss_level) {\r\n                var ssSelect = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\r\n                if (ssSelect) {\r\n                    ssSelect.value = s.slow_shutter.dss_level;\r\n                    onSlowShutterChange(s.slow_shutter.dss_level);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复快门\r\n            if (s.shutter && s.shutter.level) {\r\n                var shutterSelect = document.getElementById('shutterSpeed');\r\n                if (shutterSelect) shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复光圈\r\n            if (s.iris && s.iris.level) {\r\n                var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\r\n                if (irisSelect) irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复曝光模式\r\n            if (s.exposure && s.exposure.mode) {\r\n                var exposureSelect = document.getElementById('exposureMode');\r\n                if (exposureSelect) exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复锐度\r\n            if (s.sharpness && s.sharpness.level !== undefined) {\r\n                var sharpnessInput = document.getElementById('sharpness');\r\n                if (sharpnessInput) sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复画面设置\r\n            if (s.image_settings) {\r\n                var brightness = document.getElementById('brightness');\r\n                var contrast = document.getElementById('contrast');\r\n                var saturation = document.getElementById('saturation');\r\n                if (brightness && s.image_settings.brightness !== undefined) brightness.value = s.image_settings.brightness;\r\n                if (contrast && s.image_settings.contrast !== undefined) contrast.value = s.image_settings.contrast;\r\n                if (saturation && s.image_settings.saturation !== undefined) saturation.value = s.image_settings.saturation;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\r\nfunction loadAllImageParams(deviceIp) {\r\n    _isInitializingImageParams = true;\r\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\r\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\r\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\r\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\r\n    loadFilterStatus(deviceIp);\r\n    loadSlowShutter(deviceIp);\r\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\r\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\r\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\r\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\r\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\r\n    // v8.45: 恢复保存的设置\r\n    setTimeout(function() { restoreSettings(deviceIp); }, 500);\r\n    // v7.59: 延迟结束初始化标志(等待异步加载完成)\r\n    setTimeout(function() { _isInitializingImageParams = false; }, 3000);\r\n}\r\n\r\n\n[1155 more lines in file. Use offset=935 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783259721197}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1747670","parentId":"db3fc9cc","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:55:52.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the current state:\n\n1. The code changes are all in place\n2. The settings.json file exists with saved parameters\n3. The restoreSettings function is properly implemented and called in loadAllImageParams\n4. The shutter setting failed with HTTP 400\n\nLooking at the restoreSettings function, I notice that:\n- It only sets the UI values, but doesn't actually call the backend API to apply the settings to the device\n- For example, `onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode)` is called which triggers `setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')` - this sends the API call\n- But for others like noise reduce, shutter, iris, etc., it only sets the DOM values without calling the API\n\nActually wait, let me re-read:\n- Whitebalance: `wbMode.value = ...` then `onWbModeChange(...)` → this triggers API call ✅\n- Noise reduce: Only sets DOM values, no API call ❌\n- Slow shutter: `ssSelect.value = ...` then `onSlowShutterChange(...)` → this might trigger API call\n- Shutter: Only sets DOM value, no API call ❌\n- Iris: Only sets DOM value, no API call ❌\n- Exposure: Only sets DOM value, no API call ❌\n- Sharpness: Only sets DOM value, no API call ❌\n- Image settings: Only sets DOM values, no API call ❌\n\nWait, but maybe the select/input onchange events will fire? Let me check - when you set `element.value` programmatically, it does NOT fire the onchange event. So noise reduce, shutter, iris, exposure, sharpness, and image settings are only being restored in the UI but not actually applied to the device.\n\nActually, let me reconsider - the `onWbModeChange` is called explicitly with the value. And `onSlowShutterChange` is also called explicitly. But the others are just setting DOM values without triggering any events.\n\nSo there's a bug in the restoreSettings function: most settings are only restoring the UI values but not actually sending API calls to apply them to the device.\n\nWait, but actually the `isInitializingImageParams` flag is set to true, so if the onchange events do fire, they won't show toasts. But the question is whether they fire at all.\n\nLet me check: for the `shutterSpeed` select,\n- It probably has `onchange=\"setShutter(this.value)\"` or similar\n- But setting `.value` programmatically does NOT trigger onchange\n\nSo yes, there's a real bug - the restore doesn't actually apply the settings to the device for most parameters.\n\nBut wait, the user just said \"继续，测试\" - they want me to test. Let me focus on testing what we have and report the issues.\n\nActually, now I realize the real issue - the user wants me to continue testing. Let me check if the service is running and test the restore flow.\n\nLet me look at what's actually happening. The current settings.json has these values saved:\n- whitebalance: mode=manual, red_gain=200, blue_gain=51\n- noisereduce: spatial=75, temporal=6\n- slow_shutter: dss=*4, enabled=true\n- exposure: mode=manual\n- iris: level=160\n- sharpness: level=60\n- image_settings: brightness=55, contrast=52, saturation=58\n\nNo shutter (failed with 400).\n\nFor testing, I should:\n1. Verify settings.json is being properly saved\n2. Test the settings-saved endpoint \n3. Test restoring settings\n\nThe restoreSettings function has a flaw - for most settings it only sets DOM values without triggering API calls. But the onchange event handlers should fire when the value changes... actually, NO, programmatic value changes don't fire onchange events.\n\nWait, but this is not a bug I should fix right now - the user asked me to test, not fix things. Let me focus on testing and reporting what works and what doesn't.\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the restoreSettings function, I notice that for `onWbModeChange` and `onSlowShutterChange`, these are called explicitly and will trigger API calls. But for noise reduce, shutter, iris, exposure, sharpness, and image settings, only DOM values are set - and the actual API calls would need to be triggered.\n\nHmm, but wait - maybe the onchange handlers work differently. Let me check if the select/input elements have onchange attributes that call the set functions.\n\nActually let me reconsider. The user's core request was about memory. The restore does set the UI values. When the user manually changes them later, the settings are already pre-set. But the ACTUAL device settings aren't applied on restore.\n\nThis IS a bug. But maybe I should:\n1. First test what works\n2. Then report the finding\n\nOK let me just do the testing. The user wants me to test. I should:\n1. Check if the service is running\n2. Verify settings-saved endpoint returns the saved data\n3. Try to test the full restore flow\n\nBut actually, testing the full restore flow requires disconnecting and reconnecting the device. That's a bit involved. Let me just verify that:\n1. The settings-saved endpoint works\n2. The save mechanism works (already confirmed)\n3. Report the restore function behavior\n\nLet me run the test verification.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"`restoreSettings()` 有一个问题：大部分参数只设置了DOM值但没触发API调用。\n\n| 参数 | DOM设置 | API调用 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| 白平衡 | ✅ `onWbModeChange()` | ✅ |\n| 慢快门 | ✅ `onSlowShutterChange()` | ✅ |\n| 降噪 | ✅ 仅设值 | ❌ 无API调用 |\n| 快门 | ✅ 仅设值 | ❌ |\n| 光圈 | ✅ 仅设值 | ❌ |\n| 曝光 | ✅ 仅设值 | ❌ |\n| 锐度 | ✅ 仅设值 | ❌ |\n| 画面设置 | ✅ 仅设值 | ❌ |\n\n需要让 `restoreSettings()` 在设置DOM值后显式调用API。修复如下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TCAZwniVvRIQPqaIZbYr4710","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":5,"offset":878,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":24075,"output":1425,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timest