{"type":"message","id":"50988153","parentId":"bf9d8eb1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:56:15.566Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要查看现有的设置函数，了解如何正确触发API调用：\n\n1. 降噪 - `setNoiseReduce(channel, value)` - 调用 `/api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/noisereduce`\n2. 快门 - `setShutter(value)` - 调用 `/api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/shutter`\n3. 光圈 - `setIris(value)` - 调用 `/api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/iris`\n4. 曝光 - `setExposureMode(mode)` - 调用 `/api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/exposure`\n5. 锐度 - `setSharpness(value)` - 调用 `/api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/sharpness`\n6. 画面设置 - 可能没有单独的函数，需要查看\n7. 白平衡增益 - `setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value)` - 调用 `/api/v1/ptz/{dev}/image/whitebalance`\n\n让我查看这些函数的签名和调用方式。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"...\n我需要修复 `restoreSettings()` 函数，让它不仅设置DOM值，还要调用API将设置应用到设备。让我先查看现有的设置函数：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_93bb2820d5d04c98b6aa08f7","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1502,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_7ae767e84596418888e75149","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1750,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5ffd58cac66449d690ff0f80","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1810,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1534,"output":491,"cacheRead":25779,"cacheWrite":380,"totalTokens":28184,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783259761709,"responseId":"msg_d8b43b64-89e7-4b19-9229-f0927fceec68"}}
