{"type":"message","id":"1a8ee109","parentId":"45a5b79e","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:56:15.627Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_7ae767e84596418888e75149","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            // 中文标签\r\n            var labelMap = {\r\n                'manual': '手动',\r\n                'auto': '自动',\r\n                'IrisFirst': '光圈优先',\r\n                'ShutterFirst': '快门优先'\r\n            };\r\n            opt.textContent = labelMap[p] || p;\r\n            select.appendChild(opt);\r\n        });\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // 获取当前值\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/exposure').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n            if (select && r.data.mode) {\r\n                select.value = r.data.mode;\r\n                // 更新快门光圈禁用状态\r\n                updateShutterIrisState();\r\n            }\r\n\n[320 more lines in file. Use offset=1770 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783259775626}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ba91081","parentId":"1a8ee109","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:56:15.627Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_5ffd58cac66449d690ff0f80","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    if (!exposureMode || !shutterSelect || !irisSelect) return;\r\n\r\n    // v7.54: 支持多种曝光模式\r\n    var mode = exposureMode.value;\r\n    var shutterEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst');\r\n    var irisEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'IrisFirst');\r\n    var gainEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst' || mode === 'IrisFirst');\r\n    shutterSelect.disabled = !shutterEnabled;\r\n    irisSelect.disabled = !irisEnabled;\r\n    if (gainSlider) gainSlider.disabled = !gainEnabled;\r\n\r\n    // v8.40: 自动模式时隐藏快门/光圈/增益\r\n    var shutterRow = shutterSelect.parentElement.parentElement;\r\n    var gainRow = gainSlider ? gainSlider.parentElement : null;\r\n    if (mode === 'auto') {\r\n        shutterRow.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (gainRow) gainRow.style.display = 'none';\r\n    } else {\r\n        shutterRow.style.display = '';\r\n        if (gainRow) gainRow.style.display = '';\r\n\n[260 more lines in file. Use offset=1830 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783259775627}}
{"type":"message","id":"a638c5d8","parentId":"7ba91081","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:56:40.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue testing. Let me understand the current state:\n\n1. `restoreSettings()` function only sets DOM values but doesn't call the API to apply settings to the device\n2. I need to fix it so that when settings are restored, they actually get applied to the device via API calls\n\nLet me look at the current `restoreSettings()` function and understand what needs to be changed:\n- White balance: calls `onWbModeChange()` which triggers `setWhiteBalanceMode()` - this should already call the API\n- Noise reduce: only sets DOM values\n- Slow shutter: calls `onSlowShutterChange()` which should trigger API\n- Shutter: only sets DOM value\n- Iris: only sets DOM value\n- Exposure: only sets DOM value\n- Sharpness: only sets DOM value\n- Image settings: only sets DOM values\n\nI need to add API calls after setting DOM values for the parameters that don't trigger API calls.\n\nLet me read the full restoreSettings function first, then fix it.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在修复 `restoreSettings()` 让它不仅设置DOM值，还要调用API应用到设备：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e2c0e20e66e34c87afed177c","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":856,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":662,"output":316,"cacheRead":26159,"cacheWrite":2020,"totalTokens":29157,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783259775628,"responseId":"msg_480fecb4-82fa-4db5-b462-81b96f649306"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4af0aa0","parentId":"a638c5d8","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:56:40.043Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e2c0e20e66e34c87afed177c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings-saved').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data && Object.keys(r.data).length > 0) {\r\n            var s = r.data;\r\n            // 恢复白平衡\r\n            if (s.whitebalance && s.whitebalance.mode) {\r\n                var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n                if (wbMode) {\r\n                    wbMode.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\r\n                    onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复降噪\r\n            if (s.noisereduce) {\r\n                var dnrSpatial = document.getElementById('dnrSpatial');\r\n                var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');n                if (dnrSpatial && s.noisereduce.spatial_level !== undefined) dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level;\r\n                if (dnrTemporal && s.noisereduce.temporal_level !== undefined) dnrTemporal.value = s.noisereduce.temporal_level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复慢快门\r\n            if (s.slow_shutter && s.slow_shutter.dss_level) {\r\n                var ssSelect = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\r\n                if (ssSelect) {\r\n                    ssSelect.value = s.slow_shutter.dss_level;\r\n                    onSlowShutterChange(s.slow_shutter.dss_level);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复快门\r\n            if (s.shutter && s.shutter.level) {\r\n                var shutterSelect = document.getElementById('shutterSpeed');\r\n                if (shutterSelect) shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复光圈\r\n            if (s.iris && s.iris.level) {\r\n                var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\r\n                if (irisSelect) irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复曝光模式\r\n            if (s.exposure && s.exposure.mode) {\r\n                var exposureSelect = document.getElementById('exposureMode');\r\n                if (exposureSelect) exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复锐度\r\n            if (s.sharpness && s.sharpness.level !== undefined) {\r\n                var sharpnessInput = document.getElementById('sharpness');\r\n                if (sharpnessInput) sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复画面设置\r\n            if (s.image_settings) {\r\n                var brightness = document.getElementById('brightness');\r\n                var contrast = document.getElementById('contrast');\r\n                var saturation = document.getElementById('saturation');\r\n                if (brightness && s.image_settings.brightness !== undefined) brightness.value = s.image_settings.brightness;\r\n                if (contrast && s.image_settings.contrast !== undefined) contrast.value = s.image_settings.contrast;\r\n                if (saturation && s.image_settings.saturation !== undefined) saturation.value = s.image_settings.saturation;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\r\n\n[1174 more lines in file. Use offset=916 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783259800043}}
{"type":"message","id":"e71c2b4e","parentId":"d4af0aa0","timestamp":"2026-07-05T13:56:51.003Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue testing the device parameter memory feature. I've already analyzed the code and found that `restoreSettings()` only sets DOM values but doesn't call the API to apply settings to the device.\n\nLooking at the code:\n- White balance: calls `onWbModeChange()` which should trigger API calls\n- Noise reduce: only sets DOM values, no API call\n- Slow shutter: calls `onSlowShutterChange()` which should trigger API call\n- Shutter, Iris, Exposure, Sharpness, Image settings: only set DOM values\n\nI need to fix `restoreSettings()` to actually call the APIs to apply the settings to the device. Let me look at what API functions are available:\n- `setWhiteBalanceMode(mode)` - for white balance mode\n- `setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value)` - for R/B gain\n- `setNoiseReduce(channel, value)` - for noise reduce\n- `onSlowShutterChange(level)` - already called\n- `setShutter(level)` - for shutter\n- `setIris(level)` - for iris\n- `setExposureMode(mode)` - for exposure\n- `setSharpness(level)` - for sharpness\n- For image settings (brightness/contrast/saturation), need to check\n\nLet me fix the restoreSettings function to call the APIs.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n- `onWbModeChange` is called - this should trigger `setWhiteBalanceMode`\n- But for gains, there's no API call\n- For noise reduce, no API call\n- For shutter, iris, exposure, sharpness, image settings - no API calls\n\nI need to add API calls for all these.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"修复 `restoreSettings()` 使其真正调用API应用到设备：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cb8ce075044346f4ae3f9180","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":856,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7