{"type":"message","id":"16107115","parentId":"ca8e20a5","timestamp":"2026-07-05T14:24:14.728Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"完成了？\" (Is it done?). Let me assess the current state:\n\n1. v8.46 device parameter memory feature - backend save/load is done ✅\n2. The `restoreSettings()` function has a bug - it only sets DOM values but doesn't call APIs to apply settings to the device\n3. I couldn't fix the bug because memory flush restricted writes to memory/2026-07-05.md only\n\nNow the memory flush is happening again. The user wants to know if it's done. I need to be honest - it's NOT done because the restoreSettings() bug hasn't been fixed.\n\nLet me append the current status to memory and reply to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**没有完成。** 还有一个关键bug没修。\n\n## 当前状态\n\n| 模块 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 后端保存设置 | ✅ 已完成 |\n| 后端读取设置 | ✅ 已完成 |\n| settings-saved端点 | ✅ 正常 |\n| Toast抑制 | ✅ 正常 |\n| **restoreSettings() 恢复应用到设备** | 🔴 **未修复** |\n\n## 阻塞问题\n\n`restoreSettings()` 函数只设置DOM值，**没有调用API把设置真正应用到设备**。加上有一个typo（`dnrTemporal');n` 多了个n），会导致JS报错。\n\n**现在记忆刷新中，无法写源代码。刷新完成后我立即修复。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":314,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":35168,"totalTokens":35488,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783261445742,"responseId":"msg_b6b095d3-3c59-4bcf-93c3-89df2f15277c"}}
