{"type":"message","id":"156a30c6","parentId":"d2ba7748","timestamp":"2026-07-05T14:24:50.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n\nThe user is asking me to report the issues I encountered. Let me think about what problems I've been facing:\n\n1. **Memory flush restrictions** - During memory flush, I can only write to memory files, not to source code files. This prevented me from fixing the `restoreSettings()` bug in console.html.\n\n2. **The actual bug I need to fix** - The `restoreSettings()` function in console.html has two issues:\n   - A typo: `var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');n` has a stray `n` at the end\n   - Missing API calls - it only sets DOM values but doesn't call the actual API functions to apply settings to the device\n\n3. **The fix I need to make** - I need to modify `restoreSettings()` to call API functions after setting DOM values:\n   - setWhiteBalanceGain('red', value) and setWhiteBalanceGain('blue', value)\n   - setNoiseReduce('spatial', value) and setNoiseReduce('temporal', value)\n   - setShutterSpeed(value)\n   - setIris(value)\n   - setExposureMode(mode)\n   - setSharpness(value)\n   - apiPut for image settings\n\n4. **Testing issues** - When I tried to test shutter settings, I got HTTP 400 errors, suggesting the device doesn't support certain shutter values.\n\nLet me also think about what the user wants me to do:\n- Report issues\n- Then fix them\n\nSince the memory flush restriction is lifted (user is asking me to report issues), I can now proceed with the fix.\n老板，问题汇总：\n\n## 问题1：`restoreSettings()` 函数只设DOM值，没调API应用设置\n\n**现状**：函数读取保存的设置后，只更新了页面上的下拉框/输入框，但**没有调用后端API把设置真正应用到设备**。\n\n**需要修改的地方**：console.html 的 `restoreSettings()` 函数（约856行）\n\n| 参数 | 当前做法 | 应该做的 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 曝光模式 | 只设`exposureMode.value` | 还要调`setExposureMode(mode)` |\n| 快门 | 只设`shutterSpeed.value` | 还要调`setShutterSpeed(level)` |\n| 光圈 | 只设`irisLevel.value` | 还要调`setIris(level)` |\n|