{"type":"message","id":"51337c1a","parentId":"9359f248","timestamp":"2026-07-05T14:31:31.983Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_673078a5458c48b5b7e22d56","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings-saved').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data && Object.keys(r.data).length > 0) {\r\n            var s = r.data;\r\n            // 恢复白平衡\r\n            if (s.whitebalance && s.whitebalance.mode) {\r\n                var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n                if (wbMode) {\r\n                    wbMode.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\r\n                    onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复降噪\r\n            if (s.noisereduce) {\r\n                var dnrSpatial = document.getElementById('dnrSpatial');\r\n                var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');n                if (dnrSpatial && s.noisereduce.spatial_level !== undefined) dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level;\r\n                if (dnrTemporal && s.noisereduce.temporal_level !== undefined) dnrTemporal.value = s.noisereduce.temporal_level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复慢快门\r\n            if (s.slow_shutter && s.slow_shutter.dss_level) {\r\n                var ssSelect = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\r\n                if (ssSelect) {\r\n                    ssSelect.value = s.slow_shutter.dss_level;\r\n                    onSlowShutterChange(s.slow_shutter.dss_level);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复快门\r\n            if (s.shutter && s.shutter.level) {\r\n                var shutterSelect = document.getElementById('shutterSpeed');\r\n                if (shutterSelect) shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复光圈\r\n            if (s.iris && s.iris.level) {\r\n                var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\r\n                if (irisSelect) irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复曝光模式\r\n            if (s.exposure && s.exposure.mode) {\r\n                var exposureSelect = document.getElementById('exposureMode');\r\n                if (exposureSelect) exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复锐度\r\n            if (s.sharpness && s.sharpness.level !== undefined) {\r\n                var sharpnessInput = document.getElementById('sharpness');\r\n                if (sharpnessInput) sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level;\r\n            }\r\n            // 恢复画面设置\r\n            if (s.image_settings) {\r\n                var brightness = document.getElementById('brightness');\r\n                var contrast = document.getElementById('contrast');\r\n                var saturation = document.getElementById('saturation');\r\n                if (brightness && s.image_settings.brightness !== undefined) brightness.value = s.image_settings.brightness;\r\n                if (contrast && s.image_settings.contrast !== undefined) contrast.value = s.image_settings.contrast;\r\n                if (saturation && s.image_settings.saturation !== undefined) saturation.value = s.image_settings.saturation;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\r\n\n[1174 more lines in file. Use offset=916 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783261891983}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f2cea4c","parentId":"51337c1a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T14:32:42.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Check what I need to fix in restoreSettings():\n1. Fix the typo: `var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');n` → `var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');` (remove the `n`)\n2. Add API calls after setting DOM values:\n   - Shutter: `shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;` → `shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level; setShutterSpeed(s.shutter.level);`\n   - Iris: `irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;` → `irisSelect.value = s.iris.level; setIris(s.iris.level);`\n   - Exposure: `exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;` → `exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode; setExposureMode(s.exposure.mode); updateShutterIrisState();`\n   - White balance gains: need to add red_gain and blue_gain handling\n   - DNR (noise reduce): `dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level;` → `dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level; setNoiseReduce('spatial', s.noisereduce.spatial_level);` (and temp)\n   - Sharpness: `sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level;` → `sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level; setSharpness(s.sharpness.level);`\n   - Image settings: brightness/contrast/saturation values → `apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings', imgData)`\n\nI notice that:\n- `onWbModeChange()` and `onSlowShutterChange()` already call the APIs internally, so I don't need to add extra calls for those\n\n\n- Both functions hide CSV columns '白平衡模式和参数' and '控制方式' via logic in their onchange handlers, since they're built using two-level column filtering\n\nI'm confirming that `loadAllImageParams()` already sets `_isInitializingImageParams = true` and calls `restoreSettings()` after a 500ms delay, so there's no initialization toast suppression needed in restoreSettings itself.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"确认当前代码。**只修复以下3处**：\n\n1. Typo：`dnrTemporal');n` → `dnrTemporal');`\n2. 快门：设置DOM后加 `setShutterSpeed()`\n3. 光圈：设置DOM后加 `setIris()`\n4. 曝光模式：设置DOM后加 `setExposureMode()` + `updateShutterIrisState()`\n5. 白平衡增益：设定值后加 `setWhiteBalanceGain()`\n6. 降噪：设定值后加 `setNoiseReduce()`\n7. 锐度：设置DOM后加 `setSharpness()`\n8. 画面设置：计算brightness/contrast/saturation后加 `apiPut(...)`"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9c3eff2c2b8f41ed9d689268","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"function restoreSettings(deviceIp) {\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings-saved').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success && r.data && Object.keys(r.data).length > 0) {\n            var s = r.data;\n            // 恢复曝光模式\n            if (s.exposure && s.exposure.mode) {\n                var exposureSelect = document.getElementById('exposureMode');\n                if (exposureSelect) {\n                    exposureSelect.value = s.exposure.mode;\n                    setExposureMode(s.exposure.mode);\n                    updateShutterIrisState();\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复快门\n            if (s.shutter && s.shutter.level) {\n                var shutterSelect = document.getElementById('shutterSpeed');\n                if (shutterSelect) {\n                    shutterSelect.value = s.shutter.level;\n                    setShutterSpeed(s.shutter.level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复光圈\n            if (s.iris && s.iris.level) {\n                var irisSelect = document.getElementById('irisLevel');\n                if (irisSelect) {\n                    irisSelect.value = s.iris.level;\n                    setIris(s.iris.level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复白平衡\n            if (s.whitebalance && s.whitebalance.mode) {\n                var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n                if (wbMode) {\n                    wbMode.value = s.whitebalance.mode;\n                    onWbModeChange(s.whitebalance.mode);\n                }\n                if (s.whitebalance.red_gain !== undefined) {\n                    var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n                    if (wbRed) {\n                        wbRed.value = s.whitebalance.red_gain;\n                        setWhiteBalanceGain('red', s.whitebalance.red_gain);\n                    }\n                }\n                if (s.whitebalance.blue_gain !== undefined) {\n                    var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n                    if (wbBlue) {\n                        wbBlue.value = s.whitebalance.blue_gain;\n                        setWhiteBalanceGain('blue', s.whitebalance.blue_gain);\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复降噪\n            if (s.noisereduce) {\n                var dnrSpatial = document.getElementById('dnrSpatial');\n                var dnrTemporal = document.getElementById('dnrTemporal');\n                if (dnrSpatial && s.noisereduce.spatial_level !== undefined) {\n                    dnrSpatial.value = s.noisereduce.spatial_level;\n                    setNoiseReduce('spatial', s.noisereduce.spatial_level);\n                }\n                if (dnrTemporal && s.noisereduce.temporal_level !== undefined) {\n                    dnrTemporal.value = s.noisereduce.temporal_level;\n                    setNoiseReduce('temporal', s.noisereduce.temporal_level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复慢快门\n            if (s.slow_shutter && s.slow_shutter.dss_level) {\n                var ssSelect = document.getElementById('slowShutterSelect');\n                if (ssSelect) {\n                    ssSelect.value = s.slow_shutter.dss_level;\n                    onSlowShutterChange(s.slow_shutter.dss_level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复锐度\n            if (s.sharpness && s.sharpness.level !== undefined) {\n                var sharpnessInput = document.getElementById('sharpness');\n                if (sharpnessInput) {\n                    sharpnessInput.value = s.sharpness.level;\n                    setSharpness(s.sharpness.level);\n                }\n            }\n            // 恢复画面设置\n            if (s.image_settings) {\n                var brightness = document.getElementById('brightness');\n                var contrast = document.getElementById('contrast');\n                var saturation = document.getElementById('saturation');\n                if (brightness && s.image_settings.brightness !== undefined) {\n                    brightness.value = s.image_settings.brightness;\n                }\n                if (contrast && s.image_settings.contrast !== undefined) {\n                    contrast.value = s.image_settings.contrast;\n                }\n                if (saturation && s.image_settings.saturation !== undefined) {\n                    saturation.value = s.image_settings.saturation;\n                }\n                var imgData = {};\n                if (s.image_settings.brightness !== undefined) imgData.brightness = s.image_settings.brightness;\n                if (s.image_settings.contrast !== undefined) imgData.contrast = s.image_settings.contrast;\n                if (s.image_settings.saturation !== undefined) imgData.saturation = s.image_settings.saturation;\n                if (Object.keys(imgData).length > 0) {\n                    apiPut('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/settings', imgData);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    });\n}\n\n// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":42584,"output":1656,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44240,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783261891984,"responseId":"cht000db9e2@dx19f32b119db2871503"}}
