{"type":"message","id":"5c475128","parentId":"27990ad1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T14:35:05.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n...\n...\n\n现在 settings.json 里有保存的设置。我需要测试恢复功能是否正常工作。\n\n步骤：\n1. 断开当前设备连接\n2. 重新连接设备\n3. 检查参数是否自动恢复到保存的值\n\n但是，从日志来看，服务启动后已经在处理 GET 请求（/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/...），这说明设备已经连接上了。\n\n我需要先断开设备，然后重新连接，这样才能测试恢复功能。\n\n让我先检查当前设备的连接状态，然后断开它。\n...\n...\n...\n\n设备已连接（192.168.5.72）。需要断开后重连来测试恢复功能：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c4966177dcf2493dbd9eb4b7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"import requests; r = requests.post('http://localhost:10280/api/v1/devices/192.168.5.72/disconnect'); print(r.json())\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe user is asking me to continue testing. The settings are saved correctly. Now I need to test if the restore function works properly. \n\nThe issue is:\n1. When device connects, loadAllImageParams() is called which sets _isInitializingImageParams = true\n2. Then restoreSettings() is called after 500ms delay\n3. restoreSettings() should call API to apply the settings to the device\n\nBut wait - I need to check if restoreSettings() is actually being called. Let me check the index.html to see how it's invoked.\n...\nsettings.json有保存的参数。检查前端是否正确调用restoreSettings()：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cf2ff6adf8c646959abb9a41","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"restoreSettings\" astrohub/src/web/includes/index.html astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":246,"output":466,"cacheRead":54450,"cacheWrite":331,"totalTokens":55493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783262092404,"responseId":"msg_3304bb9a-735b-48a1-a403-7635ea3d70ef"}}
