{"type":"message","id":"5fe480b7","parentId":"b9e50636","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:12:09.757Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\nThe user is asking me to continue. Let me analyze what I've found:\n\n1. The shutter endpoint code looks correct - it's using `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` endpoint\n2. The code saves settings only when PUT returns 200\n3. The user is asking why shutter setting returns HTTP 400\n\nLooking at the code:\n- Line 3327: `xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\"` - wait, this looks wrong. It should be `ver20` not `ver20`. Let me check the original code again.\n\nActually looking at line 3327: `xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\"` - this is using `ver20` which seems correct for Hikvision.\n\nBut wait - the user mentioned earlier that shutter setting returned HTTP 400. This could be because:\n1. The device doesn't support that shutter value\n2. The XML namespace is wrong\n3. The device requires a different endpoint\n\nLet me test the current shutter endpoint to see what's happening.\n\nActually, I should first check what the current shutter value is on the device, and then try to set it.\n...\n老板的问题是：快门设置返回HTTP 400，和保存有什么关系？\n\n答案：\n1. HTTP 400是设备端返回的错误，说明设备不接受这个快门值\n2. 保存逻辑只在PUT成功(200)时才执行，所以HTTP 400时不会保存\n3. 当前settings.json里没有shutter字段，说明快门设置一直没成功过\n\n让我测试一下当前设备的快门设置：\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板说得对。快门设置失败(HTTP 400)和保存是两回事。保存只在设备端返回200时才执行。\n\n当前settings.json里没有shutter字段，说明之前快门设置一直失败。让我测试当前设备快门：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4412cfb10e074bc99ba6527c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport requests\n\n# 1. 获取当前快门值\nr = requests.get('http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/shutter', timeout=5)\nprint('获取快门:', r.json())\n\n# 2. 尝试设置快门为当前值\ndata = r.json()\nif data.get('success') and data.get('data'):\n    current = data['data'].get('current_level')\n    print(f'当前快门: {current}')\n    \n    # 尝试设置相同的值\n    r2 = requests.post('http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/shutter', \n                       json={'level': current}, timeout=5)\n    print(f'设置相同值({current}):', r2.json())\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1574,"output":669,"cacheRead":94367,"cacheWrite":696,"totalTokens":97306,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783264310779,"responseId":"msg_4e6488c6-8781-4cc4-acd3-05440ab23245"}}
