{"type":"message","id":"2e0fd7a4","parentId":"03734c87","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:13:06.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"当前状态：\n- 曝光模式：manual\n- 快门模式：manual\n- 当前快门值：1/600\n\n问题是：虽然1/60、1/500在supported_levels里，但设置返回400。只有1/600可以设置。\n\n这很奇怪。让我测试一下：\n1. 先切换到auto模式\n2. 再切回manual\n3. 或者设备有其他限制\n\n实际上，我怀疑问题出在ISAPI XML请求上。让我直接用ISAPI测试：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cab7dc5f3cf444089e7b4905","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nfrom astrohub.src.api.ptz_client import PTZClient\nfrom astrohub.src.api.device_auth import get_device_auth\n\n# 获取设备认证\nauth = get_device_auth('192.168.5.72')\nprint('认证信息:', auth)\n\n# 创建客户端\nclient = PTZClient('192.168.5.72', auth)\nprint('客户端创建成功')\n\n# 直接ISAPI PUT\nxml_1_60 = '''<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"UTF-8\\\"?>\n<Shutter version=\\\"2.0\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\\\">\n  <ShutterLevel>1/60</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>'''\n\nxml_1_600 = '''<?xml version=\\\"1.0\\\" encoding=\\\"UTF-8\\\"?>\n<Shutter version=\\\"2.0\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\\\">\n  <ShutterLevel>1/600</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>'''\n\nresp1 = client.put('/Image/channels/1/Shutter', xml_1_60)\nprint(f'ISAPI 1/60: status={resp1.status_code}')\n\nresp2 = client.put('/Image/channels/1/Shutter', xml_1_600)\nprint(f'ISAPI 1/600: status={resp2.status_code}')\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":627,"output":507,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":98022,"totalTokens":99156,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783264370016,"responseId":"msg_c68612e7-142a-4422-965f-52520f9c18ba"}}
