{"type":"message","id":"c7fea083","parentId":"1aa8bad8","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:15:39.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\nInteresting results! Let me analyze the pattern:\n\nWorking:\n- 1/25 (0.04s)\n- 1/250 (0.004s)\n- 1/1000 (0.001s)\n- 1/30000 (0.0000333s)\n\nNot working (HTTP 400):\n- 1/30, 1/60, 1/125, 1/500, 1/2000, 1/4000, 1/8000\n\nLet me look at the pattern:\n- 1/25 = 25Hz\n- 1/250 = 250Hz\n- 1/1000 = 1000Hz\n- 1/30000 = 30000Hz\n\nFailed:\n- 1/30 = 30Hz\n- 1/60 = 60Hz\n- 1/125 = 125Hz\n- 1/500 = 500Hz\n- 1/2000 = 2000Hz\n- 1/4000 = 4000Hz\n- 1/8000 = 8000Hz\n\nWait, the successful ones are 25, 250, 1000, 30000. These are powers of 10 related?\n- 25 = 25\n- 250 = 25 * 10\n- 1000 = 25 * 40\n- 30000 = 30 * 1000\n\nHmm, that doesn't make sense. Let me think differently.\n\nActually, looking at camera shutter speeds, these are typically related to the video frame rate. In PAL regions (50Hz power), common shutter speeds are multiples of 50 or 25. In NTSC regions (60Hz power), they're multiples of 60 or 30.\n\nBut this device seems to only accept certain values. The ones that work are:\n- 1/25\n- 1/250\n- 1/1000\n- 1/30000\n\nThe pattern might be related to the sensor's readout speed or some hardware limitation.\n\nActually, wait - let me look at the XML being sent. Maybe there's an issue with how the value is formatted in the XML.\n\nLet me check the router.py code to see what XML is being sent.\n...\n有趣的结果！让我分析规律：\n\n成功的：1/25, 1/250, 1/1000, 1/30000\n失败的：1/30, 1/60, 1/125, 1/500, 1/2000, 1/4000, 1/8000\n\n让我检查router.py中发送的XML格式：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的结果！让我分析规律：\n\n成功的：1/25, 1/250, 1/1000, 1/30000\n失败的：1/30, 1/60, 1/125, 1/500, 1/2000, 1/4000, 1/8000\n\n让我检查router.py中发送的XML格式：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b1ce742668664ccf9528e1ac","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":3306,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":398,"output":884,"cacheRead":102174,"cacheWrite":403,"totalTokens":103859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783264502353,"responseId":"msg_f6568b9e-d239-4f38-8120-a9950593e9ef"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e90b5f47","parentId":"c7fea083","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:15:40.036Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_b1ce742668664ccf9528e1ac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async def set_shutter(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置快门参数 - v7.07: 使用独立 Shutter 端点\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        level = data.get(\"level\", \"1/60\")\r\n\r\n        # v7.07: 使用独立 Shutter 端点\r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<Shutter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n  <ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\r\n</Shutter>'''\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"shutter\", {\"device\": device_id, \"level\": level})\r\n            try:\r\n                mac_clean = device_id.replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n                if len(mac_clean) == 12:\r\n                    save_device_settings(mac_clean, {\"shutter\": {\"level\": level}})\r\n            except Exception:\r\n                pass\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": f\"快门已设置为 {level}\"}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置快门异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n\n[976 more lines in file. Use offset=3346 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783264540036}}
{"type":"message","id":"1dc29df4","parentId":"e90b5f47","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:16:21.631Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The code looks correct for the shutter API. The issue is that some shutter values work (1/25, 1/250, 1/1000, 1/30000) while others return HTTP 400.\n\nLooking at the XML structure:\n```xml\n<Shutter version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\n  <ShutterLevel>{level}</ShutterLevel>\n</Shutter>\n```\n\nThe issue might be that the XML namespace or structure is wrong. Let me check what the device actually supports by looking at the GET response more carefully.\n\nFrom earlier tests, the GET endpoint returns:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"current_level\": \"1/600\",\n    \"supported_levels\": [\"1/30\", \"1/60\", \"1/125\", \"1/250\", \"1/500\", \"1/1000\", \"1/2000\", \"1/4000\", \"1/8000\", \"1/30000\", \"1/25\"],\n    \"mode\": \"manual\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nBut we know from testing that only 1/25, 1/250, 1/1000, 1/30000 work. This is very strange - the supported_levels list doesn't match what actually works.\n\nWait, let me think about this differently. The user mentioned that in the AstroHub web console, they can set the shutter without issues. So the web console must be using a different endpoint or method.\n\nLet me check if there's a different endpoint being used. The current code uses:\n- PUT /Image/channels/1/Shutter\n\nBut maybe the device requires a different path or format. Let me check the function.py to see how the device capabilities are read.\n代码看起来正确。XML格式是对的。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. 设备端点对某些值不支持\n2. 或者需要不同的XML格式\n\n让我检查功能测试代码，看看它是怎么读取支持的快门值的：\n代码看起来正确。XML格式是对的。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. 设备端点对某些值不支持\n2. 或者需要不同的XML格式\n\n让我检查功能测试代码，看看它是怎么读取支持的快门值的：\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_75baeb0f206e46c4bdc93a95","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport os\nfor root, dirs, files in os.walk('astrohub/src'):\n    for f in files:\n        if f.endswith('.py'):\n            path = os.path.join(root, f)\n            with open(path, 'r', encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore') as file:\n                content = file.read()\n                if 'ShutterLevel' in content or 'shutter' in content.lower() and 'function' in path:\n                    print(f'{path}')\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":1644,"output":699,"cacheRead":102577,"cacheWrite":137,"totalTokens":105057,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783264540038,"responseId":"msg_9a3a9422-9869-46a8-af82-73c4f810ede0"}}
