{"type":"message","id":"39381c00","parentId":"89a4ed6a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:17:20.088Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to continue testing. Let me understand what I've learned so far:\n\n1. The shutter API endpoint returns HTTP 400 for some values\n2. Successfully set values: 1/25, 1/250, 1/1000, 1/30000\n3. Failed values: 1/30, 1/60, 1/125, 1/500, 1/2000, 1/4000, 1/8000\n\nLooking at the pattern:\n- 1/25 = 0.04s\n- 1/250 = 0.004s  \n- 1/1000 = 0.001s\n- 1/30000 = 0.000033s\n\nThe working values seem to follow a pattern of 1/(25 * 10^n): 1/25, 1/250, 1/2500 (not tested), 1/25000 (not tested), and 1/30000, 1/1000.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n- 1/25, 1/250, 1/1000, 1/30000 are the only ones that work\n- The failed ones are: 1/30, 1/60, 1/125, 1/500, 1/2000, 1/4000, 1/8000\n\nThis is very strange. Let me think about what the device actually supports.\n\nLooking at the function.py code, it mentions that for shutter mode, it should fetch capabilities from the device to get the opt values. The comment at line 447 shows an example of what capabilities might return:\n<ShutterLevel opt=\"1/25,1/50,1/75,...\">1/1000</ShutterLevel>\n\nSo the device reports what values it supports via the capabilities endpoint. Let me check what the device actually reports.\n\nBut wait - the user said the web console can set shutter values successfully. So there must be a different API or method being used there.\n\nLet me check if there's a different endpoint or format being used. The current code uses:\n- PUT /Image/channels/1/Shutter with XML body\n\nMaybe the web console uses a different endpoint or format. Let me look for how the web console handles shutter settings.\n\nActually, I should check the function.py to see how it discovers supported values. The comment at line 447-467 mentions fetching capabilities from a /capabilities endpoint.\n\nLet me check what the capabilities endpoint returns for this device.\n从function.py看到，设备通过capabilities端点报告支持的值。让我查询设备的实际能力：\n从function.py看到，设备通过capabilities端点报告支持的值。让我查询设备的实际能力：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_98c7e8eae9e1441c84d13ae0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory && python -c \"\nimport requests\n\n# 获取快门能力\nr = requests.get('http://localhost:10280/api/v1/ptz/192.168.5.72/image/shutter/capabilities')\nprint('Shutter capabilities:', r.json())\n\n# 获取功能检测的function.json\nimport json\nwith open('astrohub/data/devices/240f9b764193/function.json', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    func_data = json.load(f)\n    \nif 'functions' in func_data and 'shutter' in func_data['functions']:\n    print('\\\\nShutter in function.json:')\n    print(json.dumps(func_data['functions']['shutter'], indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2050,"output":920,"cacheRead":103858,"cacheWrite":1197,"totalTokens":108025,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783264603287,"responseId":"msg_1ec5986f-9fe9-4c12-a306-0cada583342f"}}
