{"type":"message","id":"8c295b8f","parentId":"f96d3b26","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:35:40.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to continue. Looking at the context:\n\n1. We're fixing the shutter `supported_levels` issue\n2. The device directory `240f9b764193` exists with `function.json` and `info.json`\n3. The current code tries to find the device by matching IP in `info.json`\n4. But we already know the device MAC is `240f9b764193`\n\nThe problem is: the code is trying to find the device directory by IP match, but it should use the device_id (which is the MAC) directly since we already have it.\n\nLooking at the code:\n- `device_id` parameter is passed to `get_shutter()`\n- The code resolves `target_ip` from `device_id`\n- Then it iterates through ALL device directories to find one matching the IP\n\nThis is inefficient and error-prone. Since `device_id` is already the MAC (clean format), we should directly use `DEVICES_DIR / device_id` to get the device directory.\n\nLet me fix the code to directly use the device_id as the MAC path.\n问题找到了。代码通过IP遍历匹配设备目录，但`device_id`本身就是MAC地址（240f9b764193），应该直接用：\n...\n问题找到了。代码通过IP遍历匹配设备目录，但`device_id`本身就是MAC地址（240f9b764193），应该直接用：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"...\nThe problem is found. The code iterates through device directories by IP matching, but `device_id` itself is already the MAC address (240f9b764193), so it should be used directly:\n...\n问题找到了。代码通过IP遍历匹配设备目录，但`device_id`本身就是MAC地址（240f9b764193），应该直接用：\n\n\n</think>\n\nThe issue is clear: the code is iterating through device directories to find one matching the IP, but `device_id` is already the MAC address (240f9b764193), so we should directly use `DEVICES_DIR / device_id` to get the device directory. This is much simpler and more reliable.\nThe code is unnecessarily complex - it iterates through all device directories to find one matching the IP, but `device_id` is already the MAC. Let me fix it to directly use `DEVICES_DIR / device_id`:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_2f0a5ddcc50349c1a72cd508","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # v8.47: 从 function.json 读取真实支持的快门值（device_id就是MAC）\n        supported_levels = []\n        try:\n            device_dir = DEVICES_DIR / device_id\n            func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\n            if func_file.exists():\n                func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n                if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\n                    supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\n        except Exception:\n            pass","oldText":"        # v8.47: 从 function.json 读取真实支持的快门值\n        supported_levels = []\n        try:\n            devices_dir = DEVICES_DIR\n            if devices_dir.exists():\n                    for device_dir in devices_dir.iterdir():\n                        if device_dir.is_dir():\n                            info_file = device_dir / \"info.json\"\n                            if info_file.exists():\n                                info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n                                if info.get(\"ip\") == target_ip:\n                                    func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\n                                    if func_file.exists():\n                                        func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n                                        if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\n                                            supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\n                                    break\n        except Exception:\n            pass"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider