{"type":"message","id":"2687ec47","parentId":"6e11d1ef","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:41:00.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"继续\"。我需要分析当前状态：\n\n1. 服务已重启，但API仍然返回 `[\"1/25\", \"1/30000\"]`\n2. 这说明我的修复代码可能没有生效，或者存在其他问题\n\n让我回顾一下我做了什么：\n- 我添加了两种方式查找 function.json：\n  1. 直接用 device_id 作为 MAC\n  2. 如果 device_id 是 IP，则遍历设备目录通过 info.json 匹配\n\n但为什么还是返回只有两个值？\n\n可能的原因：\n1. 我的代码可能有语法错误或者逻辑错误\n2. 代码可能抛出了异常被 catch 了但没有打印错误\n3. DEVICES_DIR 的路径可能不对\n\n让我检查一下代码，看看是否有问题。我应该：\n1. 先读取我修改后的代码，确认逻辑正确\n2. 添加一些调试信息或者检查异常\n3. 验证 DEVICES_DIR 的值\n\n让我先读取修改后的代码。\n让我检查代码是否正确应用，以及可能的异常：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ba8bfa56cd78449997251f8b","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":35,"offset":3260,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9f53ce7bc4314c57aacee82f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, 'astrohub')\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_devices_dir\nprint('DEVICES_DIR:', get_devices_dir())\nprint('Exists:', get_devices_dir().exists())\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe service is running and responding. But the `supported_levels` still shows only `[\"1/25\", \"1/30000\"]` instead of the full list of values from function.json. This means the code path to read function.json is either:\n1. Not being executed (exception being swallowed)\n2. Not finding the function.json file\n3. Not finding the `functions.shutter` key in the JSON\n\nLet me check what's happening. The device_id in the URL is `192.168.5.72` which is an IP, not a MAC. So `DEVICES_DIR / device_id` would be `DEVICES_DIR / \"192.168.5.72\"` which doesn't exist. The fallback should use `target_ip` to find the MAC from info.json.\n\nBut wait - I need to check what `device_id` actually is. In the API path `/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter`, the `device_id` could be:\n- The MAC address like `240f9b764193`\n- The IP address like `192.168.5.72`\n- Or some identifier that gets resolved to IP via `_resolve_device_id_to_ip`\n\nThe code already calls `target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)` so `target_ip` should be the IP. Then in the fallback, we iterate through DEVICES_DIR looking for info.json where `info.get(\"ip\") == target_ip`.\n\nLet me check if the function.json has the correct structure. From earlier we saw it has `functions.shutter.opt_values`. So the code should find it.\n\nThe problem might be that the service didn't restart properly, or the old code is still running. Let me check if there are multiple python processes, or if the code change actually took effect.\n\nActually, looking at the output, the service started and responded. But the result is still the old one. This suggests either:\n1. The code change didn't take effect (maybe the file wasn't saved properly)\n2. There's an exception being silently caught\n3. The function.json path is wrong\n\nLet me verify the code change was actually saved and check the actual code in the file.\nStill returning the wrong values. The function.json read might be failing silently. Let me check:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c3dcbc4f665342fc82876514","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nDEVICES_DIR = Path(r'C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\data\\devices')\ntarget_ip = '192.168.5.72'\n\nprint('DEVICES_DIR exists:', DEVICES_DIR.exists())\nprint('Iterating devices:')\nfor device_dir in DEVICES_DIR.iterdir():\n    if device_dir.is_dir():\n        print(f'  Dir: {device_dir.name}')\n        info_file = device_dir / 'info.json'\n        if info_file.exists():\n            info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n            print(f'    IP: {info.get(\\\"ip\\\")}')\n            if info.get('ip') == target_ip:\n                print(f'    MATCH!')\n                func_file = device_dir / 'function.json'\n                print(f'    function.json exists: {func_file.exists()}')\n                if func_file.exists():\n                    func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n                    print(f'    functions key: {\\\"functions\\\" in func_data}')\n                    print(f'    shutter key: {\\\"shutter\\\" in func_data.get(\\\"functions\\\", {})}')\n                    if 'functions' in func_data and 'shutter' in func_data['functions']:\n                        opt_values = func_data['functions']['shutter'].get('opt_values', [])\n                        print(f'    opt_values count: {len(opt_values)}')\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2033,"output":1301,"cacheRead":164228,"cacheWrite":1633,"totalTokens":169195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783266019356,"responseId":"msg_400de4fa-88af-4101-8e61-3309e6c1f22d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"678c2738","parentId":"2687ec47","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:41:01.169Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ba8bfa56cd78449997251f8b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async def get_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备快门当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取快门失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag in (\"ShutterLevel\", \"shutterLevel\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"current_level\"] = elem.text or \"1/30000\"\r\n            elif tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"min\"] = elem.text or \"1/30000\"\r\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"max\"] = elem.text or \"1/25\"\r\n\r\n        # v8.47: 从 function.json 读取真实支持的快门值\r\n        # device_id可能是MAC或IP，需要两种方式都能匹配\r\n        supported_levels = []\r\n\n[1072 more lines in file. Use offset=3295 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783266061169}}
