{"type":"message","id":"753ef56f","parentId":"452fb21d","timestamp":"2026-07-05T15:56:25.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\nThe user wants me to resume and provide the full report of my progress. Let me review what was accomplished in this conversation session.\n\nLooking at the conversation history, the key accomplishments are:\n\n1. **v8.46 Device Parameter Memory Feature** - Implemented automatic saving and restoring of device parameters\n2. **restoreSettings() bug fix** - Fixed the function to actually call APIs instead of just setting DOM values\n3. **Shutter supported_levels fix** - Changed from hardcoded list to reading from function.json\n4. **DEVICES_DIR import bug** - Fixed the NameError that was preventing the shutter fix from working\n\nLet me compile a comprehensive progress report.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## v8.46-v8.47 完整进度报告\n\n### ✅ 已完成的任务\n\n| 任务 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 设备参数自动保存 | ✅ | 8个端点PUT成功后自动保存到settings.json |\n| 设备参数读取API | ✅ | GET `/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings-saved` 端点 |\n| restoreSettings()函数 | ✅ | 加载参数后500ms自动恢复，调用API应用到设备 |\n| Toast抑制 | ✅ | 初始化期间不弹误报提示 |\n| 快门supported_levels修复 | ✅ | 从function.json读取真实opt_values（21个值） |\n| DEVICES_DIR导入修复 | ✅ | 修复NameError |\n\n### 📁 修改的文件\n\n| 文件 | 修改内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| `src/api/router.py` | 快门API从function.json读取opt_values；修复DEVICES_DIR导入 |\n| `src/web/includes/console.html` | restoreSettings()调用所有setter函数 |\n| `src/advanced/device_settings.py` | 新增模块，提供save/load接口 |\n\n### 🔧 修复的Bug\n\n1. **restoreSettings()只设DOM不调API** → 现在调用setExposureMode/setShutterSpeed/setIris/setWhiteBalanceGain/setNoiseReduce/setSharpness/apiPut\n2. **快门supported_levels硬编码** → 现在从function.json读取（从11个错误值改为21个正确值）\n3. **DEVICES_DIR未定义** → 在router.py顶部添加导入\n4. **set_shutter默认值1/60** → 从function.json读取\n\n### 📊 数据对比\n\n| 项目 | 修改前 | 修改后 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| supported_levels | 11个错误值（含1/60） | 21个正确值（从1/25到1/30000） |\n| 1/60是否支持 | 硬编码支持 | 设备不支持，已移除 |\n| 参数恢复 | 只设UI值 | 调用API应用到设备 |\n\n### ⏸️ 待验证\n\n1. 连接设备后参数是否自动恢复\n2. 快门下拉菜单是否显示21个正确值\n3. 断开重连后参数是否保持不变\n\n### 服务状态\n- 当前运行PID: 21656\n- 端口10280已监听\n\n---\n**需要我继续测试验证吗？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4292,"output":712,"cacheRead":174636,"cacheWrite":680,"totalTokens":180320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783266955323,"responseId":"msg_1dbc6b40-67f4-4038-b90e-5c91c41fd782"}}
