e\n3. There's an error in the code that's causing it to fall back to the old behavior\n\nLet me check the current state of the code to see if the changes are actually in the file, and if the service is running the updated code.\n让我检查router.py中get_shutter函数的实际代码：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_cfe5882bd22d449790f1220b","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":3260,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe user wants me to continue. Looking at the conversation history, the last thing I found was that DEVICES_DIR was not defined in router.py. The error showed:\n\n```\nNameError: name 'DEVICES_DIR' is not defined\n```\n\nThis was happening in the `get_shutter` function at line 3297.\n\nThe issue is that my code changes to router.py used DEVICES_DIR, but this variable is only imported inside a function (get_all_paths at line 2180), not at the module level.\n\nI need to fix this by either:\n1. Importing DEVICES_DIR at the module level in router.py\n2. Or using the existing import pattern\n\nLet me check the router.py imports and fix this issue.\nThe error is `NameError: name 'DEVICES_DIR' is not defined` - it's only imported inside a function. Let me fix this:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bc27dc3976334892bbb3e69e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":2180,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2877,"output":870,"cacheRead":178580,"cacheWrite":781,"totalTokens":183108,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783267170779,"responseId":"msg_cf088e07-bb00-4be0-ab07-56b51a21f12f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5c3193f","parentId":"c4dd5059","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:00:08.128Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_cfe5882bd22d449790f1220b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"async def get_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备快门当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取快门失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag in (\"ShutterLevel\", \"shutterLevel\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"current_level\"] = elem.text or \"1/30000\"\r\n            elif tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"min\"] = elem.text or \"1/30000\"\r\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"max\"] = elem.text or \"1/25\"\r\n\r\n        # v8.47: 从 function.json 读取真实支持的快门值\r\n        # device_id可能是MAC或IP，需要两种方式都能匹配\r\n        supported_levels = []\r\n        try:\r\n            # 方式1: device_id就是MAC\r\n            device_dir = DEVICES_DIR / device_id\r\n            if device_dir.exists() and device_dir.is_dir():\r\n                func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                if func_file.exists():\r\n                    func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                    if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\r\n                        supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\n            # 方式2: device_id是IP，需要通过info.json查找对应的MAC\r\n            if not supported_levels:\r\n                for device_dir in DEVICES_DIR.iterdir():\r\n                    if device_dir.is_dir():\r\n                        info_file = device_dir / \"info.json\"\r\n                        if info_file.exists():\r\n                            try:\r\n                                info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                                if info.get(\"ip\") == target_ip:\r\n                                    func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                                    if func_file.exists():\r\n                                        func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                                        if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\r\n                                            supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\n                                    break\r\n                            except Exception:\r\n\n[1048 more lines in file. Use offset=3320 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783267208128}}
{"type":"message","id":"56e381f4","parentId":"b5c3193f","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:00:08.129Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bc27dc3976334892bbb3e69e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    from src.config_paths import DATA_DIR, CONFIG_DIR, DEVICES_DIR, APP_DIR, SDK_LIBS_DIR\r\n    import json\r\n\r\n    # 默认值来自 config_paths (实际路径)\r\n    defaults = {\r\n        \"local_config\": str(CONFIG_DIR),\r\n        \"device_config\": str(DEVICES_DIR),\r\n        \"test_data\": str(DEVICES_DIR),\r\n        \"sdk_path\": str(SDK_LIBS_DIR),\r\n        \"astap_path\": r\"C:\\Program Files\\astap\\astap.exe\",\r\n        \"obs_path\": r\"C:\\Program Files\\obs-studio\\bin\\64bit\\obs64.exe\",\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    # 从存储文件读取已保存的配置 (覆盖默认值)\r\n    config_path = DATA_DIR / \"config\" / \"paths.json\"\r\n    if config_path.exists():\r\n        try:\r\n            with open(config_path, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n                saved = json.load(f)\r\n                defaults.update(saved)\r\n\n[2168 more lines in file. Use offset=2200 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783267208128}}
{"type":"message","id":"2feb9e4a","parentId":"56e381f4","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:00:42.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the problem clearly. The `DEVICES_DIR` is only imported inside the `get_all_paths()` function at line 2180, not at the module level. So when `get_shutter()` tries to use `DEVICES_DIR` at line 3297, it's not defined.\n\nThe fix is simple: I need to add `from src.config_paths import DEVICES_DIR` at the module level, or import it inside the `get_shutter()` function.\n\nLet me fix this properly.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_93fd37ff104a434e8aa74e2d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":137889,"output":186,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783267208135,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0f72a613-5983-93af-bf07-70072236f48a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"39cf126a","parentId":"2feb9e4a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:00:42.506Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_93fd37ff104a434e8aa74e2d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 统一路由聚合\r\n\r\n整合 M1-M11 所有模块路由到 /api/v1/ 下:\r\n- /api/v1/health            - 全局健康检查\r\n- /api/v1/discovery/sadp    - SADP 设备发现\r\n- /api/v1/devices/*         - 设备管理(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/ptz/*             - PTZ 控制(真实)\r\n- /api/v1/streams/*         - 流服务\r\n- /api/v1/calibration/*     - 校准\r\n- /api/v1/ascom/*           - ASCOM 设备\r\n- /api/v1/settings          - 系统设置\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport asyncio\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timezone\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\r\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, FastAPI, Query\r\nfrom fastapi.responses import JSONResponse, Response, StreamingResponse\r\n\r\n# v6.40: 操作日志\r\nfrom src.operation_logger import log_api, log_web, log_error, log_info\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n#  核心模块导入\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\r\nfrom src.core.ws_manager import WebSocketManager\r\nfrom src.core.ptz_controller import PTZDeviceController\r\nfrom src.ptz.isapi.ptz import PTZController\r\nfrom src.core.device_manager import DeviceManager\r\nfrom src.core.calibration_manager import CalibrationManager\r\nfrom src.core.auth import AuthManager\r\nfrom src.core.ascom_manager import ASCOMManager\r\nfrom src.core.task_scheduler import TaskScheduler\r\nfrom src.core.health_monitor import HealthMonitor\r\nfrom src.main.constants import VERSION, VERSION_NUM\r\nfrom src.advanced.device_settings import save_settings as save_device_settings, load_settings\r\n\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n#  路由前缀定义\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\n[4317 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783267242506}}
{"type":"message","id":"90045be2","parentId":"39cf126a","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:00:59.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The problem is clear: I've been using `DEVICES_DIR` in the `get_shutter()` function but it's never imported at module level. Looking at line 45 of router.py, I can see imports from `src.main.constants` and `src.advanced.device_settings`, but no `DEVICES_DIR` import.\n\nThe simplest fix is to import `DEVICES_DIR` from `src.config_paths` at the top of router.py. But I need to be careful - the user said \"只回答问题\" earlier and was frustrated. Let me just fix this properly.\n\nLooking at line 2180, `DEVICES_DIR` is imported inside `get_all_paths()` function as `from src.config_paths import DATA_DIR, CONFIG_DIR, DEVICES_DIR, APP_DIR, SDK_LIBS_DIR`. So the path exists.\n\nI should add `from src.config_paths import DEVICES_DIR` at the module level imports, near line 45 where other module imports are.\n\nLet me make the edit precisely.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了！`DEVICES_DIR` 只在 `get_all_paths()` 函数内部导入（line 2180），在 `get_shutter()` 函数中根本没定义，所以抛出 `NameError`，然后被 `except Exception: pass` 吞掉，导致走 fallback 返回只有 `['1/25', '1/30000']` 两个值。\n\n修复：在 router.py 顶部模块级导入 `DEVICES_DIR`：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_72a92d41f32d452cb8067453","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"from src.main.constants import VERSION, VERSION_NUM\nfrom src.config_paths import DEVICES_DIR\nfrom src.advanced.device_settings import save_settings as save_device_settings, load_settings","oldText":"from src.main.constants import VERSION, VERSION_NUM\nfrom src.advanced.device_settings import save_settings as save_device_settings, load_settings"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4198,"output":454,"cacheRead":179361,"cacheWrite":1163,"totalTokens":185176,"cost":{"in