utter to see what's there.\n...\n现在需要检查实际的get_shutter函数代码，看看是否有问题：\n...\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_00a23f11652f42478803e90e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":3292,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}},{"type":"text","text":"\n</think>\n\nThe user wants me to continue working on the shutter `supported_levels` issue. The API is still returning only 2 values instead of the 21 values from function.json. \n\nLet me think about what could be wrong:\n\n1. The service is running (PID 18600)\n2. The import is at line 45\n3. But the API still returns only 2 values\n\nLooking at the code structure, the issue might be that:\n- The `get_shutter` function is still catching exceptions silently\n- Or the code path to read from function.json is not being executed\n- Or there's still an error that's being swallowed\n\nLet me check the current state of the `get_shutter` function to see if there are any issues. I should read the actual code to see what's happening.\n\nThe summary says I was working on fixing the shutter `supported_levels` to read from function.json. The issue was that `DEVICES_DIR` was only imported inside `get_all_paths()` function, not at module level. I added the import at line 45.\n\nBut the API is still returning only 2 values. Let me check if there's an error being swallowed or if the code is not reaching the function.json reading part.\n\nI need to:\n1. Check the current state of the `get_shutter` function\n2. Add error logging or print statements to see what's happening\n3. Restart the service\n4. Test again\n\nLet me read the `get_shutter` function to see the current state.\n需要检查 `get_shutter` 函数的当前代码，看看是否有异常被捕获：\n\n\n</think>\n\nAPI仍返回2个值。需要检查 `get_shutter` 函数是否有异常被捕获：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6f4ac5aa4a0a4efbb8eda30e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":3260,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":2739,"output":1656,"cacheRead":186374,"cacheWrite":229,"totalTokens":190998,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783267643559,"responseId":"msg_95ea1a3c-879e-4b4f-a441-5d1e0bf036dc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4ff729e","parentId":"8e32b964","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:08:36.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_00a23f11652f42478803e90e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        # v8.47: 从 function.json 读取真实支持的快门值\r\n        # device_id可能是MAC或IP，需要两种方式都能匹配\r\n        supported_levels = []\r\n        try:\r\n            # 方式1: device_id就是MAC\r\n            device_dir = DEVICES_DIR / device_id\r\n            if device_dir.exists() and device_dir.is_dir():\r\n                func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                if func_file.exists():\r\n                    func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                    if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\r\n                        supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\n            # 方式2: device_id是IP，需要通过info.json查找对应的MAC\r\n            if not supported_levels:\r\n                for device_dir in DEVICES_DIR.iterdir():\r\n                    if device_dir.is_dir():\r\n                        info_file = device_dir / \"info.json\"\r\n                        if info_file.exists():\r\n                            try:\r\n                                info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                                if info.get(\"ip\") == target_ip:\r\n                                    func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                                    if func_file.exists():\r\n                                        func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                                        if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\r\n                                            supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\n                                    break\r\n                            except Exception:\r\n                                continue\r\n        except Exception as e:\r\n            import traceback\r\n            traceback.print_exc()\r\n        \r\n        if not supported_levels:\r\n            # 回退: 使用设备返回的min/max\r\n            supported_levels = [\r\n                result[\"data\"].get(\"max\", \"1/25\"),\r\n                result[\"data\"].get(\"min\", \"1/30000\")\r\n            ]\r\n        result[\"data\"][\"supported_levels\"] = supported_levels\r\n        result[\"data\"][\"mode\"] = \"manual\"\r\n        return result\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取快门异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"设置快门\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_shutter(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置快门参数 - v7.07: 使用独立 Shutter 端点\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n\n[1017 more lines in file. Use offset=3352 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783267716473}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8659632","parentId":"f4ff729e","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:08:36.475Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_6f4ac5aa4a0a4efbb8eda30e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/shutter\", summary=\"获取快门设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_shutter(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备快门当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\")\r\n        if resp.status_code != 200:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"获取快门失败: HTTP {resp.status_code}\"}\r\n\r\n        root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n        result = {\"success\": True, \"data\": {}}\r\n        for elem in root.iter():\r\n            tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n            if tag in (\"ShutterLevel\", \"shutterLevel\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"current_level\"] = elem.text or \"1/30000\"\r\n            elif tag in (\"minShutterLevelLimit\", \"MinShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"min\"] = elem.text or \"1/30000\"\r\n            elif tag in (\"maxShutterLevelLimit\", \"MaxShutterLevelLimit\"):\r\n                result[\"data\"][\"max\"] = elem.text or \"1/25\"\r\n\r\n        # v8.47: 从 function.json 读取真实支持的快门值\r\n        # device_id可能是MAC或IP，需要两种方式都能匹配\r\n        supported_levels = []\r\n        try:\r\n            # 方式1: device_id就是MAC\r\n            device_dir = DEVICES_DIR / device_id\r\n            if device_dir.exists() and device_dir.is_dir():\r\n                func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                if func_file.exists():\r\n                    func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                    if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\r\n                        supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\n            # 方式2: device_id是IP，需要通过info.json查找对应的MAC\r\n            if not supported_levels:\r\n                for device_dir in DEVICES_DIR.iterdir():\r\n                    if device_dir.is_dir():\r\n                        info_file = device_dir / \"info.json\"\r\n                        if info_file.exists():\r\n                            try:\r\n                                info = json.loads(info_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                                if info.get(\"ip\") == target_ip:\r\n                                    func_file = device_dir / \"function.json\"\r\n                                    if func_file.exists():\r\n                                        func_data = json.loads(func_file.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\r\n                                        if \"functions\" in func_data and \"shutter\" in func_data[\"functions\"]:\r\n                                            supported_levels = func_data[\"functions\"][\"shutter\"].get(\"opt_values\", [])\r\n                                    break\r\n\n[1049 more lines in file. Use offset=3320 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783267716474}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e0d56dc","parentId":"a8659632","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:09:06.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The code looks correct - it's trying to read from function.json. The API returns only 2 values which is the fallback (min/max from device XML). This means the code is failing somewhere before setting supported_levels from function.json, or the service wasn't restarted.\n\nLet me check: the API returns `supported_levels: [\"1/25\", \"1/30000\"]` which matches the fallback code at line ~3324-3327. So the try block at line 3293 must be failing silently.\n\nBut there's a `traceback.print_exc()` at line 3322 now. If there was an error, we'd see it in the logs. Let me check if there's any traceback in the output.\n\nWait - looking at the earlier log output, I saw `NameError: name 'DEVICES_DIR' is not defined`. But I added the import at line 45! Let me verify the import is actually there and the file was saved properly.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"代码看起来正确。API返回2个值说明fallback被执行了，说明前面的try块出错了。之前日志看到`NameError: name 'DEVICES_DIR' is not defined`，但我已经在line 45加了import。让我验证import是否正确生效：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4ef18bef15494de0b5f6dc56","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, 'astrohub')\nfrom src.config_paths import DEVICES_DIR\nprint('DEVICES_DIR:', DEVICES_DIR)\nprint('Exists:', DEVICES_DIR.exists())\nprint('Type:', type(DEVICES_DIR))\n\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":5318,"output":384,"cacheRead":186603,"cacheWrite":527,"totalTokens":192832,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783267716479,"responseId":"msg_6883a065-c945-4ec1-9f1a-9a25ad96906e"}}
