{"type":"message","id":"0270a956","parentId":"585e0343","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:14:43.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"...\nThe user is asking me to provide a complete report on three topics:\n\n1. Auto-reading previous settings - what settings, is it based on MAC as unique device identifier, through what script?\n2. Auto-scanning and loading device capabilities - exploring endpoint availability and limits, what script is used, what file is read?\n3. Are device limits info and previous settings info executed separately? What's the dependency relationship?\n\nLet me think through each of these:\n\n**1. Auto-reading previous settings (device_settings.py)**\n\nFrom the conversation summary:\n- Created `src/advanced/device_settings.py` module\n- `load_settings(mac)` function - reads from `data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n- `save_settings(mac, dict)` function - writes to `data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n- Uses MAC as unique identifier (data directory is named by MAC)\n- Settings saved include: whitebalance, noisereduce, exposure, shutter, iris, sharpness, slow_shutter, image_settings\n- The settings.json file structure was shown in the summary\n- The `restoreSettings()` function in console.html calls GET `/api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings-saved` to get saved settings\n- After `loadAllImageParams()` completes (500ms delay), `restoreSettings()` is called to apply saved settings to device\n\n**2. Auto-scanning device capabilities (function.py)**\n\nFrom the conversation summary:\n- Created `src/advanced/function.py` module\n- `FunctionDetector` class that probes device endpoints\n- Detects: shutter, iris, exposure modes, slow shutter (DSS), etc.\n- Uses ISAPI endpoints to probe capabilities\n- Reads capabilities from `/Image/channels/1/capabilities` endpoint\n- Extracts `opt` attribute values from XML responses\n- Saves results to `data/devices/{mac}/function.json`\n- The function.json contains: supported features, opt_values (supported ranges), current values\n- Frontend `loadShutter()`, `loadIris()`, `loadExposure()` all read from `deviceFunctionData.functions.shutter.opt_values` etc.\n\n**3. Relationship between the two**\n\n- They are independent systems\n- Device capability scanning (function.py) happens during device discovery/connection to determine what features the device supports\n- Previous settings loading (device_settings.py) happens after connection to restore user's last configuration\n- The dependency: function.json must exist first to know what features are supported, then settings.json can be applied only for features that are supported\n- Both use MAC as the directory key: `data/devices/{mac}/`\n\nLet me structure this as a clear, comprehensive report.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 完整报告\n\n### 1. 自动读取上一次设置\n\n**唯一标识**：MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n\n**存储位置**：`data/devices/{mac}/settings.json`\n\n**脚本文件**：`src/advanced/device_settings.py`\n- `load_settings(mac)` - 读取设置\n- `save_settings(mac, dict)` - 保存设置\n\n**保存的参数**（8类）：\n| 参数 | JSON字段 | 内容 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 白平衡 | `whitebalance` | mode, red_gain, blue_gain |\n| 降噪 | `noisereduce` | spatial_level, temporal_level |\n| 曝光模式 | `exposure` | mode |\n| 快门 | `shutter` | level |\n| 光圈 | `iris` | level |\n| 锐度 | `sharpness` | level |\n| 慢快门 | `slow_shutter` | dss_level, enabled |\n| 画面设置 | `image_settings` | brightness, contrast, saturation |\n\n**触发时机**：\n- **保存**：每个设置端点（router.py中8个PUT/POST端点）成功写入设备后立即保存到settings.json\n- **加载**：前端连接设备后，`loadAllImageParams()`完成500ms后调用`restoreSettings(deviceIp)`\n- **读取接口**：`GET /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/image/settings-saved`\n\n**前端流程**：\n```\n连接设备 → loadAllImageParams() → 从设备读取当前参数 → 延迟500ms → restoreSettings()\n→ GET settings-saved → 设置DOM值 + 调用各setter函数应用到设备\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. 自动扫描设备能力\n\n**脚本文件**：`src/advanced/function.py`\n\n**核心类**：`FunctionDetector`\n\n**探测方式**：\n- 通过ISAPI端点探测设备能力\n- 读取 `/ISAPI/Image/channels/1/capabilities` 获取支持的功能列表\n- 解析XML中的 `opt` 属性获取具体档位值（如快门支持的21个值）\n- 逐个端点测试可用性\n\n**探测的功能项**（function.py中的FUNCTION_DEFS）：\n| 功能 | 端点 | 探测内容 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 曝光模式 | `/Image/channels/1` | manual/auto/IrisFirst/ShutterFirst |\n| 快门 | `/Image/channels/1/Shutter` | opt_values（21个值） |\n| 光圈 | `/Image/channels/1/Iris` | opt_values |\n| 慢快门(DSS) | `/Image/channels/1/DSS` | enabled, DSSLevel opt_values |\n| 白平衡 | `/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance` | 模式、R/B增益范围 |\n| 降噪 | `/Image/channels/1/noiseReduce` | 空域/时域范围 |\n| 锐度 | `/Image/channels/1/sharpness` | 范围 |\n\n**输出文件**：`data/devices/{mac}/function.json`\n\n**数据结构**：\n```json\n{\n  \"functions\": {\n    \"shutter\": {\n      \"supported\": true,\n      \"opt_values\": [\"1/25\", \"1/50\", ...],  // 21个值\n      \"current_values\": {\"ShutterLevel\": \"1/600\"},\n      \"endpoint\": \"/Image/channels/1/Shutter\"\n    },\n    ...\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**前端使用**：\n- `loadShutter()` 从 `deviceFunctionData.functions.shutter.opt_values` 生成下拉菜单\n- `loadIris()` 从 `deviceFunctionData.functions.iris.opt_values` 生成下拉菜单\n- `loadExposure()` 从 `deviceFunctionData.functions.exposure_mode.opt_values` 生成下拉菜单\n- `loadSlowShutter()` 从 `deviceFunctionData.functions.slow_shutter.opt_values` 生成下拉菜单\n\n---\n\n### 3. 两者的关系\n\n**完全独立执行，无直接依赖**\n\n| 维度 | 设备能力扫描 (function.py) | 设置记忆 (device_settings.py) |\n|------|---------------------------|-------------------------------|\n| 触发时机 | 设备发现/连接时自动执行 | 用户修改参数时保存，重连时恢复 |\n| 输入 | ISAPI探测设备硬件能力 | 用户历史配置 |\n| 输出 | function.json（设备能力） | settings.json（用户设置） |\n| 是否自动 | 是，自动探测 | 保存自动，恢复需要前端调用 |\n| 失败影响 | 前端下拉菜单为空/禁用 | 参数不恢复，保持设备当前值 |\n\n**间接依赖**：\n- function.json 决定了哪些参数可配置（不支持的功能前端显示灰色/禁用）\n- settings.json 只恢复 function.json 中标记为 `supported: true` 的参数\n- 但代码上没有强制校验——如果 settings.json 有值但 function.json 标记不支持，仍会尝试恢复（可能导致HTTP 400）\n\n**目录结构**：\n```\ndata/devices/{mac}/\n├── info.json          # 设备基本信息（IP、型号、MAC）\n├── function.json      # 设备能力（function.py生成）\n├── settings.json      # 用户设置（device_settings.py生成）\n├── limit.json/csv     # 限位数据\n└── speed.json/csv     # 速度数据\n```\n\n**执行顺序**：\n1. 设备发现 → SADP获取IP/MAC → 创建 `data/devices/{mac}/info.json`\n2. 连接设备 → `FunctionDetector` 扫描 → 生成 `function.json`\n3. 用户操作 → 修改参数 → 保存到 `settings.json`\n4. 重连设备 → 前端读取 `function.json` 渲染UI → 读取 `settings.json` 恢复设置"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":4456,"output":1901,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":193024,"totalTokens":199381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783268019401,"responseId":"msg_41131b24-3216-4df2-acab-2b0a25750431"}}
