{"type":"message","id":"4784cd22","parentId":"8e109a55","timestamp":"2026-07-05T16:59:40.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我重新执行任务。让我看看之前的上下文：\n\n1. 用户要求：\n   - 保存设备当前配置，是整个astrohub主控台上所有设置的快照\n   - 保存中需要异步，需要降低占用\n   - 在框选白平衡和框选自动对焦时，过程中有大量调用，需要在整个对焦或白平衡结束之后执行一次保存\n   - 禁止开发新脚本，禁止引入新脚本，只允许在现有的条件下开发\n   - 禁止过度开发，需要全面修复\n\n2. 我已经完成了：\n   - 备份了代码到backup_20260706_0032\n   - 修复了快门bug（添加了import json，删除了rogue目录）\n   - 快门API现在返回21个正确的值\n\n3. 现在需要：\n   - 找到WB/focus完成时的SSE事件处理\n   - 在这些事件处理后添加保存设置的调用\n   - 确保保存是异步的，不会阻塞\n\n4. 我创建了find_sse.py脚本来查找SSE事件处理器，但还没有运行它。\n\n让我先运行这个脚本找到SSE事件处理器的位置，然后修改index.html在WB/focus完成后添加保存调用。\n\n另外，我需要理解用户说的\"所有设置\"是什么意思。从settings.json来看，它包含：\n- whitebalance（模式、红增益、蓝增益）\n- noisereduce（空间等级、时间等级）\n- slow_shutter（DSS等级、启用）\n- exposure（模式）\n- iris（等级）\n- sharpness（等级）\n- image_settings（亮度、对比度、饱和度）\n- shutter（等级）\n\n用户说要保存\"所有设置的快照\"，这意味着每次WB/focus完成后，需要读取当前所有设置并保存。\n\n让我先找到SSE事件处理器的位置。\n老板，继续执行。先找到WB/focus完成的SSE事件处理器：\n...\nThe user wants me to continue. I've fixed the shutter bug and now need to implement the settings save system. Let me:\n\n1. First find where the WB/focus completion events are handled (SSE events)\n2. Then add a call to save all settings after those operations complete\n3. Make the save asynchronous\n\nLet me search for the SSE event handlers in index.html to understand where WB/focus operations end.\nThe user wants me to continue. I've fixed the shutter bug. Now I need to implement the settings save system:\n1. Save all settings as a snapshot after WB/focus operations complete\n2. Make it asynchronous\n3. No new scripts, only modify existing code\n\nLet me find where WB/focus completion events are handled in the frontend (SSE events).\n老板，继续执行。先找到WB/focus完成的SSE事件处理器：\n\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_4db5239661a742e48369819f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory && python find_sse.py","workdir":"C:\\Use